The cozy atmosphere and friendly, attentive staff make it a perfect spot for a casual meal or a special occasion. Don’t miss their locally-sourced ingredients and creative menu — highly recommend!”","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipORYSHJtVLswL4X-zIBr5A_DI2yw0214FR96G9F&fid=0x0:0x93f62016d3743af"],"When":"2024-11-26"},{"Name":"Izzy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVAgf2kUFFUPOmbKxXV6w4FXEglUD9hHripnX8rOvq95I8uwQcTgA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had an amazing experience at this restaurant! As someone who needs gluten-free options, I was thrilled to see so many choices on the menu.

The food was delicious, and the service was fantastic—attentive, friendly, and accommodating. The only hiccup was the choppy radio, but when we asked if they could turn it off, they were incredibly kind and took care of it right away.

Highly recommend for anyone looking for a friendly spot with excellent service!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP5eIdOA3ydo5p3PS96aP375FXyb4pIT9Q7hZg-&fid=0x0:0x93f62016d3743af"],"When":"2024-11-9"},{"Name":"Kristine Johnson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVGP_smfmYAXXxdYn6kX34hvFr9mR1IvLF3TA-_x61hquGska6i=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Absolutely marvelous server :) I had so many dietary restrictions, and she made sure I got exactly what I could eat. And the salad was delicious as well. I can't wait to go back ♡","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPM3hO99UAYTOGSWLJsttOF_RGvKQHzeznjceFo&fid=0x0:0x93f62016d3743af"],"When":"2024-8-19"},{"Name":"Maria Teo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLWyktuFjeslZVKUjk8Q5cAT0oRtHf1mhF8v-MshhF0aeQQodU=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Food was great!! We had the salmon benny (3.5/5) and the pulled pork hash (5/5) for brunch! The bistro was clean and has nice decor. Our service was a bit slow when we dine in but staff members were very friendly. I would definitely go back 😄","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPPWHOuxTroWCk7vTSJMMFIzHhTvLZau6tGyPwj&fid=0x0:0x93f62016d3743af"],"When":"2024-8-29"},{"Name":"Mehr Poulad","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKnMmsASCmXLOvaFhR1RoQ03vxNx7oVUBdwy_npEYvb7k7uZA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great spot in maple ridge with really good food and service. The tacos were amazing. Gets really busy during peak times so be ready to wait.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMqgiVxecbAj9pT8-aq7nxoDkzoio8mxgqR3kxf&fid=0x0:0x93f62016d3743af"],"When":"2024-8-19"},{"Name":"Kyle G","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK72jrQUOno3MgtLl1WKy-Lz_eO61EdbiS2qO4YAE9hJAly_w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Quite far from Vancouver.

Came here to meet some friends for Saturday brunch.

Ordered the Big Feast Grilled Club and sneaked a few bites of the Breakfast sandwich.

The grilled club had thick crisp bacon, chicken breast, lots of mayo, shredded lettuce and a side of salted fries. The club was a bit messy/fell apart, fries were crisp and salted just right. Overall the club was good and would order again.

My sneak bites of the breakfast sandwich with roti as the bun were good but the side roasted potatoes were a bit burnt and carbonized which was a bit off putting. I would try the breakfast sandwich next time but with a different side maybe with fries if they could substitute. The carbonized potatoes were just off putting and I don’t think I’d enjoy the rest of the meal because of that.

Staff were nice and attentive always came by refilling beverages.

I would recommend and definitely say give it a try if in the neighbourhood but not so much trek from Vancouver.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOUmd2RqDI-EfOrMMgoERD42-nQGneS23YaRbxL&fid=0x0:0x93f62016d3743af"],"When":"2024-6-9"},{"Name":"James Mendonca","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKDOYVs1G-8iT9QF6Fj3_nUauDo1DS6zISrEp3lZ9wij4inDQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is fantastic restaurant. I enjoyed everything about this restaurant. The service is optimistic and professional. I like the design of the interior, despite the small venue space. I ate there for lunch and had the Lennon's French Toast. It was the best French toast I have ever had at any establishment. All of the ingredients pay compliments to each other and taste great altogether. The coffee was not just great, it was Grade-A quality. I hope to come back to Big Feast Bistro very soon when I am in Maple Ridge again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP3_5WxTHzhY1ttn8VTIuxmZW2fbMK6T64vznqn&fid=0x0:0x93f62016d3743af"],"When":"2023-11-28"},{"Name":"Shirley Treger","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJHx6Pc61V0ABlvEQKFkcuPpCGH2YyflokfZ6ACHcUWA7KJxg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The food is sooo Delicious. I would definitely recommend this to Everyone. Breakfast: What's your story morning glory..Yummy 😋 Meat loaf...just like mama made. My friends and I go there whenever we are in the area.","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"jasmimaria R","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW4pJsI6zmjzg6T7Vv1nULcTI0hckuLuMTShtjT6u4cC-gzFPL6=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I had a good experience at Sammy J’s in Maple Ridge. The food was delicious, and the customer service was friendly and attentive, which made the visit enjoyable. However, I was disappointed with the drinks. Out of the three different drinks we ordered, all of them were either watered down or lacked flavor. I hope they improve the consistency and taste of their beverages, as this was the only aspect that missed the mark for me. Overall, a great spot for food, but the drinks could use some work.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPDiRl-nZy5cP77L5fnmFOLJtL88N6_3XaxGg5Z&fid=0x0:0xf535f635f633f58d"],"When":"2024-10-8"},{"Name":"Fallon Conway","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIRn0Q61dGB1Ogh71s4IMnyPpSgIxz2IAOpiPuQnyr0ts3m-A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Our experience was amazing. Over all it was a 10/10 and definitely recommend this restaurant!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mrityunjay Kumar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK02yKU4inEgudvhGGlKrBrAKZRxhuwnfeJyD_JeTGVlWa7qQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Me and my wife had good time there, it was sunny afternoon and happy hour. We had Guinness beer, good vibes, nice ambience. Will visit again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPixfVGvfjQYbS1HHSlBjrodmEy10jDdg7HXY0E&fid=0x0:0xf535f635f633f58d"],"When":"2024-9-28"},{"Name":"Jessameen Dela Peña","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX9mRpmL8-ZJUG7UPFcnsjzRdxjABif-MswbO1rxgJyyWfns8Jd=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I had the Canadian burger, which was good but didn’t stand out as exceptional. The fries were actually the highlight of the meal for me. I also tried the chicken wings, which seemed a bit small and were served in a bowl that made the portion look less impressive. The honey garlic wings were somewhat dry, but the Cajun flavor was fantastic. Overall, it was a mixed experience.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN5OL_bw8B-kUBbiNtC0Axq7qm7qO8arvvn-P3b&fid=0x0:0xf535f635f633f58d"],"When":"2024-8-24"},{"Name":"ClayPhoenix4","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVelJECogE7AFzsG2ZmzVGlq92_4MqwMY_QK6n2nHeBRJeGCXg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We managed to get in without a reservation on Father's Day without any delays, but had to sit at a bar stool high table because all other tables for 2 were allegedly reserved (even though we could clearly see there was 2 booths by front window for 2 but dirty). I would have gladly waited for them to clean them because I have poor balance due to strokes and asked for a low table or booth but was denied. The tables ended up unused for at least 20 minutes.👎 Lucky for me a brought my percussion gun to use on my leg for most of our time there.
The food is decent and service is ok. The drinks were good and there was lots of people there, but the music is a bit on the loud side. Which is kind of ironic because if you go outside there is a sign asking people not to be loud. 🤔
Hopefully next time I can get a proper chair or booth that will not make the side of my body go completely numb and I can enjoy the atmosphere since they gave us a $10 promo card for "Dads."","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM9j41vk7-ebX0mWwHOb3HEIFZ94f8sfoN_rb8c&fid=0x0:0xf535f635f633f58d"],"When":"2024-6-17"},{"Name":"RIO HR","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVIF7GpV4m64oZ0qQLa2t66NMefnxrzruALvqDOSbCmwkvF-Ues=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The girls out here are so dam. Sammy j is the place to be for great food, awesome cocktails and drinks and smiles of happiness","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN9JiN0_n4boMTj3oipaqeLn1vRMSbG0U0ikbhK&fid=0x0:0xf535f635f633f58d"],"When":"2024-9-2"},{"Name":"Anna Manansala","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUmPEjbEU--G6ZvwM9BF3cXB1twGAgi58wl6xVmDzsfFIrX-aN6=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Food is great! Even if you're not going there, it's worth traveling across Canada to try the pies—they're scrumptious! The food is amazing. The atmosphere is very Canadian, making me feel like a tourist, lol. The service is excellent with very friendly people. The ingredients in the food feel very fresh, which makes it special.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP2aJVHFpsl_4xj9TDXq_bGhqoYh0UTgehlWqpZ\u0026fid=0x0:0x63c9b20db4c582cf"],"When":"2024-7-6"},{"Name":"Meral","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWZgJDSBQQNKp8dP0oLNQ0hDG3ysmSYlwA2fle373dORaWJmgoR=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Bought pie for $7+tax+tip so almost $10 for each slice,but to go sizes are so much smaller than what they led us believe. So disappointed. You can see how little that pie is next to my finger and hand cream","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMkiP0Y_XmvTIRiEfeApg4CkBT_ktVgZ3GVoRwo\u0026fid=0x0:0x63c9b20db4c582cf"],"When":"2024-10-28"},{"Name":"Taz e Bear","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWUZQyNVNSfKOL9C89OWIJAxQIkFj-drpgJaXIBnJ3XH8o9jkaH=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is one of my favourite restaurants the staff are very attentive. Did I mention they have some of the best Pies I have ever had many people come to just buy the pies to take out.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPzh0iayn86ffihFCsFPTDtzFbGLnguFR1bfd1R\u0026fid=0x0:0x63c9b20db4c582cf"],"When":"2023-3-13"},{"Name":"J. [{"Name":"Sydney Doucette","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVdUZIJT4JRDl1o0l6MQBPnumPIkN3Dfsmrob9XSLV_dhidQyk=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve never written a Google review in my entire life, but this pizza place was so good that I had to write one. The workers were very helpful and very nice. The prices were so good that I went 3 times in one day! My favourite item there is the Bronx bread deluxe. All in all, a very underrated pizza place.

If I could rate 10 starts I would.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMZq4v9oU2UT450TpRRwXPb4Czj-9ZNUBbMvpse&fid=0x0:0x9a3de7542d4571ba"],"When":"2024-10-26"},{"Name":"Jennifer MacLeod","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUadxIWYt0q6QEIVv32j21XPBQqLCZCzg2bPSR_6PhDEjmDiFc=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My boys are in love with Albion Pizzeria and my husband and I love it too. It’s one place we can all agree on! Our favourite pizza is the custom 3 topping pizza with cheddar cheese, sausage crumbles and pepperoni - it’s amazing! And the deluxe Bronx bread is also amazing. The new owners are so kind and always chat with us and our boys while we pickup. I can’t thank them enough for selling top notch pizza and making my boys smile too! Thanks Albion Pizzaria!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPnFn43VbuztR3Byh5KEb7m5_fbqY1FGHOb9BMh&fid=0x0:0x9a3de7542d4571ba"],"When":"2024-11-12"},{"Name":"Nick","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV8i6aZWX5wFrYB9tM2WdmFdLgNXisODy2uyMR7VD7WXU3hwANM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Super friendly staff and tasty pizza. Great way to recharge after mountain biking in the area!

Pictured: a small Rustic Italian pizza for $16.99","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPYA_A9Gtf3KM9WAoa5GhsDqYMJc1ha7wqJhA3P&fid=0x0:0x9a3de7542d4571ba"],"When":"2024-8-18"},{"Name":"Blanca Dominguez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXozJyQEsVNp6ciGkUY6Sa-1YO272YN4VblUKVzCFOM8bSL-1c6Aw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I’m not picky at all but this was quite the shock! The quality and taste are night and day from what it used to be earlier this year. We ordered a pepperoni pizza this evening and I literally thought it was just a cheese pizza cuz I did not see any pepperoni. My husband said there were a couple on his. The pizza was SO flat, crust was flat. It’s too bad cuz this used to be our favourite place as it’s walking distance. So disappointed. I’ve seen the owners comment they are using the same recipe but if this was so, I wouldn’t have run to the reviews to see if owners had changed after we opened the box.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Rochelle Soriano","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXWGxDqO26_it_aLWhqYDbBce7Hdq3JHVPDqMz-d6ad5S6xcvdQWQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is my 3rd time having a pizza in Albion and i keep on coming back. Firstly, this is a small pizzeria in a small town and i am always a fan of locally made pizzas that makes it special and unique. Second, the place is really clean. Thirdly,  I always love double pepperoni or hawaian pizza. Fourth, it is best if you eat it fresh from the oven because of the quality of their cheese and the dough. (I worked in a chain pizza restaurant so i can tell the difference.) Lastly, the customer service especially the young girl in the store today is outstanding. Kudos!

and of course always ask for the "today's deal" to have a really good price! ☺️","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMQlK6FjYAIm_SNZbPTHHTkF4fJNq1YB_ck3sg_&fid=0x0:0x9a3de7542d4571ba"],"When":"2024-1-5"},{"Name":"ulearn","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVVqdbbGKqtOlB_UPwPQj-3KwX4ez-IUE9Zs16_kfn3C4jmbXC5ag=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Residing in Burnaby and making regular trips to Maple Ridge for chiropractic appointments, I've consistently driven past this pizzeria. Looking back, I regret not stopping in sooner, as the pizza here is undeniably delicious. While it falls on the pricier side, the exceptional quality of the food more than justifies the cost.

I visited on a Wednesday as a walk-in, and the owner, who was alone, was managing a constant flow of walk-ins and pickups. Despite the hustle, he immediately acknowledged my arrival, inquired about my order, and, to my surprise, had already started preparing my pizza while simultaneously working on another customer's order. A true multitasker! It was evident that he's a big NY Yankee fan, judging by the sizable logo proudly displayed on the wall.

Being a vegetarian, I did notice that the menu options were somewhat limited. It would be fantastic if they could consider incorporating vegetarian alternatives like a Cheeseburger, Buffalo Chicken, or Pesto Chicken without the meat and chicken but substituting it. Additionally, introducing options with 'Beyond Meat' could cater to those seeking healthier choices.

To top it off, Albion Pizzeria even offered ice cream. When I inquired about the small and large scoops, the owner mentioned that their large scoop is an equivalent to three scoops, unlike the standard two you'd find in many other ice cream parlours. I know my kids would be thrilled about  that!

Let's get back to the pizzas....Despite the somewhat restricted vegetarian choices (4 pizzas), the exceptional taste of the pizza makes me eager to return without a doubt! I was so captivated by the pizza that I couldn't resist grabbing a slice before taking a photo of the entire pizza—that's how impressive it was!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOTHkJyQzSrcufpfApTy-cNnPtbLxXcSggUseKj&fid=0x0:0x9a3de7542d4571ba"],"When":"2023-12-9"},{"Name":"Joanne Walker","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLJ-skD3gNOCBq_Kpl45bWQPCFqoryaLNUEMcjTKCZ8ip4W0Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great customer service. Ordered a couple of pizzas via door dash tonight, one was missing the extra topping I ordered. Phoned the store and they sent out a replacement pizza immediately at no cost. Very great service!!! Will definitely order again.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Crystal V","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJy_8JzOAdXYM50ytFR2HidA0G9Xsyge4e68t8ePZBmeAOiPA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great customer service and great pizza. Definitely one of our household favourites.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPSASCZZDDa31zysyOQOmpJ70W0weq0MSDGBRFE&fid=0x0:0x9a3de7542d4571ba"],"When":"2024-12-1"}]

The food was outstanding – everything was packed with flavor, fresh, and beautifully presented. The kebabs were tender and juicy, and the spices were just perfect. The service was top-notch as well; the staff was attentive, friendly, and made us feel right at home. It’s rare to find a place where both the food and service are equally amazing, but Hani Kebab delivered on every level. Highly recommend this place for anyone looking for delicious, authentic food and a wonderful dining experience!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Josh Woolgar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVgz3VfDT9HwXIZMM-_pOdiCbrHemy_2r-gjg2BoMFxbozJyz4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Absolutely huge portions!!! I got the number 1 ground beef option and it was really good! The staff are very friendly and offered us some red spice which was a great touch","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipObzCwB61pW-YhCchbogNe51Eqi19zV8Puac55-&fid=0x0:0xb7a90fbebcbd630"],"When":"2024-7-7"},{"Name":"ClayPhoenix4","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVelJECogE7AFzsG2ZmzVGlq92_4MqwMY_QK6n2nHeBRJeGCXg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"If I told you that I just got back from camping up in Harrison and on my last night I was joined by Bigfoot himself (and he really does drink Kokanee lol) there is no way you would believe me!

But this story is true.  There really is a spot for authentic Persian food; and it's in a dump of a mall in Maple Ridge. The portions are massive,  the food is awesome,  and the people that are working there greet you with a smile. There is even 3 different types of rice you can get with your meal. I highly recommend you ask for some of the red powder spice for your food to take it to the next level. They also have a nice hot sauce too! I had a chicken and beef skewer combo and I will certainly be back to try some other stuff I saw on display too.
Thanks for the fantastic lunch.😀","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOdGu0BDd1grVfiwIAxdJkXSgJFj-ZUbQopF1hZ&fid=0x0:0xb7a90fbebcbd630"],"When":"2024-6-23"},{"Name":"Jovelyn Rimando","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKsYQEuf-HbNcGuK304rveatZBvuqVQR33ng8N-3aVxgzaYKg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My experience here was great. My family love Iranian foods. The servings was so generous my son cant stop eating all the food i take home. For sure i will buy more of your foods. thank you so kuch","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOM7U2W8ry8ad72bP6M3wb0chPHHPPxfu8IftcY&fid=0x0:0xb7a90fbebcbd630"],"When":"2024-10-18"},{"Name":"M Lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIsGv955Ri875E7vGmsYaHqa37baEVpl4eh0b_zeRaT_a88ew=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"All the positive reviews for this family run establishment are correct. We had the steak kebab and Chicken drumstick. The portions are so large we couldn’t finish it. The food has such good flavour! Note: they are open late, after Haney Mall is closed. We did takeout at 7:30pm, which requires you call ahead, wait about 15 min, and you pay and grab your food at the back door. (See my photo for a pic as it can be easily missed). You can just pull up in your car and the door is right there. Easy peasy.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMjfFx6dfw50pU3WzJ4M91QgV1ezNJkiGJ2DRbz&fid=0x0:0xb7a90fbebcbd630"],"When":"2024-2-15"},{"Name":"Ben Chua","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUCSW5TKJ19PNA5OJkbpbbOOnA0K2QN6aO0WAwwmH4V0bXfi0sR=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Ordered Ghabeli which is only available every Friday Saturday and Sunday. It's lamb stew too very delicious. The owner is very kind as well highly recommended.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP1i61ssq2fSzR6TpQQP9Z3XZ2OBdXxt3eBnIWR&fid=0x0:0xb7a90fbebcbd630"],"When":"2024-11-26"}]

user_reviews: [{"Name":"Y. Cherski","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK-7SLlKKRW0Rqcp9wRXFlvt6gbh0rtI7PMIroLgxETtGiPwQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"For me, this wasn’t about the food – it was all about the experience! Got invited by friends to check out this quirky spot for all-you-can-eat Taco Tuesday, and I left with a pretty positive impression. Sure, the tacos are buffet-style, the simplest Tex-Mex you can imagine, but you can load up for just 11 bucks and change with no limit. Probably even better if you are having a few drinks too. But what really stood out to me was the saloon-style vibe and the farm surroundings, complete with scattered farm machinery and, the best part, horses! It’s simple, humble, and you won’t find many places like this around Metro Vancouver and close by. While the food might not blow your mind, at least in my experience, the atmosphere and the memories are totally worth the trip.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNg-SRzMYbykNFWD1NFF318L6Nb-fahQiO8vegw\u0026fid=0x0:0x1715fa59497ee645"],"When":"2024-9-13"},{"Name":"Mary Servant","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXHgLbeT0gou0iFPpk0IOFdoMBnJ7rC_3eS_v5DrAOPsTKPD22a=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I went down on Sunday for the first time for a meat draw that was a lot of fun. They had 4 draws, breakfast specia,l drink specials. It was a fun way to spend the afternoon. The place is quite rustic with a horse ranch out behind. You'll see some pictures of the horses. I liked the rustic feel. Really enjoyed my day.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNBYTloUDO_3mMB6KSrPd3uXAmZiM3bf1TFn67C\u0026fid=0x0:0x1715fa59497ee645"],"When":"2024-2-19"},{"Name":"Jacquie Montgomery","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVakvhPhacxeS1WwgOroGpzbPBsfmFp83Y69hps_mEVBdCz0b2z=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Attended a live music event. It was excellent with very friendly servers.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPSVo-QEX8FGmh7-d8ovHYch8CTvJk7DJqvKbSy\u0026fid=0x0:0x1715fa59497ee645"],"When":"2024-12-22"},{"Name":"John Pozer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXe0BvqmYZVSdl8vMzkjfI5nnnXlGPCIuhLYzs9LnFZvwXYyqQh7A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had lunch on the dog-friendly patio. Service was wonderful! Good pub-type food: fish \u0026 chips, chicken quesadilla. Limited beer selection. Not crowded at noon on Friday. The lovely server made our stop here a memorable one.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNPhsay5SYwp30uFbPYnmAfTuXDlmxJJBDaftNO\u0026fid=0x0:0x1715fa59497ee645"],"When":"2023-10-14"},{"Name":"Chris L","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIlo27yi0c3tMg1MEFW8gltVROJwlBrQGtk927fnMS7KkAAA0UJ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"First time here with the famjam for the all you can eat taco buffet! You can't make food for this price at home. The food and the service was great. I can't get over the pricing of the food on the menu! I will defs have to come on a Wednesday for the burger and fries deal ($8.99). The price was right! I love how it's on a farm, love the vibe and best of all there where not too many other people (although I'm unsure why). We will be back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNpmKfrNrOh_MdTO8D2gO0TcoJI9_X7B6rt1luV\u0026fid=0x0:0x1715fa59497ee645"],"When":"2023-5-24"},{"Name":"Cassandra McDougal","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJEBUUqL3tIKmBdP0uJmyV8mvHRYPUb5ko5tg4188n33eDiww=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Super overpriced for the quality and serving sizes. Only 1 server for a large place so she was struggling. The pound of wings for $17 didn’t look like a pound and were overcooked. Not to mention the additional $0.75 for each dip… $19/Lb for those wings + 2 dips squirted out of a bottle is offensive.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMNkWZf4c2jQlsm2vYIe7nN6Q5vSX9x3rnLGrTv\u0026fid=0x0:0x1715fa59497ee645"],"When":"2024-3-29"},{"Name":"Laura R","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUGZhuVC2uAx0k5suRhJV1ugZ6Fs5IjHznwevseQ2nCnLEtoYg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The turkey melt was so good. everything we ordered was delicious and the staff were so kind and attentive. [{"Name":"Mumtaz June","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIJ57yuZsE_ZTkcmBSuSsnrCUFQFFqIO1h71zfMaPC0pedJxc4=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a fantastic experience at Desi Village! The biryani was absolutely flavorful, with the perfect balance of spices, and the chilli chicken was a standout—succulent, spicy, and incredibly tasty. The restaurant also has a warm and inviting ambiance, with tasteful decor that complements the delicious food. It’s a great place to enjoy authentic Indian cuisine in a relaxed setting. Highly recommend and will definitely be coming back!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO6XdGqgBOUTwZS_nyT60fYqy2x300WU1JO-gh7&fid=0x0:0x196e9603bd1d89db"],"When":"2024-12-3"},{"Name":"Prabhjot Pallan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKgO21cjeV01RW1fYtVVl6PtIv5eeCe5VS5GzlzoGXz_pXnTQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had an amazing experience at Desi Village Restaurant. Food and customer service was outstanding. An attractive ambiance is very welcoming. My kids loved their Shahi paneer, garlic naan and desserts. Highly recommended!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP3aWzdxmd3Y5aXwOQpSHQq46J5gD8DFKo0OKmY&fid=0x0:0x196e9603bd1d89db"],"When":"2024-12-14"},{"Name":"H M E","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX_onQ_VWTg3rT--s4p5BWrgkdHsv4YFtp2G5IvwsR019b0iUL7ZA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Fantastic. I found all the Indian restaurants in Maple Ridge so far to be quite bland (in terms of flavors, not just spice level) OR really inconsistent. The flavors of the food here absolutely blew me away. Can't say enough good things about it. I hope this restaurant stays!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM3KZli8btK833TtkTWUawdGbGxiWYzaATbxEPz&fid=0x0:0x196e9603bd1d89db"],"When":"2024-9-14"},{"Name":"Lovelreet Saroya","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUvOGb2IfCFbypZsuOw-IjYYD3blCxyEfzhhvvKF0CGDaT7vTw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This restaurant has a high-end, clean appearance, and the ambiance inside is very pleasant. The food was quite good, allowing me to experience a taste of indian cuisine. this place felt safe and clean. While the staff were friendly,. Overall, a good dining experience.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMRz1dgufk1-EgU7uN8o-EnxilF0mDl-2eOWHE&fid=0x0:0x196e9603bd1d89db"],"When":"2024-12-23"},{"Name":"Daniel Momich","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVMLmjbBzipiWC9y5kDPd5UcqBNmqkZL6tcv-IJKvt7gyj3UtM=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Wow! This place exceeded my, admittedly high, expectations on everything! Even the doggy bag containers. Absolutely the best onion bhaji I've ever had and the lunch special (pictured) is fantastic. Wish this was closer to me so I could eat here frequently","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOSl3I4ij-VLSDZ4MKJLVkvbLVt2c46K-W0fMYK&fid=0x0:0x196e9603bd1d89db"],"When":"2024-9-2"},{"Name":"kim steve","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVY0aDu0XYBkItQHLfUVtDyOF6M60HTL1zv2rPb7HeY4cWcnBitsA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Service was friendly and attentive, making for a truly enjoyable experience. Whether you're a fan of traditional Indian dishes or exploring new flavors, desi village is a must-visit. Highly recommend!

We order from desi village for company catering all time and it is always fresh and warm-  arrived on time +packaging is awesome. Food is warm for hours!

Call desi village for your next company catering. You won't be disappointed","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOA5wvlXEzVrdlb_SPpPXqlNM9BiJLrCYaK4a35&fid=0x0:0x196e9603bd1d89db"],"When":"2024-11-26"},{"Name":"Harsimrandeep Singh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJGFt-x6HLFjHpb_Q3PLYde7ugytZerHeSXMefsrXsO0NCc9Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We went for dine in first time and we had a really good experience over there . Ambience is so good and food was delicious. The manager and owner were so welcoming. They really put lot of efforts to ensure we are enjoying our food . Manager Jasmeen is polite and she make sure food is being served hot and asked us if we are having good experience. Must recommend to someone who wants to taste Indian food with good ambience in maple ridge.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Simmi Khanna","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUGpUak9WlX6-Up2MwVKzB2TnrCjSwj55Jg-LZgTqdZv_Bb4sKK4g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"If you’re in the mood for an exceptional dining experience featuring authentic East Indian cuisine, I highly recommend visiting Desi Village,  Recently, I had the pleasure of attending a Christmas party there, and it was an amazing experience. The ambiance was warm and inviting.The service was truly remarkable.
Every dish we tried was a testament to the chef's skill and dedication to authentic flavours. From the aerobatic biryani  to the flavourful curries, each bite was a celebration of spices that danced on the palate. The appetizers were equally delectable, perfectly complementing the main entrees.
Overall, my experience at DV was nothing short of fantastic. I left feeling satisfied and eager to return. This restaurant offers not just a meal but an unforgettable experience.","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Matthew Burger","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLJRolkmm2fzfIke3005sW5UKXFG1l2S4OhjL21TYo52WLgLQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My wife and I just celebrated our anniversary at Chameleon in Maple Ridge and were blown away by the food and service. From the amazing flight of margaritas and crispy pork belly, to the beautiful duck and salmon entrées and silky smooth Creme Brule. The food was matched by the super friendly and professional service. The next time we want a fine dining experience, we'll save ourselves the drive into Vancouver and go back to Maple Ridge.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM23BRISycp1Rbn993xX_elG-AFBpZ-v7rCfxsN&fid=0x0:0x9716dc938b2e95cc"],"When":"2024-8-9"},{"Name":"Tabitha Marie Geraghty","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW9l1bo7byb7Ucg-7YubvvEIA3WJTeAtKK5wv4tH4R1rOlNJiNsuQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Definitely kudos as we came during the holiday season and it was rushed..

Our server was incredible, the atmosphere and feeling of the holiday season was nice.. the food was good and the cocktails were great.. cost of the cocktails seemed a little bit high considering we were in Maple ridge..

The food was good and the intentions were great I think. Had we been there and ordered just a single meal that was hot and fresh we would have done better..

I will definitely give the chameleon a second try as I love the vibe and think that this type of restaurant is much needed in Maple ridge.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"I M","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI1LyaX0CiLTrEq3bzFkA46TOUxf3F2uw04JXuyWMEYipULAA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"First time being in Chameleon restaurant. Very open concept, nice decor. I would say a furniture could be upgraded a bit to more luxury seating or at least more comfortable. Air conditioning was a bit too much on for a cold evening outside so everyone in the restaurant wore their jackets on. The prices for food are apart with some of the expensive restaurants in Maple Ridge. Food was cooked very nice and very flavourful but by the time we got it 2 out of our 3 dishes were already not hot. Service was very good and the ladies are very friendly and professional. Bartender was very good and he made very tasty drinks. Overall a very nice restaurant and very good food.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM3u3wArI1S0QGuEnAexQKPIxi7m91IU1WXwgtc&fid=0x0:0x9716dc938b2e95cc"],"When":"2024-2-11"},{"Name":"Jordyn Ellis","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXsI3LX_wvDAdV8BpWxjJFMdZu6awlgZNab56wLuIe4uRha2LHqUQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Such a great restaurant! Came with my family for Mother’s Day. Our server was great and the girl they were training too!
The bartender came over to offer us a round of drinks because, to them, our food was taking a while but honestly it was such a great time to talk and catch up with my family. Overall experience was amazing and super friendly and welcoming! I can’t wait to come back and really wanting to try their brunch on weekends!

We got the house fries to start, soooo good! Then my dad got the pork belly, another amazing starter.

My main was the Seafood Risotto, so filling! Everything was so yummy.

My images consist of the seafood risotto and the butternut squash ravioli (without arugula)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOPD4elmKG2FI9WAamuWkKRE6FXTvT4qdhX4PQ3&fid=0x0:0x9716dc938b2e95cc"],"When":"2024-5-14"},{"Name":"Adrienne Thiery","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUUBXCivlSBhJvOBZazHc4ioFjrNhntsDhE4PMl3eZOKT8Bi10S=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"What a gem of a restaurant. I was sat on the lovely outdoor patio by my server, Kegan, who I am certain has fine dining experience and if he doesn’t then this place has outstanding training because he has that air of grace and courteousness I’ve only seen in fine dining. For the cocktail, I ordered a hibiscus spritzer (made by Kegan) and as soon as I tasted it I knew I was in for a treat regarding the rest of the food because this is a place that takes great care in getting things right. For appie I had the house fries which were cooked with the perfect amount of crisp and served with delicious aioli at well as fresh Parmesan. Also for appie fluffy fresh bread was served with cranberries in whipped butter…this was a stroke of genius, how often does one eat butter and think “wow this is remarkably delicious butter”. For the main course, I had the seafood risotto. It was perfection. Took the little bit I couldn’t finish home with me because I want every bite! I can’t wait to come back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipObS2A0Wh_perm73oY3q44eJJ_lPDK8bIi5EyMB&fid=0x0:0x9716dc938b2e95cc"],"When":"2024-8-12"},{"Name":"Lori Maginnis","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKXMpF1QdVxNT7xKos53oPkdIhvucK7OFj4gMh8jaKRBtudgw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Thoroughly enjoyed my meal at this restaurant!  Smoked tomato soup and grilled three cheese sandwich on sour dough. Good size portion. Reasonably priced. Very tasty. Soup was served up hot enough that it was hot to the last spoonful. Finished my meal off with a dessert of warm chocolate cake with a delicious chocolate sauce and gelato. I thought the portion was small but it was so rich and so delicious it was enough.

It was quite busy and only one server so it was a little slow but well worth the wait.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"J L","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIFhDWn7ZUpLtRn99UuZsUyHFtHtjy_5DOO3shBPyiizb4_vg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"First time customer, had an anniversary date here. The smells from the open kitchen had me salivating from the moment I entered. Food and service were top notch. Ceasar salad was the best I have ever had. The duck and the tenderloin were absolutely perfect. Very impressed with the desert. We shared a strawberry cheesecake deconstruction. The overall presentation of the food is artful and tidy. The portion sizes were reasonable. Inside the space is fairly small, but tastefully decorated, and lit for romance. Definitely not a cheap date, but worth every penny. I am so glad we chose this place to eat on our anniversary! I would rate 6/5 stars if I could!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"C Akins","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJfJ5TOZAppAoK1v3vAH4WnWh-tBc433e5bioDUDCccco7SkQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Hidden gem in Maple Ridge with great food and service. Prawns and oysters were fresh and delicious and the acknowledgement of our anniversary was appreciated.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOnTXw_ll8EK2bg0_AeQ0jD4V8ANr2jDeMMm2NT&fid=0x0:0x9716dc938b2e95cc"],"When":"2024-9-27"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Nidhi Kukreti","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUkwLGU0qL5R4gpFxJSktJd2bFgwdSs8uzUdgRJFVvHPQaNnjI=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"OMG, I love this cafe. I visited this place with my partner in evening. Everything was so good. I love the ambience, food and drinks. Recommend to set outside in evening, sunset looks amazing.

If you’re nonalcoholic and vegetarian you should try Blended cocktails peach flavour and Mediterranean falafel burger both are amazing. For alcoholic beverage we tried Corona bomb and original Bellini bomb and chicken wings. It taste so good. If you visit this place must try Corona bomb, chicken wings and their burger, they taste amazing.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO_ArvjDJcwgWIbb7HemgNeVJbeXv5QbLrTASJE&fid=0x0:0xdb1c783ecca39027"],"When":"2024-8-8"},{"Name":"Hay Leigh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU3lw-VM_9NiDkl3P2xmDBrgW_mHw454nMiYrvTPrl44QLhjbc7=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"This was our first time dining at kingfishers, and likely our last. The wait time for food is definitely longer than it should be, perhaps they’re short staffed on bussers and kitchen staff. The chowder is very underwhelming and bland. The wings were decent. The oysters arrived not on ice but in a pool of water. They were replaced but as another diner review stated, they seemed slimy? I wouldn’t recommend getting oysters here.
The burger tasted sort of good but it is thick and on the dry side. The fish and chips seemed to be the only dish that was enjoyed with no complaints. The service was really friendly and accommodating, I feel for the servers as the kitchen is clearly struggling to provide quality dishes.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMuxMNOufg28u_6KGNZclsLjNfE_Troz9ZqaNiJ&fid=0x0:0xdb1c783ecca39027"],"When":"2024-8-30"},{"Name":"MAY","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWaprK9T_y6Ya-MZ-gYNQwYVv0YO4LriJa7e6HtacNm__1Wvj4=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Ordered the halibut burger and fries. Burger was good. Fries were great! Location on the river is very nice and the staff were all friendly and wonderful. Will definitely come back!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMYTRPm0a0h4igfVbXKb5_9aw4iyjfMFsBEwzDx&fid=0x0:0xdb1c783ecca39027"],"When":"2024-12-17"},{"Name":"Cleemar M (CLM)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXGCGYDgdTLDzn3zRPmQzI47thdkSDXTgZ2wOwEV-c1M78oYSBe4Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"For a long time this restaurant was maligned and we did not go. Then we heard new management and went back and it was good. We decided to go back for a non transition time. The potato pave was spectacular and oysters were delicious. the chicken wings were overly salty and the chicken tenders were slightly dry but the salad was good. Service was excellent and the view is always good. The frozen mule was award winning and the margarita was kick arse. Beers and wine are solid and parking is ample. We will be back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMrZRPKgwT3O47ybARkJNqte4xCS7-lOuAR-KY7&fid=0x0:0xdb1c783ecca39027"],"When":"2024-5-17"},{"Name":"Anju","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV3NBFx2EqwPeNoEkV2MebyCIf0Znuxcr0FFtfaRAHKwPRpguQHlw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"They have a veggie burger which is amazing to see. We rate it 8.5/10. The falafel patty and sauce is really nice but there is a weird dry after taste. But it’s still yummy and would recommend it. Much better than any beyond meat type products.

Bellini 7/0. The ice is yummy but it’s at the top. The bottom tastes too alcoholy

Very nice along the river outside","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMhRgjhISHMh98uNj2jaFOVr7Lm1l9TH1R1Eph-&fid=0x0:0xdb1c783ecca39027"],"When":"2024-6-30"},{"Name":"Genn Richards","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIv-Bp7UhIKlk7R_WNzPvF8-SHy2B8dPh4abiUjm-9Owih0FQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Beautiful sunset dining on the patio.  One of the very few quiet places to enjoy a good dinner.  I had chicken, brie and arugula sandwich on focaccia.  Real chicken breast and not too much bread.  With house side salad was perfect with house wine.  Partner was happy as always with their fish & chips.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPQ5A-x7Zl1vfgaAaxS62rOS113eXGACnXnU6Pm&fid=0x0:0xdb1c783ecca39027"],"When":"2024-9-5"},{"Name":"Shawna Tregunna","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXYTagW2AheSQ7DO79y1mQQdFj6wxJ7_zgBzjQovYKazP5V_Mm_=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great view, great service, fantastic food! The salmon trio was excellent, my sister loved her fish tacos, we both commented on how delightful the crab cakes were and the beignets and mousse desserts were sinfully wonderful! After lunch we lingered and worked from our table for a while and it was lovely! Was surprised it wasn’t busier considering what a great experience we had. Will definitely be back when I visit the area again!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO5IBW8zm9iBC8lVI7T3ab71ardDEoHMh7XsSM&fid=0x0:0xdb1c783ecca39027"],"When":"2023-10-6"},{"Name":"Kim","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLNzJbWMZ95Bu6OYJjVkBX_DVmBC4cvkfu0ynB-Z65Byxh-Kg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had an exceptional evening at the wine and food pairing event! The food was fantastic – every dish reflected the chef’s dedication and artistry in creating a memorable menu. Greg was a warm and attentive host, making sure everyone felt right at home in the relaxed, casual atmosphere. Steve’s insights on the wines added a deeper layer of appreciation to each pairing. It was a wonderfully laid-back yet elevated experience that we’d highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"nayomi dilrukshi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKUCBqCVJYhiKOPG_Kq_gOhjPW_v7_VxNNSwZohvuvtYylBWA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently visited Ronny's Bistro and had the pleasure of trying their Carbonara Pasta. The dish was absolutely delicious, with the perfect blend of creamy sauce, crispy bacon, and well-cooked pasta. The garlic bread served alongside was a great addition, adding a nice crunch to the meal. The presentation was also spot-on, making the experience even more enjoyable.

I’ll definitely be coming back to try more of their menu. Highly recommend this spot for pasta lovers!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMaEK7fNQtkSFNPotrNYUgfjhfNSjiO8AvXjjsC&fid=0x0:0x6f3e2391bba5bfd9"],"When":"2024-8-25"},{"Name":"Mitch C.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUigQKnsqnd6-ECKxiWLF3yOJGPZULiTcrsHXswZ-6rjxY7_wxITQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Ordered breakfast. Both were overcooked. Accidents can happen 🤷 I specifically asked for soft scrambled eggs. The server repeated "scrambled"
I repeated *SOFT* scrambled. My friend ordered medium basted. They were full on hard cooked. Sausages were flavorless. Trouble is noone came back to check after food was delivered. The opportunity to fix it was there, but not attempted. Nice location in the industrial area along the river. Hope experience is not the normal one.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNU-Nn9IIeVfJMSqROBLEDHykrBkx6OEpeIFRRm&fid=0x0:0x6f3e2391bba5bfd9"],"When":"2024-8-27"},{"Name":"Ramesh Perera","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVyGA6fUD6Xdk_4LzEtJUlIgguhCdAdAHW5zHo_49OVhxbKNfQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently picked up Ronny's Bistro's homemade meat lasagna, shepherd's pie, and borscht, and I was happy with my purchase! The lasagna is rich and comforting, filled with a perfect blend of meats and cheeses, with a "sparkle of love" that you can truly taste. The shepherd's pie is hearty and flavorful, packed with tender beef and vegetables. To top it all off, the borscht was delicious and made my meal complete. Highly recommend Ronny's Bistro for anyone looking for quality homemade meals. Five stars all the way! I will come again for some more homemade frozen meals which are ready to eat or bake.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMt_LVJr_jvqfhe-y5mx7EM3w-uoORR9PRmPiBp&fid=0x0:0x6f3e2391bba5bfd9"],"When":"2024-9-4"},{"Name":"Vilma Yoder","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVCshCxnZzZyI6-eeQNlvQN0OkpVSmJm4fyuNm5pzhGp74l2Yk=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My husband and I were looking for a place to eat breakfast and found this cute restaurant. Inside they were playing wonderful music, then we noticed their homey decorations that made our experience pleasant. The food was out of this world delicious. I ordered the croissant and was fully satisfied after eating it. The dish came with fried potato cubes that were crunchy and perfectly seasoned.
Friendly staff, they were smiling from ear to ear and it made us feel welcomed.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOBO3tyyjhDNM1tNx859qD5jS1XXy9hIXtwRoU&fid=0x0:0x6f3e2391bba5bfd9"],"When":"2024-7-8"},{"Name":"Cheryl Kathler","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK9TQWPDmnOA_h-SxOo5p_UwYGe8FJqXXhmMfPn2eJzdkrxrQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My friend brought me here for lunch.  It is in an unassuming location, but as soon as you walk in, it feels very welcoming and fun.  The food was so fresh and tasty (right down to the homemade pesto).  The owner is very generous and friendly and in spite of being busy, we had a great conversation with her.  I will be back.  There is a lot on the menu that I want to try.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN9kTzAEXk3C5wUNJiWdqz0mBEPbELl4D8xE-wg&fid=0x0:0x6f3e2391bba5bfd9"],"When":"2024-6-29"},{"Name":"D S","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKuROdrsF7vogaT38uZexLigYz1e5VXiDiWb4Iq30REJ6CyNw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Outstanding food and great ambience. Casual and clean diner. Lots of HD and other motorcycle paraphernalia. Great for everyone including families. Their cheesecakes are to die for and are made on site, but only once a week...so plan accordingly as they sell out quickly. Clean washrooms and adequate space between tables. It's located in the Industrial part of Maple Ridge, but very easy to get to. This place was previously Summer's Diner and IMO, the food is much better now. It is easily some of the best food in Maple Ridge. The only thing that needs work is the time to receive your food. We have been there a few times in the last month and the service is slow. Once, it took 45 minutes to receive our food and the restaurant was not busy. It is still worth the visit though, so go when you're not in a rush. Highly recommended!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOtk_X-IZD8h_XnLaTeGdaOnNBH-YgSk-No4Vid&fid=0x0:0x6f3e2391bba5bfd9"],"When":"2024-5-26"},{"Name":"Udari Nisansala","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWI5wgDzbdl2O6sXNemlC6v7mOL_F2kJd_iqTO2aXvqKDlmspov=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I can't say enough good things about the Special Ronny's Burger at Ronny's Bistro! This burger is an absolute masterpiece. The beef patty was juicy and flavorful, topped with crispy bacon, fresh lettuce, and a perfectly balanced sauce that tied everything together. The bun was soft yet sturdy, holding all the delicious ingredients without falling apart.

The fries served on the side were golden and crispy, making this meal all the more satisfying. If you're a burger lover, this is a must-try. Five stars all the way!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNBvKBSnlZbJoXfkBEAcB7lA18EhUfIVup5SFaA&fid=0x0:0x6f3e2391bba5bfd9"],"When":"2024-8-25"},{"Name":"Saumya Siriwardhana","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXJ1IunhRfABP7fGLICHAl6HNIBzYnUAQpkceKd0QliRu_wwec=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had the Lasagna Bolognese at Ronny’s Bistro today, and it was absolutely incredible! The layers of pasta were perfectly cooked, the meat sauce was rich and flavorful, and the cheese was perfectly melted and golden. The portion was just right, and it came with a side of fresh Caesar salad and delicious toasted bread, which made the meal even more enjoyable. The menu has so many tempting options, and I’m already looking forward to coming back to try more dishes. Highly recommend this place if you’re looking for a memorable meal!!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOWKizfqDXJL0AdpuRTM2XNleCPoObL6bbEOOvz&fid=0x0:0x6f3e2391bba5bfd9"],"When":"2024-8-21"}]

[{"Name":"todd lazarenko","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXMWhJK6u9XNG2-gmnhPqFucz9pNeWhp5Mzp9oBrrbII94Vr5o9=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We go to Maple Ridge Keg about once every 2 or 3 months. The food has continued to be consistently good. We almost always sit at the bar as we can walk right in at just about anytime and get seats right away. From the Baked garlic shrimp and the wedge salad to the 12 ounce sirloin, it was all fantastic and we were stuffed. They even gave us a free birthday Billy Miner pie to go with a candle. Courtney was our server working behind the bar. She gave us absolutely flawless service. I am a Maple Ridge Keg alumni so I can certainly appreciate great service paired with great food. Now the Keg ain't cheap, with the 20% tip it was $242.00. I don't mind as we enjoy our meals there. Keep up the great job Courtney and Maple Ridge Keg.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNaACummdyJEVgGY0I39CTjR_UvRfRFIlSt65Y&fid=0x0:0x58172c4aab381a8c"],"When":"2024-10-15"},{"Name":"Dvir M","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUxK6vUXIZPF_mBYpyYRstLoQm3iHWCiUkMzdVCeCCrurOmcIbk=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We were celebrating my friend his birthday. We were 6 people. We had so much fun, we got the food at the same time no issues. Scotty was our server. Let’s put it this way, he knows his job very well. Let us feel super comfortable and made sure that we’re happy with everything at all time. Food was good. The wings with the chilli oil and the blue cheese omg.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPIggME2dZvlWZ9ueSj2a71MgvQVwhXFJbwXzln&fid=0x0:0x58172c4aab381a8c"],"When":"2024-12-13"},{"Name":"Star Forbes","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVX3bxa6epj-Pmj6Ysk7djR6GPyFN2Nb3oWlupv9ZY8ucFacX7F=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I love this Keg it's casual dining 3 steaks are always done right, and food tastes amazing. I had half Lob and steak it was very good meal. Great waiter named Declan, who helped us celebrate our  22nd anniversary dinner! Thanks for a memorable night, Keg!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPImFZO5frUVCDMLYyHWb04fRXCWc_vDNHAY5YM&fid=0x0:0x58172c4aab381a8c"],"When":"2024-9-5"},{"Name":"Olivia Leaf","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVzloLoDK6qGN7OOG3lV2DyC7b9nIFZQdd3rh1F80nxbwNaod8v=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had a wonderful night! They also managed to get me the rarest piece of prime rib possible, which was fabulous! We appreciated it, and will be back!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM0XPURyEP4MDPMGUIx0ZikzWqejuc_bua0wUFi&fid=0x0:0x58172c4aab381a8c"],"When":"2024-8-29"},{"Name":"S M","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLaVQBXA2LqzncrzyqIA7NUO-NlvmCIPf8x9w2beJYJtlvwkA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had an exceptional dining experience at The Keg, thanks to our waiter, Jarred. He was attentive, knowledgeable, and made excellent recommendations that elevated our meal. His friendly demeanor and prompt service ensured everything ran smoothly. Jarred truly went above and beyond, making us feel valued and well taken care of. I can't wait to return and hope to have him as our server again! Highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Megan Fraser","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVuqaxfaCnCiXPjlH1wGlkoULMBFXQYi7bRU5qpZ_0Tn5TVHIi3aw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It's been quite awhile since I've been to a Keg, and my first time at the Maple Ridge location. We were crazing a steak and wow they did not disappoint tonight! It melted in my mouth and was exactly what I was craving!! Loved the beets with green beans tonight as well, it's not often you get beets. Service was great and dinner was a beautiful night out!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Rayant Yeo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUaSGd8rGguK-MzK7O72I-ocdHyBHvKJG59MOmI710XLPYz1DeB_w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I must compliment the restaurant manager for going the extra mile in making us feel comfortable while waiting for our table. We made reservations for 8 pax at 730pm. However, our table was taking a bit longer than usual. So, the restaurant manager offered us complimentary drinks and appetizers while waiting for our table.

Food at The Keg never disappoints; delicious & fresh; especially the lobster and salmon.

Thank you for your Great Service!! 👏🏼👏🏼","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN_djeCr3xBpMuJZMvMITSpE8XqVIlWMv4zn0iM&fid=0x0:0x58172c4aab381a8c"],"When":"2023-12-22"},{"Name":"Arthur Pangilinan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVGrMo8Q0uYkleyMEXyLc0uVJCPhvFTuVKvzIq5qSp-cV9pow=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had a fantastic experience with Andrew at The Keg! He was attentive, funny, and kind, making us feel well taken care of. As long-time patrons of The Keg, this was our first time learning about the Keg Classic meal, which included everything we normally order separately. It truly blew our minds—we’ve been missing out on this better deal for years! Also made us feel comfortable bringing our newborn with us on our first ever date. We never felt out of place with the stroller and all! Thank you for being awesome, Andrew and team! We’ll definitely be back to this location.","Images":null,"When":""}]

If you visit, I highly recommend adding the wonton soup to your meal. It’s flavorful, comforting, and just what you need to chase the cold away. Definitely a must-try!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNhgvzHj2ye3DGttkL9R7mMcn6m62Ios8jku93p&fid=0x0:0x59611bc8262fc104"],"When":"2024-11-28"},{"Name":"Brianna Kim","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJCxjGqq-S1P9AXC3kyzrcipFbDfAa10QiVhewDcELC-y7EHg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"If you haven’t tried this spot, you’re seriously missing out. All the servers were so kind and the food was amazing, especially the pulled pork skillet!
Also tried their hand made wonton soup and you can definitely taste the difference that the wontons are hand made, super juicy and tender.
It’s definitely my new go-to brunch spot, and I can’t wait to come back!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipORs1c74i358tM_45WF0Sdw4vTE8jO7oYh1JYLG&fid=0x0:0x59611bc8262fc104"],"When":"2024-10-20"},{"Name":"Willow kehler","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWrGyM4Cox8sgLgFo2GdYuDP6ylhpy80buz1nGPvDlIYwB5ju7P=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Had a good lunch! Beef bulgogi skillet was amazing! Wish there was a few more iced coffee options","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNlPrDoKV5U4ezighE12rKFhPmc5AU4QtFtL6Ua&fid=0x0:0x59611bc8262fc104"],"When":"2024-10-14"},{"Name":"Clara Shin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK8r3qq6Ia1p9jreBiNgO6aoNhyUS6wr0640Ek21mGJv2Pi2Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I usually avoid eating meat when dining out because I am very sensitive to smells. Many restaurants seem to use lower-quality meat, which often has an unpleasant odor. However, I was pleasantly surprised when my friend ordered wontons here, and I decided to try one. They were absolutely delicious! I was told they are handmade, which explains the exceptional taste. I liked them so much that I ordered takeout to enjoy at home. I was also impressed that the packaging they use is made from safe materials without harmful chemicals.

Although it’s a bit far from where I live, I would love to come back often. This place serves incredibly delicious and healthy food. Highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"shashi kunwar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUzBMRxLk_KtTH24JWx0H4EXhP5GNOYpsNCyvkx8jxQxDr-XdCh=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"One of the best spots for authentic Nepali cuisine! The flavors are truly exceptional—every bite is a delight. I highly recommend the Butter Chicken Momos; they’re an absolute must-try. Can’t wait to visit again!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNd4cdi0J5JNjOmLj2xdChHH1PUKpkprV6hw1Mu&fid=0x0:0x58cb2544af0eee2c"],"When":"2024-11-27"},{"Name":"Nihit Malhotra","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXfeHWYeDGkDTZNd33AgDsCmLoJ4NSwzG1vpopgAV9OU-hgspcS7Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We’ve visited Mt Everest 8848 twice in the past few months, and both experiences were great overall. The butter chicken momos are an absolute must-try—the gravy is rich and delicious! Chilli momos were also a hit, and the tava chicken had amazing flavor, though the texture was slightly tough on the outside.

On our second visit, we loved the butter chicken momos again and tried the BBQ chicken momos, which didn’t impress us as much. However, the house special chow mein (with chicken, prawns, and egg) were a pleasant surprise—even as someone who doesn’t usually enjoy saucy noodles, I loved them.

The portions are generous, and the staff is very polite and friendly. Definitely recommend this place, especially for the butter chicken momos!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNlgMPWOgCbrMmbit3iaDeDGOSPeyBSquv7838s&fid=0x0:0x58cb2544af0eee2c"],"When":"2024-11-24"},{"Name":"ᇫ","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXlngfQVtGilUz62ScjKSTnwc5UnbrCxqB5h7iWhaVLUWtSTDz7=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Really really good food with very wonderful service, I'll be back to eat here forsure

Edit: I came back the day after and had one of the best meals ever, id recommend coming during lunch time to get the special. The butter chicken momo is out of this world, and if you get a chao mein with it you'll have enough food to feed a family of 4. You will not regret coming here, thank you rajeeb and laxman for the wonderful food. I really appreciate it!
Also the Nepali masala tea is great id get that","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPz3m_t6WJloCn3SAkoIIXsXA1arL4bU82VgU7K&fid=0x0:0x58cb2544af0eee2c"],"When":"2024-10-9"},{"Name":"Adam Tamer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUVReOi9kwYutOGqTk6O5XbycBVvDD5p1KuBhAqqEnPU5K6fel1=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"After a hike in MR, we were looking for a later dinner. Upon seeing the reviews we decided to try this place.

So glad we did! The service was incredible! So kind, helpful and fast.

Decided to try the Butter Chicken and the Chilli Chicken Momo based on the reviews. Both were out of this world! Best Butter Chicken sauce I’ve ever had.

Can’t wait to come back and try more things.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMThzhwQSyKTcGz6gqnGoPg-y0Lbv5M22Or1bg6&fid=0x0:0x58cb2544af0eee2c"],"When":"2024-7-14"},{"Name":"Aliz A","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUCLUVCARWUQzG9kwVMKWfiRsIBhLU_6JMuFFZXwEGUC6rYLLEo7A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Ordered uber from this Nepalese-Indian fusion restaurant, been wanting to try this place and it did not disappoint in flavours!

What I got:
- House Special ChowMein (Recommend)
- Veggie spring rolls, Nepali Style (Recommend)

Both dishes I highly recommend, even though I got take out. The spring rolls still had a bit of crunch, they serve it with a sweet chilli sauce. The veggie spring rolls are on the small side but flavours were great, has like a cumin/all spice type of note. The ChowMein was delicious!! If you love indo/Chinese flavours, this comes close to comparing flavours but this noodle dish is spice with everything nice!

Overall, I’d come back to try other dishes. Thank you!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOdBX49x9AfR7MwNOQK861a_yG1gjLRJE_uSGwI&fid=0x0:0x58cb2544af0eee2c"],"When":"2024-11-29"},{"Name":"Iceyplz","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVzXvKjm8e3vwcZLs5lgD6pZTy1hqvhaCDXCRR_gSyIwonhGwbW=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The best momos in town, hands down! The jhol momo is a must-try, especially on a chilly day – it’s the perfect comfort food. The flavorful broth and tender dumplings make for an unbeatable combination. Every bite is packed with authentic taste and warmth. Highly recommend for anyone looking to indulge in delicious, hearty food. This place is a gem!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPCx5YrH-CC6xuD7YqwfsJycoGWzlfTkZChmHe9&fid=0x0:0x58cb2544af0eee2c"],"When":"2024-9-29"},{"Name":"Avantika kumar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWQjFEbM5JO-aYhmaM9SNeCkg0qehBTc5xq5CTV2hkJZDSTKT_K=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"They are such nice genuine people working here. There was a mix up with the food but they gave us 2 entire dishes to make up for that. Not only the sweetest people but the most delicious food. The best Nepali restaurant we’ve tried in all years in the lower mainland. Definitely a wonderful neighborhood restaurant to support. They’ve earned us as regulars","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nathan Chang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjULis9x-C7u8jouJ6bmV-m7Mb2r-esn5uJaOqGwjwAA9z2MADUV=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This was quite the culinary experience. The momo’s were warm and delicious. The flavour was clearly there and we had some to take home as they were really filling.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMXwoo06FufiPmRM945mtaOx8hlrcogx40JvBhv&fid=0x0:0x58cb2544af0eee2c"],"When":"2024-9-26"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Max Luo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJOIlU5nJBhhMt4LhC3zOj5-erzOKLJv2GOSpcFK4XvUCtyZQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"With stellar ratings of 4.9 in Surrey and 4.6 in Maple Ridge on Google Reviews, I decided to give this highly praised Indian restaurant a shot—and it didn’t disappoint.

From the moment you step inside, it feels like you’ve been transported to India. The ambiance is authentic and immersive, making the experience even more special. Following the waitress’s recommendations, we ordered their signature Lamb Korma paired with the famous Garlic Naan, as well as the classic Butter Chicken served with Fries.

The flavors were rich and aromatic, exceeding my expectations. The Lamb Korma had an incredible depth of spices, while the Butter Chicken was a perfect blend of creamy and tangy flavors. Every bite was flavorful and satisfying, making it easy to see why this place has such high ratings.

Would I come back? Absolutely! For anyone who loves curry or is curious about Indian cuisine, USTAADJ 76 is worth every visit.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOuhE4PDtYS7uE0jxMzxCeKTR_v2nxsq6C4J1w4&fid=0x0:0x6ccf4a3eef0094e4"],"When":"2024-12-2"},{"Name":"Harjot Singh Thiara","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUzOWwYq4K3U1PHL-O7BVjU4O_407b0Owm7Wzd6z3KttiPqwyct=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Hi all, I would like to explain my recent visit to Ustad G76, We were group of eight, and I must say, it was an exceptional experience. We ordered $150 worth of food, and every single item was spot on—delicious and perfectly prepared. I was particularly impressed by our server, Shagal, who must have a photographic memory. She effortlessly memorized each member's order and the necessary amendments, ensuring that everything came out exactly as we requested.

A big thanks to Chef Harjap, who did an amazing job in the kitchen and truly made our day special. We enjoyed a delightful spread that included Kadai Paneer, Chana Bhatura, Pav Bhaji, two Veg Thalis, Veg Noodles, Paneer Malai Tikka, and dessert. The portion sizes were generous, far better than what you often find at other restaurants, where you might feel shortchanged.

During the meal, we all sampled each other's food and were consistently amazed by the flavours. I wholeheartedly recommend this restaurant to everyone—it’s truly great! A final shout-out to the restaurant owner for assembling such a brilliant team.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNfxj_Kb--lPZA12v6wUlKAUF_cGWY8Y8fVp4EX&fid=0x0:0x6ccf4a3eef0094e4"],"When":"2024-10-1"},{"Name":"Just B","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXbqlkGphBGO4ZFtnvvHRFErtzljMxdFcSC7D5K0agOlbgekAWrBA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Mmm so good. Every dish that I have tried here is absolutely delicious. The atmosphere in the restaurant is comfortable, inviting and Shagal is very kind, knowledgeable and friendly. I highly recommend that you give them a try, you will not be disappointed.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMkf_qtas4_paxsJhu4aG1Tj0TwVKTUurFLGvEJ&fid=0x0:0x6ccf4a3eef0094e4"],"When":"2024-8-30"},{"Name":"Anju Garg","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJs_C0AyLXyV9zsoE79mnQhwb9-QfkUY_7BK5NfmZm6p2l9LQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"we ordered dal makhni and we got chicken tadka free. despite being vegetarian for whole life and first meal after karwachauth and you found meat in ur meal. thing which i wasnt expecting. it was really sad and annoying. feel like throwing out. not going to order again 🙏","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMDiVtzx27KpOEb2nabatOfuHBL2gRh-QFtj5TC&fid=0x0:0x6ccf4a3eef0094e4"],"When":"2024-10-20"},{"Name":"Elaine Payne","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLi-cZ79vVwFEPuZ0jB7xl3YujoVxBK2BTnin4mf8s3bdVAog=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"First time at this little place and we will return. The server didn't greet us when we came in so I wasn't sure how it'd be but once she came to take our orders, she was friendly and very helpful.
We have had takeout from another Indian restaurant in town monthly for about 20 years and this is just as good but different than what we're used to.
I can't remember the names of 3 dishes but the butter chicken was tender and delicious, the rice had peas in it and we loved it and we had mango lassis which were very filling but so yummy and the garlic Naan was also so good.

The location isn't great so I think it gets overlooked but I hope people check it out because it's worth it.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mike White","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWxVYwdZXdW6rHD5JUMV8cij2U9tyTjkBrWNk2tBFvnLkXd-3w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Wow wow. Very good food. Great portions perfect amount of spice.The service was amazing.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOk6xzAZ0DY_P6siuZlOyews4hyrjh6MWbL6GNn&fid=0x0:0x6ccf4a3eef0094e4"],"When":"2024-8-31"},{"Name":"Shalini Sehgal","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK_xKGlI9Px4AT2Uw-lnQWBNnj60Kyr16zcfO4UtHOgSeYIb_Iu=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Amritsari Kulcha was not at all delectable as desired. Didn't have enough flavor,  some more dash of spices, butter and chutney required. Not happy the way it was served and platted. Spoon was placed on the table with just one napkin (no paper mats/plate... Straight onto the table)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN-rhMxYdTDHRqUmVKyV8n1Mg_mb3yl4OrWNBEK&fid=0x0:0x6ccf4a3eef0094e4"],"When":"2024-2-19"},{"Name":"Jennifer Osborne","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXGAFIwFtDqyI8D36gZAiSDBU2XmVs34SHaebe4yPZ1-D2Xa3xc=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This place has amazing food and the decor is fun. Great music, good service, I came back two times in a week when I was working in Maple Ridge. [{"Name":"rashad preet","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI7l1E9Yl-cEPNvtQlKi4BreGC2j7rGjpmIdtPwIF2S7ekAMw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":""Sunfire Pizzeria is a fantastic spot for anyone craving delicious pizza and a great atmosphere! The cozy, modern interior, with its warm lighting and unique decor featuring wooden pizza paddles, creates a welcoming and stylish vibe. The pizzas are truly top-notch, featuring perfectly baked crusts and generous, flavorful toppings. Whether you're a fan of BBQ, pepperoni, or something unique, there’s something to satisfy every craving.

What makes it even better is that they serve IP beers and pitchers, offering the perfect pairing for their incredible pizzas. The staff is always friendly, attentive, and quick to make sure your experience is seamless. Whether you're stopping by for a casual hangout, a quick lunch, or a laid-back evening with friends, Sunfire Pizzeria is the place to be. Highly recommend giving it a try—you’ll keep coming back for more!"","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOCzGbc3-cgOYzD83_1egxMVueMK1fp6gBqUC3z&fid=0x0:0x390308853b054c33"],"When":"2024-11-14"},{"Name":"funinbc01","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVNuK8goS9LTbcAK-83ltMtkrpeV3KdlWUEm7KeXqEETYn9CeI=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"The ablute worst pizza I have ever eaten! Best pizza  in maple ridge","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN9LceXBOh7qnfnTbCkTml-Hg6VpujZIspmEsle&fid=0x0:0x390308853b054c33"],"When":"2024-9-19"},{"Name":"Shawn Yang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLBtmJkH_7NwsaHdVxpMp8J8SdREbfUwW9YdCV0UXHcSRrfKw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing experience, staff was so so nice and was provided sauces for us on the house. Staff striked up conversation with us and made us feel very welcomed. Pizza was amazing as well! Prices were great.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPBcwSVxVmLOzAyatez1yrs84I3WarkoirD-8L7&fid=0x0:0x390308853b054c33"],"When":"2024-12-1"},{"Name":"Dev Deteriorate","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW174d3q1C68k3CIpTb3Y2mjhbzxdBX3351-dOCoOvMShWcsYWq=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Sunfire Pizzeria holds a standard of excellence that is executed through simplicity, fresh ingredients, and love of the pizza game.

You get the classics here. Prosciutto, real pepperoni, basil, and the structural integrity of the pizza is to die for, a crispy thin slice that you can give the traditional fold to.

There’s really something for everyone here, lots of traditional meats to explore and refreshing vegetarian options.

I also have to give highest praise to their garlic dip. I’m from Windsor which is not only known for their pizza but the garlic dip that comes with it and this is the closest i’ve found to something as good, if not on par. If you’re ordering from Sunfire I promise you, order some extra cups of it!

I have nothing but love for this place and their employees, I work delivery gigs on the side and they’re always so happy to see their customers when I come in to grab an order.

If you haven’t given them a shot yet, this is your sign.

Sunfire forever ❤️","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOlqu8_HX-PMKLd4_kXpZR-sXVaSF1K4M1ZE2DC&fid=0x0:0x390308853b054c33"],"When":"2024-8-12"},{"Name":"Ignacio Villalba","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU27mCvoX7yWI8W90PNknNcH_GKVViWKlcqOsZqJuCx7EqEabQUww=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My wife and I visited the place yesterday after ordering online two times previously. We love the pizzas there. The homemade thin crust and the ingredients they use are simply delicious and hard to beat. The service is top notch as well. The manager even gave us some house sauce to try with our pizza for free. I am recommending this place all the time to friends. 5 stars.","Images":null,"When":""}]
