Started off with a platter of appetizers (calamari and bruschettas), followed by a trio of pastas and a tangy balsamic vinaigrette salad that led to a surf n turf entree of grilled lamb, chicken, prawn with veggies and ending with a classic tiramisu with an an apricot purée twist ! 😋🤤

Everything was very well seasoned and delicious! I’ve lived in maple ridge my whole life and for some reason I never thought to visit this restaurant lol. Now that I’ve moved to Burnaby, I’ll have to make an effort to visit here again the next time I venture back to MR

The wait time between each dish was a bit long, our entire meal took 3 hrs so one star off for that. Also we told our server we wanted to take home our leftovers but he forgot to pack them up and we forgot to ask about it as we left, would’ve been nice as we had a bit leftover that we would’ve love to finish off the next day 😫😩🥺😢

Overall, a great experience at a MR landmark!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMZyBUqJhLBogabhczvMG80XMVsMmzzejGR53ew&fid=0x0:0xb59e691906a3e81d"],"When":"2022-12-19"},{"Name":"Jamak Golshani","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWUj2LK0XJaxGCkMdV1Y3vwaPy3axo29-O-pu7Kb7eqy9PgvRrN=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Giving four stars because we had to wait an unreasonable amount of time to be served. Consistent experience.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOrTGcGpIaHafbWmiJ476Uus-gblmqmGZkgVZV8&fid=0x0:0xb59e691906a3e81d"],"When":"2022-6-12"},{"Name":"Naser","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU0-YQ8zU5RxMjX7Szhrzpzf3k8mT3TPmCIoVpC7Yu8SS5YsZfI=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great night with my wife here. Soup was sooo good, sea food and desert was amazing. the old gentleman serving us was really nice and can definitely rate him as one of the best staff l have ever seen in a restaurant. Despite the great tasty food, his warm greeting, and checking several times if we need anything , made a great night for us . Environment was kind of cool and the Italian music was so relaxing. Especially the God father one😊
In general it is one of my great food experience  in Maple Ridge.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN2_xT7TfKSry-koe59CCKkYJTWoDH93RtmBU2c&fid=0x0:0xb59e691906a3e81d"],"When":"2022-3-15"},{"Name":"Maya Schouten","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUO9x8oFl1z-2ncMLmfWu71Y053fpa-t4BYxDTv_0_AzOsAsA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I can’t say enough good things about Trattoria restaurant.  The service was warm, friendly and welcoming.  They placed the napkins in our lap and brought out focaccia bread and oil which was lovely.  We ordered the calamari as an appetizer and the batter was perfect, seasoning spot on, and the dipping sauce was divine (I think homemade). The main course was phenomenal.  I ordered the Gnocchi Russa and couldn’t have made a better selection. The gnocchi was perfectly tender, and the sauce was the ideal balance of cream and tomato. I will most definitely return.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMcx_hFxwOqG_odHOXyvVCMl74XJTcwW7XuSyI&fid=0x0:0xb59e691906a3e81d"],"When":"2019-5-25"},{"Name":"Lorene Stuart","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJXqnmzUHq9uX8JdgxKRCwjZLhEDZiMKRm3pIucQxFcArTvdg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Service was welcoming, friendly, & timely.

user_reviews: [{"Name":"Elizabeth A","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVxfTEWSeX8uYXtcmqTBPDV_ujOByqiofeonLevJdviVTPcCUc=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Wings were pretty decent. Service was pretty slow and we had to get up to find the waitress for the bill, but it was busy. What was confusing was that I ordered a Sapporo and got a dark coloured beer instead. Not too sure what it was (it wasn't a Guinness), but it supposedly came out of the Sapporo tap. Thankfully it wasn't a huge deal because my second choice was a Guinness or another dark-coloured beer.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOyTtusXiGeOLST3ayqZvn8rb6MeciAaKveEonG\u0026fid=0x0:0x7b858298d0c2e331"],"When":"2024-12-20"},{"Name":"Madison Bailey","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKg_8c4BJ7CfR7Pr54kKUbOvdzzGbRH5vrwUWxRQnSSGOfk2w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"My husband and I went over here for Wing Wednesday and to watch the hockey game the other night. The wings were fine, but the service absolutely tanked. It was a louder night, but not over all super busy. We were sat for over 30 minutes before seeing a waitress, she finally took our drink order and didn’t come back for another 25. If we had seen her running around the restaurant, we would’ve been more inclined to be more patient, as we understand things get busy. She passed us several times, each time without our drinks which could’ve easily been placed on her tray and dropped off. She’d run past our table, tap it and say she was grabbing whatever we had asked for or to take our order, but would take nearly 30 minutes each time to come back. We saw her maybe 3 times, and what should’ve been a quick in and out for some wings, we were there almost 3 hours, had only 1 drink refill and nothing else, never asked us if we needed anything, and you couldn’t catch her otherwise. Also, they cease to mention that pop refills are not free on Wednesdays, which seems like a scam to get you in the end. While it’s just pop, I understand, be upfront with customers so they can decide what they want to do with that information. It wasn’t until we asked for the bill (3 different times) that she finally came and had a second to stop and chat, to which she instantly brought up her children and Christmas coming, which to us felt like tip baiting. Terrible experience, which tanks because the atmosphere seemed like it could be fun, and the food (wings at least) wasn’t bad.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"John","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWw5rMQatibni75tbNpjJbP4ehPrGlbmCLKvcJ6Naf176pomyyjJw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have never been to \"The Reach\" before. I simply popped in as I was early to visit friends in the area. It was 3:30 on a Friday afternoon before the Christmas week ahead. The place was packed, filled with people smiling, laughing, and having fun. I didn't order any food. The people and staff were super friendly, and the price on my favorite craft brew was an amazing $4!!! Plenty of TVs for the sports enthusiasts and KENO as well.\n\nI'll Be Back!! See you there? 😉","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"claudio quinones","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL6KyrjNGdxf2c2scfa5GSK3lpFjNu_-VlN0L2IvDo98alq-A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I find the service was unsatisfactory. After we paid for our first order with the first attendant which she said she was off. I order for a last beer. The next attendant twice came tonight to our table asking if we were done even she saw my glass was still full. We said we’re still ok. Then left and says “ oh G with other costumer”. Felt insulted its just because i ordered with her  just 1 beer and she keeps on coming back if we were done? We were there to relax after a long hour work in the hospital. It was incredibly flavorful, and the promos make it an even better deal, sometimes saving you nearly half the price. The store was also exceptionally clean, which added to the overall experience. Plus, the location is perfect—just a short walk from the bus loop and close to the park.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPP4JTz-O4Bq1-kUZtMCLKhRw2TEbWNWsavfR8a&fid=0x0:0x6b998b5d4e4999ca"],"When":"2024-8-24"},{"Name":"M. Petr","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW4z89Me6qOaraIDGghLnCpRJmrntMOdBCRhpnTB7C9G1NxtXc=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Super friendly and helpful staff and great food. Caution on the extras-they can up.
Just like homemade but I didn’t have to make it.
They are new in Maple Ridge and definitely worth checking out.
Poke done right!!

Edit:
SPB is a regular stop for us now when we head out for the evening. We can always count on them for fast yet healthy options when on the run. Sometimes we forget to recognize another reason we continue to return: The Staff!
We enjoyed our dinner there tonight, in fact. We just wanted to take the time to let folks know hat the young person working there tonight, Luke, provided us with exceptional service. He is professional and personable. We know the service industry can be challenging and it's way too easy to post when dissatisfied. Experiences like the one we had tonight, however, are what will keep us coming back to Steve's Poke Bar!!.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPzX3RyTVhDyDnaBA9C-HOqVspfa8y1PPgoCaSw&fid=0x0:0x6b998b5d4e4999ca"],"When":"2023-5-3"},{"Name":"Marie craig","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKJ-y4s9oFXK1qOEM2dzdHMCrPCzjet0vfqdlo_WPphrIrEw8g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Music is upbeat  but not ridiculously loud. A hidden gem, it wasn’t busy at all on a Friday evening which I was surprised. The food was delicious (Greek salad the best I’ve had) the Greek style ribs were tender (lacking salt, but once I added salt it was really yummy) over all I would recommend!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPhGgjYPib05tBlTwUJIY3txFEcyYAMcyS11TmP&fid=0x0:0xc7f0e74e24c00bc0"],"When":"2024-12-14"},{"Name":"Alvaro ADA","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWHfR0wv7SAbPUpdi8lH7IrK4oJU5U7YtQ6w224hdNUnfPXA7lg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We enjoyed the attention and the food. The waiter was very polite and try to make us feel at home. Food was serve shortly after ordering with a good portion presentation and warm. Taste: I can just say, my son and wife love it! That should say enough. When finish we were offer desert but food took its toll with us. Finally, I highly recommended for your lunch or dinner meals.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Iman Rahmaty","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ4fZOqYHX8glodHVRySbk9_tWVDRu59jLTmQrTwItu0Etgfw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My wife and I had an incredible experience at Socrates. The atmosphere was perfect—warm, inviting, and just the right mix of elegant and comfortable.

The food was fantastic, with fresh ingredients, rich flavors, and beautifully plated dishes. Every bite was memorable, and both of our meals were absolutely delicious.

The service was top-notch. Our server was friendly, attentive, and made great recommendations, adding a personal touch to the night.

Socrates is a true gem where everything comes together—amazing food, great service, and a cozy ambiance. We can’t wait to return! Highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Victor Safonov","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVH7q93d1K9tn9Dnmg-HYEGcil6kwKd6Jh5GVCelXsB2yHcMtq3=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"We had a family dinner at this restaurant. We ordered several different dishes. Overall, the food was delicious. The atmosphere is nice and not loud. Service is good. Unpleasant surprise at the end of the evening - they automatically add a 20% tip for a group of 6 or more. I have no problem with tipping, but in this case I feel like someone is just reaching into my wallet without asking. At the entrance to the restaurant we noticed a lot of people taking take out. We won't go there again.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tristan Bosnjak","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV5dDkomF66OX55DVF0cecHSvIVXQw82_r6Nj7yxfmIxBJx-Vo=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great service and a super friendly atmosphere. I had the Lamb shoulder and the taste took me back to my grandmother's house when I was young. Great meal and great restaurant. Highly recommend for Greek food.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Leah C","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKSvkg4jot2o9e-I5XPpyMexBrtiq8sg9MIK4yISu3_L0cYww=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Server Julia was an absolute quality, professional server with an enchanting disposition

Owner was especially accommodating and displayed a professional disposition. This was my second visit and continue to be impressed with appetizer and dinner options","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jaeda Okell","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVWIW6EvO7vOUAEpF7_qb1mhH2RhcyN5niBvAHaJp-fAp3B6mY=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Me and my boyfriend went out for my 23rd birthday and I had an amazing experience! Our waitress Yasmin was very good specially because it was her first day, and I had no complaints:)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNcv_FSz1mYv8BCJBk3JVxx_ZmUGCN-ew2s09vh&fid=0x0:0xc7f0e74e24c00bc0"],"When":"2024-4-30"},{"Name":"Street Hazard","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjURFbIXZgFohAMrMR_ZDnInasbkLj2VtqII5gRfvJ8LxVhZgb_sCQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"The food wasn’t horrible but it’s definitely just an bad attempt at real Greek cuisine
Start off with the fact that the “Greek salad” was hardly edible due to the HUGE cuts of the tomato’s and cucumbers, then is topped with some “in house dressing” that goes horribly with it and isn’t even a attempt at Greek salad dressing which I find amusing
Secondly I’m not sure why they put raw onions with the calamari?? Never seen that before
Additionally the lamb rice and potatoes weren’t bad, potatoes reminded me of home and the lamb was well cooked and so was the rice
Lastly the service was not bad but I was the only person in the whole restaurant so can’t definitively say service was amazing and quite disappointed when I said happy Easter weekend to her and got a weird look and no response (Easter is tomorrow)
Wouldn’t recommend to someone looking for authentic Greek food","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNuXXvnRJHIazc5_yObsm_IcRiJFoMsoSaWosUQ&fid=0x0:0xc7f0e74e24c00bc0"],"When":"2024-5-5"}]

It's a big portion and deliciously filling. I am intrigued by how chewy and crispy their batter is and the rose sauce is liquid gold. Thank you so much for offering a huge vegan menu, at reasonable prices, great portions, and, most importantly, real TASTY food. ❤️

Please keep in mind that the wait times for orders tend to be longer than usual, but it's definitely worth the wait! Though you don't have to wait too long just to eat - everyone gets a complimentary focaccia bread with balsamic olive oil upon arrival - such a thoughtful touch!

Nicely renovated. Feels cozy and intimate. Recommend as a cute hangout or date night spot.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMnOeiViBP6UwxhFQoQczZcPFmfkCRL-hD02Eo&fid=0x0:0xafa5e197af61323e"],"When":"2024-1-27"},{"Name":"Ryan Bates","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIvbi-lOAKVp_EI635G5lV9rkUZeqJmkIg2yjkrD54pM5BPfA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Party of 2, we walked in, after a few seconds, the employee with bright dyed hair told us to sit anywhere, but every correctly sized table was covered in dirty dishes, so we sat at a large table. then were told to sit at a small one (understandable if on its own). We then sat at a small dirty table, that was sprayed while we sat there and not wiped down fully. We were then asked if we are vegan or not, we said vegetarian, and the employee flatly asked us again if we are vegan or not. We said no, vegetarian. We were given meat menus, then waited a while and heard this employee lightly argue and correct a customer on the phone, then did the same to the couple that walked in after us. Thankfully those customers corrected her arrogance to ensure they get the right food with their dietary restrictions. We then asked for the vegan menu and got a snappy “oh you want vegan now?” Then received a very dirty vegan menu.

I work customer service, so normally I don’t really mind if someone is having an off day. But this was far past that. First time I’ve ever walked out of a restaurant. uncomfortable unwelcoming, unclean place.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jayne Wright","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUms7PcN3Vy1M-xxhw_bkbo3QTmP5q-g8ISEeKG_LRu_HHeOy0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Lovely atmosphere. Paliottis vegan menu is really extensive with lots of choices! I had the crispy rice balls (similar to arancini) and Cajun vegan chicken penne. So delicious, I look forward to going back and trying the fettuccini cashew Alfredo!
I’m visiting town and they let my party stay and chat for a long time, they were very accommodating and great drinks menu.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM3ogMnJEuPE0xdowksSNGWfHNZ78NcmFA2ptkH&fid=0x0:0xafa5e197af61323e"],"When":"2024-2-22"},{"Name":"T Dang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXMSEwMA3m2f2pUNvDSD01evNvY5ImU08gKtdPmCpcdgJy2LmVY=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Service was impeccable. Very cute little restaurant with lots and lots of options including vegan options. I also love restaurants with a kids menu. That’s a plus. Only reason they didn’t get a full 5 for me was the spaghetti noodles were a little over done. I prefer al dente but the sauce and bread was really good.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMNKWDW06SyebUNwpuPwO119ro5p_lgjPBGnj3a&fid=0x0:0xafa5e197af61323e"],"When":"2024-4-13"},{"Name":"Babeth","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWf4WovMQFERSvhxzEoCuuSb4_AjZcTnpLowA2HY_C3jDQ0LV66=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"We were totally disappointed when we ate here. We waited almost an hour— if not for the free bread—we would have been so hungry and have left the place. It wasn’t even full (3 other tables), but we had to wait a long time; only one waitress who was doing everything from reservation, seating, serving, etc. She tried her best though. Flies were everywhere, food was not great as expected with all the “good” reviews. Too pricey for the order, steak was medium rare but it was too chewy. Mashed potatoes too salty. Waitress said they’re closing in a few weeks. Even so, they should have at least ended well as read on reviews.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Thomas Lovey","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ_sxu-gJcM6Bn62duXbg1cuPha8c77oPsgPbYDcIR07FvhTw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"tried this place tonight and It was an amazing experience start to finish. the customer service was incredible, and we shared some great conversation with our server. the pre meal bread was soft, christ p on the outside and had a nice garlicy flavour, the portions were enormous and filling, the carbonara was some of the best i've ever had with a perfect smooth texture with well blended flavours, and the vegan cheesecake was incredibly creamy and the coconut flavor was suble and not overwhelming at all like it often is in other places. the only complaint I have was that i'm not a fan of the gluten free crust texture, but the flavour was still quite good. the experience was amazing and I will be reccomending this place to anyone with ears 5/5 stars well earned!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNkquxSw3IiHVUwDqxtYBBEx9hepLAU2EJ7scp5&fid=0x0:0xafa5e197af61323e"],"When":"2023-2-12"},{"Name":"Espartaco Gonzalez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJQvqC7CHvoOBhM7UyOXHX4wB1JILNV3X-lgettj-tkSlS61g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"10/10 for vegans!!
We ordered the vegan pizza rolls, the vegan chicken marinara and the vegan spaghettini carbonara, thinking we were going to get Vancouver sized portions...

We were such fools! The food portions are huge and absolutely delicious.

The amount of vegan options is staggering, there are more options here than in any other vegan restaurant in Vancouver!

From the complimentary bread to the wait staff this place is definitely worth the drive if you are from out of town!

Edit: the vegan chocolate caramel pecan cheesecake is breathtaking ❤️","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNuDH6sKqx8mmaiMkBlEuMWvXeUbXN-hAvMYzLF&fid=0x0:0xafa5e197af61323e"],"When":"2023-12-28"}]

Meat was properly seasoned and very tender. Price is very reasonable and the flavour was outstanding!!! I didn’t have to add salt and pepper as the dish was perfectly seasoned, and it wasn’t greasy at all. Located in Meadow Ridge Shopping Centre, easy to find and very accessible to both Lougheed Highway & 207 Street or Dewdney Trunk Road & 207 Street. A hidden gem if you’re craving for authentic and flavourful Indian food.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMyfD5OT3HPfceWcdC3NC1_-uWwZ70n_fREjec&fid=0x0:0x5dc3122565fa06d5"],"When":"2024-10-28"},{"Name":"J T","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLXEjN5JGe3Mrw7txzZNbJPQzEJpLs8Rpa82nsQC7v0x9esng=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"HANDS DOWN , the best Indian food in Maple Ridge !!
Food is always fresh, DELICIOUS ( so much flavour!!!) and their prices are the best in town. We have been ordering from them for YEARS ( I can't believe this is the first time I'm writing a review :(
My partner and I stopped in for lunch last weekend and the service and atmosphere was lovely - not to mention we were both stuffed for $20 ( plus a good tip of course :) !!!
The server was GENUINELY pleased to hear that we loved the food - it's nice to see an establishment take pride in serving nothing but the best quality and taste  ( this rarely happens anymore).

I was also pleasantly surprised at their inexpensive lunch special prices !  ( although I shouldn't be surprised as they have excellent prices for all their menu items).
If you haven't tried their food and are a fan of Indian Cuisine, you must check them out!
You won't be disappointed.
Maple Leaf is truly a hidden gem !","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jaydeep Patel","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWBXLByJSfdj2nIcvUyl_WMvvevCVtJDF5tLCYak7E_L25sxLA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Maple Leaf Indian Cuisine in Maple Ridge is a hidden gem for anyone craving authentic Indian flavors. On top of the amazing food, the service is top-notch. I’d especially like to commend Rushi Patel for providing exceptional service. Their attention to detail and friendly demeanor made our dining experience even more enjoyable.

Highly recommend this place for anyone looking for quality Indian cuisine and excellent service!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"GURNOOR DHALIWAL","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUyrwXokaVNx8XD-mGLglp7fNN6Y-6xMUXfgN_AE1q_FhLUVtA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"a week ago

[{"Name":"keira r","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLJrKHZ2A5kiDlS4xDR-NV_HhOc8W11pUwvzgPGNuDoF9uE2Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"A guy at the restaurant, about 5’8, grey short hair, and short beard is EXTREMELY rude. My boyfriend and I went into the restaurant to see our other friends that were there. My boyfriend had broken his leg about two and a half months ago, causing him to still have a limp while walking. The “bouncer” told him he was not allowed in and said to him “you sure you want to come in buddy.” This was because of how he was walking, due to still having a limp, and after explaining the broken leg situation he continues to say “well that’s too bad.” Extremely rude, 0 customer service skills, overall a horrible human being.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Liam Bassetto","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI7Wc94he_Fv9ZV0PACxI2ew_06dTizhZ9qK0TIYRmxhUAHeeY=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Place was very understaffed for how many people were there, my buddy who broke his leg a few months ago was denied entry because he was limping  (they said he was too drunk, he was our DD and didn’t have a single drop of alcohol) even after showing the bouncer at the door his scars from his surgery, all he got was a “thats not going to cut it buddy” and sent on his way. My other buddy and I didn’t even find out he wasn’t allowed in until an hour later because we were stuck in a 50 minute line for the bar to get a beer, all while drunk parents were cutting the line and harassing the bartenders until they caved and served them before the rest of us waiting patiently in line. Missed majority of the game we came to watch.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"P Yorkie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKXm8fzxlgv8V7tzyor1eAw3X_TYnp76PqzhYwDa2d-_ANa4w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Sat on the patio. Very dirty, leaves weeds. Dirty bench. Got it on my pants.
Wouldn't take much to make it better. Clean, maybe put out some flower plants?
Service was good, food was OK. Good price for a hamburger & fries.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Crash Ca","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKP-yIbUHbzqOyPnimZsGdHdI8HFw0BftxGUURkfEffnvjo5Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Overpriced for the quality. $11 for 5 small potato skins. Chicken in sandwiches and burgers were cold. The Ceasar dressing was of poor quality and had "blobs". Fries were over cooked.

Sever was rude. Yelled at customer. She even stated that she hates her job. Why work there then.

One of the worst places we’ve been to. Do NOT recommend this place.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMitWc-i16eNCTxvCu84D-bLzqvvwSlhFOoXaLf&fid=0x0:0x3fa692001c37a0a1"],"When":"2023-3-6"},{"Name":"Brant Andrews","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ8syFIoV5yLPh5G3s30c8WgmcBHZhv_w2vjaZWSEUawPUEfw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Worst burnt burger i ever ate in my life waitress Phenomenally rude
Yam fries completely burnt. Chicken club comes with the butt Of the breadin the center.
Took an hourcause I guess they had to heat up. The grill should have known when no one else was eating in the restaurant and it was empty.
But the waitress.  Was the worst part of the whole experiencebeyond rude","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jack Pajak","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV7kRSq5QM1wGXm36_dbE9YR6CpcUs9VUAhu1SxvpJkrQ-nGO0N=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This place is your typical hockey rink pub, big place with lots of room and nice views of the ice. I really did enjoy the atmosphere and our server did a great job. She had a wonderful attitude despite being really busy. Food selection isn't bad, but pretty basic pub fare. Quality was hit and miss with our group. Beer selection is mediocre, would be nice to see some craft beer. I won't be rushing back...but I also wouldn't object to coming here again (especially if I was at the arena for a game).","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"PJNL13","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLYPenjQYBi9sFajObxhGbZrQmEfqvSOaGuZPg6t3amiBJgGQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"This place used to be great, but recently: food has gone down in quality , service is meh and today we showed up at 17.30; it stated they were open. The board outside the restaurant even said open 1600 mon-thu.

Fully locked up, lights off.
Bring back the old management, Stacey rocked!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"H Sek","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKMZVBQClOO1wdbrsI_ks2Ywv7fIj5-Iry7hRMHVjHL3MNiuQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I like this place but I don’t understand why they are always closed during the day on the weekends.

We planned to have lunch there as a family while our kids played hockey. Only to find that they were closed for a private event. Then the next time we came today only to find that their hours have shifted from 12pm ( as shown on the Google hours ) to 2 PM opening on Saturday and Sunday.

At least change your hours of operation on your Google page so people don’t get their expectations set and then arrive at your door only to find that you guys are closed because you’ve written on a chalkboard that you change the hours or that you’ve written on a chalkboard that you have a private function . It doesn’t build a good relationship with the community with people who want to spend money and support local businesses.

If there are staffing issues or other issues, why not just have one person working at the bar and do a limited menu with walk up service?French fries and a pre made sandwichs and beer is for parents who had to get up and bring their kids to hockey.

Maybe create a buffet style brunch menu with and advertise to all of the household’s in east Maple Ridge looking for a closer restaurant/pub option?

Reducing hours is the first move towards a decline in the overall business. Instead of reducing hours for costs savings - adjust the operations to be lean and mean and try to increase traffic into the restaurant.

I will support every small business owner or business owner of Maple Ridge and Pitt Meadows 110% of the time as long as they are making the effort to create something exciting for all of us like me who are willing to support.

If the situation changes I will change this review","Images":null,"When":""}]

Absolutely blown away by the quality, flavor and freshness! Fast service and reasonable prices too.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOWmbBZP-sX03Oy16_dVDhu-MD0tP1oQgn3rN2H&fid=0x0:0x281ae37263ce53eb"],"When":"2024-9-9"},{"Name":"A L","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVDuox32jyJxnkzAm48h5i9Ht66Z7AvtkXQcQV08flbS_JcS1Q6eQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"What a fantastic find!! We just happened to be in the area and the signage caught my eye. On a whim, we decided to give it a try.

The decor is simple and modern. They have a few small tables, with highchairs and booster seats available for little ones.

We came in for a light snack but ended up ordering a full meal because the there were so many great options to choose from.

The oshi sampler is fantastic!! The perfect way to try 3 different oshi sushi on one plate. I'd highly recommend the oshi bento - it's delicious and you get so much for $19. The popcorn roll was amazing and it comes with a salad, so it's practically a meal on its own.

The staff were incredibly friendly, which was just the cherry on top of the cake!

UPDATE: we've been back multiple times since our initial visit and each time, it gets better (if that's even possible). The snow roll and the salmon/scallop flower are both INCREDIBLE!!! I'm seriously so impressed with this place.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPWvduQSzsfG2fvmvUO1-_BCzc-SosNsFP80URt&fid=0x0:0x281ae37263ce53eb"],"When":"2024-5-26"},{"Name":"Myeongseon Kim","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKHjh4_B5Gg_MY2sH5o-yYbPDnBQKnCdyPjl2p8KBFvNNvM2Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I visited Hako Sushi yesterday.

[{"Name":"Jai Baska","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJgkVPK_Dkiw14Vm-Aq7um0HdWnamyEkaSho4iN_N9YjX5tLQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Do not recommend. We ordered the cheese lovers and the studio veggie. The sauce was awful on both, it was more of a tomato paste and not a sauce. The pizza dough is too thick and ended up being mushy.
Definitely won't be ordering from these guys again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOHDMEihRidrYnZiCYn7vqA7n0FhmOQeXMlj4rw&fid=0x0:0x936d5124f21b01e6"],"When":"2024-7-21"},{"Name":"Lucía Servín","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUS0_1SZzrl8MIWHz7K1wgt06GCwcZ1zKDx5HXdd_56GENeUF_s1A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I cannot recommend this place enough.

The pizza was wonderful; The dough was soft and it reheats nicely. It is not greasy or salty, it's actually just right.

Service was great, the attendant was using a new machine and accidentally overcharged our card. However, they IMMEDIATELY noticed and returned the money. They were very apologetic and kind about it, which is rare nowadays.

Overall this place was just great. I will definitely be making it my usual pizza stop.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOpmnB4BupSydYNDdEUjJ7IPhCu5o650dBOiLID&fid=0x0:0x936d5124f21b01e6"],"When":"2023-3-19"},{"Name":"Preet Kaur","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIsErSLsaqmTPJIfLNU0QuSZ_oZ6micYt6hx6KblhQJc9uRnA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had their new samosa pizza last night and it was absolutely delicious 😋
Their baked pasta was also amazing. Just love their pizza. Best in Maple Ridge for sure 👏👍🏻","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNH_4XdzXoOoRuuQ9Y-FilAXy9l6qZqGgPjZhjj&fid=0x0:0x936d5124f21b01e6"],"When":"2023-12-31"},{"Name":"Justin Jack","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ83y92dTYSVI7JzjGk6IzdJ9YPapHBr8qfzRVUGZV_I1l0Bw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"The worst lasagna i have ever tried to eat. Just disgusting. Like soup. Pizzas were also just cold and bland missing toppings. Almost 90.00. What a waste of money. Prices are going up and the quality is going strait down. We will never eat here again.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"marksfc13","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWaVwWIUJXqYrfKREpaCfryO84EX4-G_JrUFkK12W5gQvu9XlzJ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great pizza.  I got a half pepperoni half Hawaiian and it was nicely browned (possibly too much for some people so be aware).  Lots of cheese and quality toppings.   The sauce didn't stand out but that's not necessarily a bad thing.  The crust was buttery and crispy, I enjoyed it a lot.

Excellent pizza overall, I'll order there again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNgTVr49bdFRE2izVbya63mbBNCJxcY5n7KN6I2&fid=0x0:0x936d5124f21b01e6"],"When":"2023-8-3"},{"Name":"Aryan Panech","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL7WJLB1QG4i053CDqUVljjA7cMznQO2bkJD1pz2fG7pVmz1g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Pizza Studio is hands down my new favorite pizza spot! user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Alex","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVxP-ADvohB6hXpEbci04qD4fdlJ8qjEvYJvIIZqjiOIuWU9BVM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve never had Korean fried chicken before and I kept hearing that this was the place to go. Words can’t describe how impressed I was but I’ll give it a shot.

The restaurant was clean and spacious and very well organized. There was only one person working (I’m assuming the owner) and he was very friendly and attentive. He also brought us a couple of glasses of water even though we did not ask for any which was very nice.

We decided to try 2 half orders of boneless chicken. One of their signature seasoned chicken and the other was the garlic pepper chicken. At $16.50 for a half order I have to say that they were massive portions! The chicken was boneless thigh meat in an insanely crunchy breading and tossed in these delicious, sweet and spicy sticky sauces. We managed to eat half of both and packed up the rest.

The chicken was hot, juicy, and stayed crunchy even after sitting in the sauce for a bit. This place is seriously amazing and I would recommend this to anyone. Can’t wait to come back and try their different flavours! I read in some reviews that the cream and onion flavour is good so will most likely try that one!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO_-4XpVXwS4tuiPw6wDS5_y5bBOxBRywq3CB-z&fid=0x0:0x5a3b1015c27fd198"],"When":"2024-11-24"},{"Name":"Jessameen Dela Peña","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX9mRpmL8-ZJUG7UPFcnsjzRdxjABif-MswbO1rxgJyyWfns8Jd=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"If you're a fan of Korean fried chicken, this place is a must-visit! I opted for the cream onion flavor, and it was absolutely delicious. Just a tip: if you're short on time, it's best to order ahead. Despite calling in advance, we still had to wait an additional 15 minutes upon arrival.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMDLVd5vGEFwAwdybRijl7rs9DyaZuw9XPlJ74R&fid=0x0:0x5a3b1015c27fd198"],"When":"2024-6-13"},{"Name":"Joshua (ThickBurger_Bites)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUbIhhMlbxk7OIMpcaP-aSx2m75kt8-mqmXoXAJQ5K99gnxiff1zg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Delicious fried chicken. Slightly pricy but worth a visit.

Service is good, staff come round filling water/tea every so often without having to call them over.

We had the soy chicken, spicy and original chicken and they were all delicious. A perfectly battered and crunchy fried chicken.

I’d highly recommend coming with friends to share different platter flavours.

Parking is a slight pain given how limited street parking is in this busy downtown maple ridge area.

Great place. Highly recommended.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOXdqRqFugRFsjSIar-OrOFg9YSYS3BANxLtdar&fid=0x0:0x5a3b1015c27fd198"],"When":"2021-12-26"},{"Name":"MB","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIefn3FTp9aV_tkLEMerRsiSn9abrY5dqOppBPJehNZyaGMiA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We ordered the garlic and spicy pepper and the Honey chicken. They were both amazing! Great portions, we will definitely be back and highly recommend them if you’re wanting Korean fried chicken.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPvBzA7dB5WU4vdi-h7GyCGuFA1fhuSxSZTNOfu&fid=0x0:0x5a3b1015c27fd198"],"When":"2024-2-7"},{"Name":"What did Dada buy Today!","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU7GTyMhR08A6awgaZC75A11vjN-sR6OzhegVertGwB80jthNLK=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The food was delicious 😋  excessive wait time however he was working alone so that's understandable. He did open 10 minutes early for us which was extremely kind. I will be back!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPdSi3lCKQgXgN3RIgT3BeDbZtbh41YkuS-2QJN&fid=0x0:0x5a3b1015c27fd198"],"When":"2024-4-19"},{"Name":"Mahsa Abtahi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVzZdwC4FLiBEJuimDmJEsrIg9RPx_6E61CBkExvji0Lr8i8fNl=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great fried chicken! Perfectly crispy and not greasy at all. We got the half order of original boneless chicken and the portion was big and good for two people.
The best fried chicken I've had in a very long time.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Duke Pufus","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWukW7L6iD7Fsj98lKPEw1hzjJ0B-rpWvm75WLGKOM6jjGxeeRp=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Ordered pick up, half boneless soy, half boneless honey with an order of fries. No complaints at all, excellent.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNfmuSnNKgRyuaboSV8knt3Kvt-4gSwI6r6C-QZ&fid=0x0:0x5a3b1015c27fd198"],"When":"2024-8-17"},{"Name":"Em Sm","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVlvVFz7AHLmpCOuf_XMefZGhUTofAT-w3GkZDB3K6y9G__d1JL=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is one of the best Korean Fried Chicken in the area. We've eaten in and done take out a few times, after all there is nothing like grabbing it to go and then going to a local brewery. Our go to's are the spicy mayo chicken, honey chicken, and garlic & pepper. Service is always friendly and the only thing I wish is that there was a parking lot instead of just street parking as it fills up quick.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO4wOA9AZsNdcaAHlSUDtDacmbGg3YwKHaGGfPc&fid=0x0:0x5a3b1015c27fd198"],"When":"2023-8-5"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Tara Elizabeth","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWafp5-DbmdXd42lrIMIaPpUa4TG8IACFTFef3W9rqO44JjPcQgRg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I enjoyed my chicken caprese and my friend her steak salad. What we weren't thrilled with was the service. The place was quite empty yet we were told our party of 10 was too big for the specials. They finally relented, and only one of us ordered it. The waiter was slow to check in for drinks. I easily would have had at least another, but he was missing and by the time he came back I was over wanting one. It also took way too long to get the bill and then wait for the bill to be fixed. I liked my meal and it was clean and in a nice location but I felt there was nothing special about the evening. I'm not sure I'd go back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP1A-gl_I8GkfC5NRTv5O5QgKiYMrN43U-HUACY&fid=0x0:0x9b0f34c76b4c5a9a"],"When":"2024-8-31"},{"Name":"Jim McAdie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX-13-EGR_Lu7cU4Hn29WE_0T0MjDbq8biaK-w2BWXLRJzw-ft1=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The tables are spaced very nicely and the noise level in the dining room is very pleasant. The staff was attentive and the food was outstanding. We are new to Maple Ridge and it is our first time going to The Loft but it won't be our last. Dylan was our waiter and he gave us White Glove treatment. All in all it was a wonderful experience","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Colin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWTlcHOnN1Y_P8i7yAuyqaF0Qvno8USrEfh9as8qA5pMJpj_n-z=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We went for the Thanksgiving three course. Service was excellent. The live music was fine from where we were seated but quite loud at the staircase up to the restaurant.

My companion enjoyed her salad starter. My butternut squash soup was tasty but closer to a puree in texture and it would have benefitted from a little stock or cream.

The turkey dinner was very good. The turkey was moist, the mashed potatoes were smooth and the gravy added a lot of flavor. I would have preferred more veggies and less potatoes, but the proportions were pretty standard for most restaurants.

The pumpkin pie was smooth and tasty, if a little cinnamon forward. It was a bit surprising but I liked it.

This was our first visit to The Loft and we will definitely be going back to try brunch and prime rib night.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Antonio Vidal","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXh_xAWsf04qNgEzZEcU9YIpjJ4mya_-AYPRaWQ1_Pj-gNwn70DRg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Was disappointed. I understand that it was new year's eve but they should've planned better considering the price of the "experience" they were offering. The French 75 drink wasn't very well made - Prosecco mixed with gin and citrus are just not a good combination. Plus it wasn't served cold. The kushi oysters were weirdly served with carrot and turnip/radish slices. The carpaccio, while good, had too little beef and was overwhelmed by the salad. The Cesar salad was good.  The soup was good too and so was the surf and turf. The beef medallion was perfectly cooked but the scallops were too salty. They forgot to serve the palate cleanser between the starters and entrees. The creme brulee was much too thick and sweet as if made with condensed milk.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPn00zQfvMrVj1waX5Hlm7uAJNaNkUloexMaFcx&fid=0x0:0x9b0f34c76b4c5a9a"],"When":"2024-1-1"},{"Name":"Ghazal","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWUxPjakfUDfUlOphLX0NHrhY3j03bOfl1WB2qtK88VIEBoxSUc=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Beautiful space. The food tasted good and they had good options for the wine flight. The bread was complementary which added to the dining experience.
We went on a Sunday evening and the place was really quiet. It’s good if you’d just like to relax and enjoy your food but I prefer a busier place.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM9T4DQuAsHB1pIcQsCTWs5OCBxIw7OEA9bCPcd&fid=0x0:0x9b0f34c76b4c5a9a"],"When":"2023-2-13"},{"Name":"danielle loranger","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJnptNzs1wQbaw2FFsd1jy4E7t0vjMoJDS7syMM-SOyTKG9og=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Such a great view from the restaurant and beautiful at sunset. We stopped in after hitting the driving range up one night and enjoyed some cocktails which were great and I’d go back for the Caesar salad alone! We both really enjoyed our meals and can’t wait to try them out again hopefully for their prime rib night!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sheida Ji","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXfmsaPSmIspnVYmHG0D2yN09pwU4n-gVoapn6SGWlQigfUs2rQGQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’m mad at myself for not coming here sooner !
It was AMAZING !
All the dishes we got were very tasty and the waitress ( grace ) was very friendly and nice","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPJ7vARWmUF7N8JkUc08bnHi7-UOAq6Jngjah-m&fid=0x0:0x9b0f34c76b4c5a9a"],"When":"2023-9-1"},{"Name":"Tanya Grubic REALTOR","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWnpefUHC_L67dV5Iazonxfl2ZjNS2LupqOELwQK_dGIraI59FLjg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This restaurant is a true gem, offering a dining experience that combines top-notch cuisine with a beautiful setting. Whether you’re coming off the green or simply looking for a great meal, this establishment promises to deliver on all fronts. Highly recommended for its excellent food, superb service, and delightful atmosphere.","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"ClayPhoenix4","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVelJECogE7AFzsG2ZmzVGlq92_4MqwMY_QK6n2nHeBRJeGCXg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"2 Peaks is a place that if you were driving on 228 between Louheed and Dewdney Trunk rd that if you blinked; you will drive right past it.
This place serves up protein smoothies, protein iced coffee,  energy refreshers, and of course protein waffles too.
I stopped in there on a Sunday morning and this tiny 7 seater place was super busy and makes stuff custom and fresh to order. It takes some time to get your drink or food, do don't be in a rush when you stop in.
They have plenty of choices and even have a festive Christmas items too. I tried the strawberry cheesecake waffle and a drink.  I will try this place again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNZSDImt3xNICHu1ThyvV7_JuN1iXmDoQ-umLJF&fid=0x0:0x226e12fa572d776"],"When":"2024-12-9"},{"Name":"Rajneet Kaur","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVuDeAhvKvr2CfZCfms0-FbTtJcx7KrL3q8k01yvvkJ8kbgOjg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I went at 2 peaks this was the amazing place for healthy and nutritious food
So hygiene and most importantly their taste of the things I tried was amazing  must try their waffles I am in love with them and shakes are so yummy and delicious.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOPXcp8iN-7eSyjsaT6d_g1_XNfDaU93bTtHbmr&fid=0x0:0x226e12fa572d776"],"When":"2024-12-14"},{"Name":"Erin Belong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKUAZ1cw3oG6a19gSLsIUcNmMv23rMusq1hsAnvDHBk67o_2g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is one of our family’s favourite spots in maple ridge. Everything is delicious and healthy, allowing us to have a guilt free treat packed with protein. The owners are both wonderful and kind people who take the time to chat and get to know their customers. Highly recommend giving 2peaks a try!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNZ4HsyGQdll_2UJ4Nh2zTNLeeG_eNv8LWaZ-V3&fid=0x0:0x226e12fa572d776"],"When":"2024-10-25"},{"Name":"Tara Phaneuf","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK_1ZNS1aZ82sIvocAL3LMm-3mbxcWf4QhpeHIiFTHNmzn89w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"First time in this morning and I will definitely back. So many things on the menu I want to try! Today I had the banana split protein shake. Delicious and satiating. The owner was so friendly and welcoming, and the waffles they were cooking up smelled amazing. Definitely want to try them as well as the protein coffees and refreshers (less than 1g of sugar! compared to 20+ grams in the ones from SB) So happy to have a place like this in Maple Ridge! 👏👏","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN1fAuPLaMlINAe-eJnGKuaiaxLjaOdbT1_M-cx&fid=0x0:0x226e12fa572d776"],"When":"2024-6-1"},{"Name":"Christyna MacKinnon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVd03A-MQOjTk0kQYLO-W9Hh-dzCH4U9h6OLZm8TKedakM4y8HE=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I love this place. Everything I've tried is delicious! The owners are so personable and the service is great. If you haven't stopped in do it. We will definitely be back to try their protein waffles and their energy refreshers!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNaj8Rxll2FkjnOHg2gqt7rmJSX5mvtXY7dg5_b&fid=0x0:0x226e12fa572d776"],"When":"2024-9-2"},{"Name":"kirandeep kahlon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXzJl_fv3oj-ENurE7kXAPhr1fPN-hlvHQVGyNAR6xAXA-PMzQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"If you’re looking for a spot that offers nutritious snacks, 2 Peak has you covered! Food wise the bowls are interesting - got the poke bowl with lemongrass chicken and it was stringy and didn’t taste like lemongrass. They also just drowned the bowl in the dressing - next time I’ll be sure to ask for dressing on the side. The poke bowl with salmon was a lot better but again way too much sauce for my liking.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO5YoJfd1tqSTUy18pa3WTROElOIO6zuXnS-sZ0\u0026fid=0x0:0x304d765bd7ee491b"],"When":"2024-8-18"},{"Name":"Elizabeth M","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXuhhJ3L27gYQJMwvKARhYEqE4v9PowLqfpDtvNV5G-CUir9-oeQg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Finally visited Alina Cafe! After hearing all the positive reviews on Facebook my husband and I decided to have lunch there! These pictures don't do it justice. The food is amazing! Clean food and just good! The service was also amazing. We were greeted as soon as we walked in and I just loved the atmosphere! Cannot wait to go back and try more dishes. An absolute gem here in maple ridge ☺️","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNYm2S9iHGc1ugp3DeKNpq9iw56me77xTKEoTL5\u0026fid=0x0:0x304d765bd7ee491b"],"When":"2024-5-21"},{"Name":"Suzanne Mizuguchi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI8b0Ockfgm8cZmPcyRnN5zpwKwmWy9CesunN2BLeMd0cWNNA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"First time visiting, but I will definitely be back! My partner and I split the lemongrass beef banh mi, which was such a refreshing sandwich, as well as the bbq pork banh mi, which was hearty and delicious. I also loved their Vietnamese iced coffee. The matcha latte was well made, but it does come unsweetened, which might not be for everyone.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNVbaDbslHEOiyDzcDVU6LnDUaBFh3xYep6HtZT\u0026fid=0x0:0x304d765bd7ee491b"],"When":"2024-10-1"},{"Name":"Amrita Nayak","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXJgJ3b8LMBlPc7G1Rv8sy6cyH33IeJwYGYkw6c-i8ocBKF5odAKg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The menu promises healthy and tasty food, and it delivers exactly that. I tried their lemongrass chicken banhmi, and it was a delightful blend of lightness and fullness, bursting with flavor in every bite. Plus, their packaging adds an extra touch of cuteness to the experience. If you're looking for a cozy spot with delicious food and a welcoming atmosphere, this cafe is a must-visit!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOxlo1YdSFh6n_r_b4Nn0NHkFaiSLaE_aYUDMgx\u0026fid=0x0:0x304d765bd7ee491b"],"When":"2024-5-28"},{"Name":"rue deda","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXibaxGcWhkUgVv8yAdsNj_gFfT8xdcP4x5agl54xhRKeqduIfe-A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Loved it. The server was so patient and hospitable,open to giving us recommendations,  the ambience is refreshing, just what you need to wind down, there's a little corner with books, coloring books and a fish tank, the kids love it too. Food was great, vegan options were a bonus, accommodated every one and affordable prices. Definitely coming back","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOa_Bu7Tmvxd9Mvxt5oMytzAxBlyXB9h66JshpV\u0026fid=0x0:0x304d765bd7ee491b"],"When":"2024-3-21"},{"Name":"Emanuel Alvez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLDqzPVRZ29DEvctA5XU2KzMKH2kzwG3aCUYnzHdsDlf93QYg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"great time here while charging the car. got the chicken bahn mi and viet iced coffee. delicious!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM-STGvIu2rbYKPM05lOEvFUqgB0gN4tx3_7o-r\u0026fid=0x0:0x304d765bd7ee491b"],"When":"2024-8-10"},{"Name":"David Watson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIlLXWimZHgvvuzr5ZcDE94rTPwZPQ5wMHGDSK7k_gT43KEXw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Absolute gem of a restaurant. [{"Name":"Rolando_ Rose","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIQBfjayv2V3eqQ6nmwU1uOEqgsWCG5VdwRxO3uXCF1EsXQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Just average donair. The ambiance of the restaurant looks too tired and needs some love. While the tomatoes, onions, cucumbers and iceberg lettuce are fresh and crunchy, there’s not enough flavour in chicken donair, garlic sauce is not garlicky at all. Good location in Maple Ridge, easy to find and easily accessible from Lougheed Highway, Dewdney Trunk Road, and 207 Street. But what I am looking for a great Shawarma is the ones that you can find in the streets of Dubai, Doha, Riyadh, Jeddah, Abu Dhabi and other Middle Eastern towns and cities.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNIQPd4E_o7w_BbGyfqPk915vsWz1S8eH70Rz8&fid=0x0:0x5e8488cbaa6706fa"],"When":"2024-12-20"},{"Name":"Paxton Skrukwa","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLIn2o1TGm6qhK760ufU-Ks7kFr_uE1jgLQEnBiAZxtwNR7zw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Donair was hot and fresh , I've never experienced so much flavour. Great job ! this may be a monthly occurrence since I'm out of town . Its that good . Tell him Cactus Jack sent you !","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPHgQao0OeuiW5zKxrRPHm3XHJacxPgUExW92cC&fid=0x0:0x5e8488cbaa6706fa"],"When":"2024-8-30"},{"Name":"Aaron Z","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVRwH-T4meTA46mZWwBX8SW-8HRP3aTbI4qdWLp7QDk8OwKOg_kvA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Fantastic establishment. I don't even live in maple ridge but make the commute often to eat here. They have delicious beef and chicken as well I just prefer the falafels myself.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPNZLZeJxYHUamHEcsS-3f7nYAZ-IBAabR5u-lj&fid=0x0:0x5e8488cbaa6706fa"],"When":"2024-4-24"},{"Name":"Amy Lapka","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKz5WqBgZ-zOQMq0YADkQNpSRdLNSESLBD_mbCIt7uT_WLpFQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We love Donair Top! They offer generous toppings, good flavours, and lots of options. Any time we’re there, we’re never the only regulars in there. My pictures are of tonight’s chicken salads!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN8B_uAMdw62GFbfxByZe4axPxMpxFrsk0biYgv&fid=0x0:0x5e8488cbaa6706fa"],"When":"2020-3-5"},{"Name":"Kim Lovino","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVgFvPz1MLcDh2p7hkNMTeAwE3jmU0_hDAwvlUIGOia6_lY6RBkFQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"HAVE YOU TRIED A DONAIRxPOUTINE YET? For less than $10 you can!

We tried this small Donair shop at Maple Ridge and it's 🔥! Hands down one of the best Donair places we've been to in a while! 👌 With the price, you also get a drink 👀

We ordered:
-Super Donair Poutine ($8.50)
-Chicken Platter ($10.00 w/ pop pop)
-Hawaiian Lamb Donair ($8.50 w/ pop)

Check the place out when you're HANGRY and you're near the area!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNA5DZTlvcsL8Y5pWGihmlRWo07dKeuy26Dd1Pv&fid=0x0:0x5e8488cbaa6706fa"],"When":"2020-2-10"},{"Name":"Farzad Yarahmadi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWVL1ZNumRCDrzHwZgrUFz5SXcIggox3bY1UrnohOO-CZKUBM3msA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I recently purchased a chicken donair from Donair Tope, and I am extremely disappointed with the quality. The donair had a terrible smell, making it inedible. I couldn't even take a single bite before having to throw it away in the garbage. This experience was very frustrating, and I don't recommend to any one.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Elizabeth Bruneau","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVEfdwdzg7a-t-FvED_e_ICeY6c2F9wWHziEFSCxCklwPPHJYvB=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"They're one of my favorite donut places and I kid you not I have tried everywhere. Nowhere is as good as this place and if anybody says different then they are absolutely out of their freaking minds. Every time I have to order a donor protein from somewhere else it's always missing one thing whether it's the gravy the cheese or the taziki. I'm not sure why every other donor place doesn't just make their donairs exactly like this place.

The only downside of this place is they do not have any delivery services they need to get on skip or Uber or something. I would literally become a delivery person just for this place.","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Rose Brooks","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLEZN6Jp2sdXZuycOhlLCrFmULMG7W4UHOyCzCH_Jn46bjpOw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Can’t believe we hadn’t tried this great little small business before now. The menu is exactly the right size for each item to get the attention it deserves, and focuses on traditional diner dishes like breakfast and burgers. The tomato basil soup is great, and even better paired with the incredible Parmesan crusted 4 cheese grilled cheese!
Omelettes are perfectly cooked, with hash browns fancied up with onion and peppers. Love the sourdough bread! Our server Miranda was an absolute delight.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPU3vLEt9JIL-tDiSvPp9gu2RBgDKizcXTTd4gh&fid=0x0:0x32c5fde9dcd4fc1d"],"When":"2024-8-19"},{"Name":"Hemant Kumar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVCmWxkyjYv7PKwZ6ybYox_-smlfUHZeT12o3_8VllBRzoBeRg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Recently visited Ricky’s Country Restaurant and had a pleasant experience overall. The service was fantastic—our server was attentive, friendly, and made sure we had everything we needed. The atmosphere was also a highlight, offering a cozy and welcoming environment that made for an enjoyable dining experience.

However, I must mention that the food was a bit of a letdown. I ordered the chicken sandwich, and few other things but unfortunately, the sandwich was quite bland and lacking in flavor. Despite this, other aspects of the meal were satisfactory.

In summary, Ricky’s is a great spot for a relaxed meal with excellent service and a lovely atmosphere. While the chicken sandwich didn’t impress, I’m looking forward to trying other items on the menu on my next visit.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNdSvNGylvLjLgi7wZWmxXE4ushe68gLepIMM4&fid=0x0:0x32c5fde9dcd4fc1d"],"When":"2024-7-11"},{"Name":"James Mendonca","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKDOYVs1G-8iT9QF6Fj3_nUauDo1DS6zISrEp3lZ9wij4inDQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The Ricky's Country Restaurant in Maple Ridge was pretty good. I only had the Cheese Lovers Omelette with cubed hash browns and sourdough toast. The omelette was good, although the cheese could have been melted more. The hashbrowns and toast was decent. The service was top-notch, since the waitress was very cordial and came to my table frequently. I will come back to this location the next time I am in Maple Ridge.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNrlk4Ajxg-nLrNXIWmwD8woD7BDhl2SdUYQdzn&fid=0x0:0x32c5fde9dcd4fc1d"],"When":"2024-10-8"},{"Name":"Maryam BG","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXYOocnrrI0wz1xy1UzzrfX002uyW86PfiNNhxdXyfBusTbUhlS=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing customer service, our server was very attentive to our table and the food was out in 10 minutes! We ordered the big breakfast with the veggie chicken omlete. I replaced the toast for buttermilk pancakes and I am so glad I did because the pancakes are amazing!

Addition: we visited this restaurant again today and I would like to aknowledge Shannon as an excellent server, she was very attentive and exceptionally nice! Love the energy she brings","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNCP9iVEGlJY3qhwpDF7uAMI8NTIuTJzt0tCoKi&fid=0x0:0x32c5fde9dcd4fc1d"],"When":"2024-3-26"},{"Name":"Uros Nikolic","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXqZKUGj61BfmTYu8vecdYC7cNoaJsQnfWJB3zipm50mUOPG3Y=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Food was delicious 👌🏼
I highly recommend this restaurant when you’re in Maple Ridge","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMAR4gV8BbiJlMbacua5ZLyt_brb717LA5m_x_Q&fid=0x0:0x32c5fde9dcd4fc1d"],"When":"2024-11-28"},{"Name":"Chelsea Vancouver","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVHVWaXfVBGL-NRGFFbHN7eiAD3hCGrOaEohFBcpGwJyjbv0CUl=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Food was ok. Few vegetarian and vegan options. I got the avocado toast without egg and it was a little sad TBH. The meat dishes others at my table ordered looked much better though. Friendly service. Gendered bathrooms.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNk-cri_Nphzuqrcwp0wxB7za5YCqw5Vc7bWFY&fid=0x0:0x32c5fde9dcd4fc1d"],"When":"2024-4-27"},{"Name":"Jamie Marchand","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXLHCICIGmDe3ikuqwvvxfxv0KoSickBkjAxg4OpQHFM_hqiTE=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I would say the service was even a 6 star experience. The food here never disappoints and they always have something new and fun to try. Ricky’s always has well trained staff that communicate well with customers, smiling and patient yet efficient! We always leave full and happy. The kids love the treasure chest too, great idea! The bench seat we were at needed a little love, but we were still comfortable. Thanks for the service and good food!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Blake Andrews","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLr6CliOagk-ptarMCoZSHXojGr-ApVBclb60FlmLRpUMAGdw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had a lovely Sunday meal. We will definitely be back every weekend!","Images":null,"When":""}]

You will definitely leave with enough food for another meal.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPZRpQbd1dwXrnY6BMQdJFpzOfV_73k8tc9HofC&fid=0x0:0xf67d5394cd500611"],"When":"2024-9-30"},{"Name":"Ash R","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUCcJlHwE4izM0F5v3JT69CAyK03CVkDSxImo4puINMRF5V7q8eog=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Was recommended to us, so we ordered two daily specials yesterday for dinner pick up.

Staff: I believe it was the owners that I interacted with. They are so efficient, warm and friendly!

Food: The prices have gone up since the menu pictures posted on here. So the daily special is now $15.95 for 3 items and wonton soup. But the portions are refreshingly large, and the food is delicious! ☺️👍🏽
(Pictured is the mushroom fried rice, pork chop suey and sweet & sour pork. Wonton soup not pictured, but I would say it's a 2 cup sized container).

Parking: There is some street parking out front. Which is great for pick up.

Highly recommend and we will definitely be back!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMsBCY_VR9xw8nTt6iCU2yAv-5lDUiqwh1mNMAJ&fid=0x0:0xf67d5394cd500611"],"When":"2024-8-19"},{"Name":"Robyn G","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK9GXkw-9s6-iB_2NgpG9t2eLiMtiw6ShgHbyNxnStcj0ZIWA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"First time we ordered from here. We've tried every other Chinese food place here in maple ridge. Wow we are blown away. This is what you call authentic Chinese food. Big portions. Definitely will be our go to Chinese food restaurant! Highly recommended","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ashley Stanowski","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJcBriTpE9lCmUCcexEfwU5vbtIxzzdMxIMDrT2rcWMt02YOQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Don’t let the dated building fool you, this is great food! Everything was cooked perfectly and super flavourful. AND THE PORTIONS ARE HUGE! I had to stop only a third of the way in, I was stuffed! Excellent experience, we are very satisfied and happy. THANK YOU!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOP_uLyk1zMWmgImheBgdF1lLEMymkepPNcc_we&fid=0x0:0xf67d5394cd500611"],"When":"2024-6-23"},{"Name":"SALLY YOUNG","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJfcu_oZoQJtUA7Yjtpc8LxpW0k-K7e3GcuoTzP9-IlkP9Llw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had chinese food for Xmas eve. Food was ready on time and we ordered several dishes and all were very good.  The couple who own it are very friendly.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Cdn Chick","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU545v6W7r-6x-UEIb8QlKT_isW0v2lWx4NGtJqmJLsyjTjHpg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Small mom and pop restaurant that offers great deals and huge portions!  Best prices in town!  Thanks Peter and Lily!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNPLS44vDt8ky1LGFzBKs_z92GM3WACynRcLiMK&fid=0x0:0xf67d5394cd500611"],"When":"2023-7-23"},{"Name":"Simon Joe","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW0f5G4fJ3M8QEGA_STxGDiI3Ok5iguc7BSlANH3xP15ogo-pLQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is a small Chinese restaurant which is most likely run by a husband and wife team. The decoration is dated, but the food tastes really good, even though it may be better if the amount of salt or conditioning can be reduced a bit to suit our lighter taste. We are amazed at the speed of serving & plate sizes. The price is unbeatable too. Three big dishes of fried rice, wonton soup, cheese sandwich and fries offered more than enough for our family of 4 with 2 preteen boys. We can't believe that the total price was only a bit more than $30. What a friendly and down to earth Chinese restaurant with great value for your wallet!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM884l3nRd_9t1-MC5K57XavEsCCX_Wrdh8ccud&fid=0x0:0xf67d5394cd500611"],"When":"2023-8-2"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Maddie Cruz","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLYQL8qAGmTqshoOvCaBdSsq6642zngm2cAUSDTjLzVVtrLpg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This family owned business offered a variety of delicious foods to choose from. Each one were super tasty and I love that they can customize too based to your preference or remove ingredients that will cause allergies. There are many vegan/vegetarian options. The servers and the owner were very attentive to our needs and came to often us ask if we need anything else.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNLndGC3GHhppjePZ5bsHgfypqV-1J8mP1GoutX&fid=0x0:0x5d2de521def31059"],"When":"2024-8-18"},{"Name":"Mitsuba","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWPTokkJ7B-7PXzC1asSVZYKNDX01MAmrvmPdKoBlxIra8E3U0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I came here for lunch with my friend. And ordered the butter chicken lunch special.

I usually do not eat such cuisines. However the food was made with heart and very authentic. It had flavors I did not taste before. And I enjoyed it greatly.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOP6ye1gyjFbkwpJjBB2DQcuAO5R61wbXZB-wqy&fid=0x0:0x5d2de521def31059"],"When":"2024-8-31"},{"Name":"Tracy L Last","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ38Cu0Ieij8mOpHtzR8lkJfIZMeXwsqQPTIoyMuZiP-SX_Gg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"GM is always great food! For my birthday my husband said order from anywhere so I chose this. I also spoiled us with getting double of what we usually do. Taking time to read all the descriptions. Everything we ordered was absolute deliciousness.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNip6Et0N9sBmAHpgoL1Xz0LAcFQU2wII7JNtcm&fid=0x0:0x5d2de521def31059"],"When":"2024-5-15"},{"Name":"Ryan Blight","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXbpH73lI2xtK9WJxadw5s8Ist4ItI3NEBYZImc9aopB1Hhs9lf=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"First time at GM. We ordered a veg platter and a meat platter, and finished off with a slice of salted caramel cheesecake. Food was delicious, but lacking one star due to ordering a 5/10 spice level and the food was definitely lacking spice.
Overall good experience and friendly service.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMOxldDBLIOnjCpUtt4AhbxsCu_TWic2FxZ8d4E&fid=0x0:0x5d2de521def31059"],"When":"2024-2-16"},{"Name":"Annie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJAG4UtHNdn-C74S5I053c9lMdRMdh_AH35u090AgjHoFmF2GSW=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I am not the biggest cheesecake lover but kept hearing great reviews about the cheesecake at GM so I finally went to try. The cheesecake was absolutely delicious. The texture and flavours were perfect. 1 slice is $10 and a whole cheesecake is $65. The lovely and friendly owner said that with 24-48 hrs notice they can fill your custom flavor order. We will definitely be back!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP3JUPV3ePj8FKBEXmBUjWRO3l_-1iS54YfLSrF&fid=0x0:0x5d2de521def31059"],"When":"2023-5-26"},{"Name":"Laura Elizabeth","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWYZmTmHFFXOkGtfdW2Ry40xOSRalp27hpu_nLOavLst35yPmg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Today was my husband’s birthday and by the time dinner rolled around I was too tired to cook (throwing 3 parties in a month is fun but exhausting) so I decided to order out. My daughter has severe allergies and so I called GM and asked about some dairy AND coconut free dishes. With a solid option in hand I looked on the DoorDash menu and couldn’t find it. So I chose something that sounded allergen free and left a note. When my food arrived everything was  there but they had also included a free dairy/coconut free dish for my daughter that was unexpected, delicious and the random act of kindness my heart needed. Thanks GM for going out of your way to bless our family and gift my daughter with food options - it can be hard as a 7 year old to constantly hear “sorry, you can’t have that.”

Not pictured is the garlic naan bread - so delicious.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNfzohkWzevQtdqmGpaHJk-7AY0p5daZkiSshoR&fid=0x0:0x5d2de521def31059"],"When":"2024-6-9"},{"Name":"Phil Rumming","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJI8F-4PSRI8O1IIK_Whhw86Nv8AmAOyTVmk8Hdizbg38WBDQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Excellent food and service. I had Butter Chicken (a large serving, enough for 2 at least) along with naan bread and basmati rice: all were very good with an Indian Kingfisher beer. This was followed by an slice (huge!) of delicious eggnog cheese cake and an 'Indian' coffee. They have a large variety of cheese cake flavors to choose from.   Looking forward to future visits.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mike F","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXniLjCJHKt8Gj17xGqax1pu33ZsNusLLpEEFXEep3h7_9bcNk=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I already know this will go against the grain since this place has always been very good and very popular as well as very expensive. Recently we ordered take out from there, typically butter chicken, naan bread and rice. We also ordered one samosa of each flavour. I’m not sure what happened to our food but it was the worse, least tasting butter chicken I had ever had, actually despicable. You spend a fortune on a meal thinking you’re paying a little more but never expecting to get the tasteless slop we ended up with, never again. On the other hand, the samosas were on point!","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Brad Phillips","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJQyFNsFglxRT3PC62NhebhL95uOjnpyv1STZkZSCcY47DFig=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Absolutely fantastic service and delicious food. I wouldn't hesitate to recommend this unique little dinner to anyone. We have some friends coming from Australia next month, and can't wait to bring them here for an experience that will last in their memories for ever. Rachel was our server and she was so pleasant and helpful. She really made us feel special and appreciated. What a great addition to the experience, she was very professional, friendly and fun to interact with. We can't wait to go back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPcu50mtB-OjViO7YevVbLD2g9vK2QCDE4ZbEwK&fid=0x0:0x59ed2235bfec975b"],"When":"2024-12-22"},{"Name":"James McCann","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVeljiarzTiu1tTE6Pve6MGW2hSCoI2cGrsZixTLACpSmPcWmbb=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I saw this place on Google Maps, so I checked it out in person.

The atmosphere is fun and colourful. It's an idyllic 50s diner. The place was busy, food was portioned well for the price, and the coffee was flowing.

What really sets it apart is the friendly and happy staff. They'll make your experience worth the visit.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMIk5YXkjJoNnfq-0sx_mC6_ebbuxl7d81r8QXx&fid=0x0:0x59ed2235bfec975b"],"When":"2024-12-23"},{"Name":"James Inouye","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUGMUsvXLijMfgZydLJhU2TpG1bqPFbrelq3iJSQAmmOzYoUfG8Bg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It was one of the best breakfast places I have been to. I ordered the tater breaky bowl, and it was amazing. The staff is very friendly and provides excellent customer service.

This place used to be awesome but the last few times I've been here...it's gone WAAAAAYYYY downhill 🤢
If I didn't say anything they would've charged me for the non-existant cheese and the whole wrap.
SERVICE IS GREAT THOUGH!!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO73ctKdt-cPX_0hy_cIGNvkxS2-9T4jnK7QaOI&fid=0x0:0x59ed2235bfec975b"],"When":"2024-9-18"},{"Name":"Wihse Stacey","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLleemwAf-XK30uwy4fv5glDOpm4ky8um81Yx_HZwfIc6-vFA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"My burger was awesome.  Whiskey BBQ sauce!  Can't go wrong.  50's style diner truly fits.  I loved the decor.  I'm not a huge fan of 50's music, but they had some good chair dancing tunes going.  It was a last minute choice and it was a great choice. Very good prices too.","Images":null,"When":""}]
