user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Alex","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVxP-ADvohB6hXpEbci04qD4fdlJ8qjEvYJvIIZqjiOIuWU9BVM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Came here for a spontaneous date night. Spacious eating area and live band on weekends so that was nice. Food was really good. The Well Burger is solid. Homemade 6oz patty with a nice char on the outside. Service was a bit slow (we were there about an 1h30mins) however they were hosting what looked like a Christmas staff party for a large group so it was understandable. I also felt like the portion size for the fries that came with the burger was a tad small but everything was hot and fresh so overall it was delicious. Would definitely return!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMk0TReCZMW6ByWvE3B4u4CqyRh0Uy0F3XtYt7K&fid=0x0:0x29766a1c2996e3c1"],"When":"2024-11-3"},{"Name":"Julie B","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW4pd43YT5KSqkORSPaVbra7_KcodZ1kkwID5yaolZD_WuCOEiQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Had dinner with friends.
Her and I both got the Veal schnitzel, was good but the vegetables were over cooked. The roasted potatoes were ok.
And our other friend got the Ginger Beef and Broccoli, it was meh. Not really anything close to a Ginger beef, more like Hosing cause with beef and broccoli.
Last was the Well Burger. Was OK.

There was only one server and she was extremely run off her feet but she was doing the best she could.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPFCL0kdKDFaAhQxSjUK8C6rhh3pz4aTqtGeUfC&fid=0x0:0x29766a1c2996e3c1"],"When":"2024-1-25"},{"Name":"Barendina Smith","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU4gAXNw7bsOWNo-qAPQuFfFYX-uW_wVZHByRe8lPzJaAZZQQG6pQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Wow this place has certainly gone down a long steep hill since 2022.  Paid $18.90 + tip total $22 for this tiny grilled ham & cheese.

Bread was sourdough & EXTREMELY hard.  It tore apart the inside of my mouth. Only 1 thin slice of ham folded in half on my sandwich. Paid $2 for side of gravy, which was only filled a quarter of the way up in small container. What did they expect me to do with that! & that was $19..

What a disappointment. I go to this establishment a few times a month, & I've never been so upset with a meal. No, I did not complain; it is not my nature.

My son also got chicken strips & fries, & his strips were so hard & small & he got about a tablespoon of dip in his small container. 😡

Overall, just a really, really bad experience. I do hope management sees this!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNkChnt9LmPwwlV2ou89or3GsgwnAD-iLAsWbS2&fid=0x0:0x29766a1c2996e3c1"],"When":"2024-1-10"},{"Name":"Leah","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWt2ep7OMjltFmWQzS3XFoIWjRO47VrI6MupJ2gMQDNDdAaE18CrQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Wonderful staff, amazing food, and very enticing atmosphere. We had the Mac n cheese w/broccoli and bacon, the beef dip, and a Ruben. Absolutely amazing and all for a decent price. Would definitely recommend and go again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP5qk-4NGeIGRQ2CnV6foYf1wHo9gPWWIFDxTUk&fid=0x0:0x29766a1c2996e3c1"],"When":"2018-7-5"},{"Name":"Grace Baptiste","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWYWSGyxL6xv7wCMnONngE95_lFn-QFdC26NOw2Rzl5vHdq9MLmkw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Steak & eggs were delicious. (Not on the menu btw but you can request it) Service was very good and the atmosphere was nice and relaxing. Nice fireplace and open concept. Will try again forsure! Pricing was also good.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPJKFWp_W7FK46gBxgohi5ezIxjTJY9ssEBXvQz&fid=0x0:0x29766a1c2996e3c1"],"When":"2023-10-10"},{"Name":"ClayPhoenix4","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVelJECogE7AFzsG2ZmzVGlq92_4MqwMY_QK6n2nHeBRJeGCXg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Pre covid this was the place for great deals and good quality food and i would eat dinner here 3 tines a week. But for the past 3-4 years the quality and value of the food has become a complete dumpster fire and 🗑. There are no daily deals, no specials, just the most mediocre food ever. It is so bad that I frequently choose to go hungry than to eat nothing but disappointment. It is now $10 for a bowl of tomato soup or even a simple mushroom soup (not even a protein 🤦)
The only thing keeping the doors open is the casino, because if this was a "stand alone restaurant" it would have closed years ago.
The only savior is the long term staff that all know this place is a joke! I have eaten here tons of times and know the difference between good food and garbage,  so take my advice and eat somewhere else; unless you enjoy breakfast that almost everything gets dumped in the deep fryer flavor where the only savior is the toast. 👎
I give the food ZERO stars if I could and I am being very generous with this review.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Pooja K","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI-ssEEl6Av2NXTNEvITlxy4r9NclpyO6oAAInk0KHt0F4u0jQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Ordered their wings and they tasted like they were old had been fried multiple times... were not tasty. Felt gross/sick after eating them. Drinks were ok.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Leah Bruce","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWkX62WTTSocBgHktQdxD3aUnx5z9bphuCE7ycZjFNu-MaWl5q7=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It was our first time here last month and we popped in for lunch. We were very impressed with the $9 price tag on the flatbread pizza so that's what we ordered!! I had the "Mediterranean" which is nicely finished with some fresh, cold cucumber! Delish and took home half for breaky the next day! My husband had the "Pepperoni Plus" and was happy with his choice. Yum! Will be back again!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN7fAPVAPMax8HEyiSB5gwIRKWXpxfUyDpkvvaj&fid=0x0:0x29766a1c2996e3c1"],"When":"2017-10-5"}]

[{"Name":"Nidhi Kukreti","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUkwLGU0qL5R4gpFxJSktJd2bFgwdSs8uzUdgRJFVvHPQaNnjI=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Went for dinner, it was good 👍. Food was decent i like onion naan(must try). Chole bature were also good in taste. Service is little bit slow. Overall my experience was good.
If you’re looking buffet for a lunch in good price then do visit. Parking is available and free.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOdhJaDq--0Ap2MoURqhN_MUbNlhlOtOT7FGqal&fid=0x0:0x1e49bab05c66116c"],"When":"2024-7-15"},{"Name":"Boomer Melba","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLpQCzaaqJHvJb1W9difmwMVVfm_-vvbvXCCr9-sUgk4-fMLw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Always the best. We drive by dozens of Indian restaurants to get to this gem.
They have now added a mango cheesecake for dessert that was the bomb!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOgEqodMqRMKqHn_6MedZOpEedkAW6PzYdl1EaI&fid=0x0:0x1e49bab05c66116c"],"When":"2024-9-10"},{"Name":"Angadpal Singh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW1E381c52z9XIVulx92KauqWKJLwuMBE0Z7OrBhAurLG5IAkAInw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I recently visited JMK Mahal Restaurant for their lunch buffet, and it was an okay experience. The buffet offered a decent number of dishes, but the quality was hit-or-miss. For appetizers, there were only two options - tandoori chicken and samosa. Unfortunately, the tandoori chicken was dry and not impressive.

The main course had two chicken items, and the butter chicken was the highlight - it was flavorful and enjoyable. The vegetable mix was just average, and the rice was good. However, I was disappointed that they ran out of basic salad items like onions and cucumbers by 1:30 PM, and they didn't replenish them even after we asked. This was a letdown, especially since the buffet was supposed to be available until 3 PM.

Overall, it was an okay experience, and the price of $15 per person was reasonable. However, I hope they improve their buffet offerings and replenish items more regularly to enhance the dining experience.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN94vgQ14iXtz_OpUP7y9Iab_xIy9VY2sf7fXRv&fid=0x0:0x1e49bab05c66116c"],"When":"2024-5-14"},{"Name":"Mitch C.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUigQKnsqnd6-ECKxiWLF3yOJGPZULiTcrsHXswZ-6rjxY7_wxITQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Happy to see this place spring back after a fire during covid if I recall correctly... Went for the Dinner Buffet. They have a lunch buffet every day I think. The dinner buffet is Friday through Sunday. Tasty food, seemed like good quality ingredients. With a nice variety of dishes. There was a lot of available seating and the place wasn't busy (2 other tables in use), which is why the service was kinda shockingly bad (there was a high staff to guest ratio). I think it might have been just bad luck, or maybe just the person responsible doesn't understand buffet service expectations. In my opinion, even at a buffet service is important. Plus it's an opportunity for the staff to earn tips to share with the kitchen etc. It would take much effort to really elevate the experience. Clearing the plates, bringing more water, asking if I wanted anything else to drink... I just didn't feel the care you want to feel eating out somewhere. Hope the owner / manager sees. Will come back sometime and try again to see if it's a consistent issue.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPQDdTzB_27kVawKu9G0jAbi1h_m0luszfJe5YW&fid=0x0:0x1e49bab05c66116c"],"When":"2023-8-14"},{"Name":"Frances Torres","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWW5Hv49QyUd0tzfirSnNxCfr7BBsJHZ8ToeL86V4tPrquxKFaGXQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Ordered delivery from here for the first time today. I called just to check on the order. The employee who answered the call was very kind and gave me an ETA for the delivery.

My order arrived perfectly. The delivery employee was nice and friendly. Food is extremely delicious and flavourful. The dishes were not cold and the naan and rice not stale.

Fantastic food and awesome service. Highly recommend.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Yasmine Esmail","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWEZXBMNTPF4jvg42VCs7awd7M64MsfZxN-AdLy-sBCNVAIaJYSAg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The food is amazing. We had lamb kabob, Amritsari kulcha and butter chicken.  It was amazing. The set ice was great too. Very friendly and very welcoming  we will surely go back there.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPbwCHNs5zajDHigc6JF02w_-XsAjqzeF0b0kV3&fid=0x0:0x1e49bab05c66116c"],"When":"2024-3-29"},{"Name":"Souparno Bandyopadhyay","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUuCmVH2mv_B0Bnwyt-4L46dIFgiFVTDV9cKvZ2hdJ2RLLkzO9WWw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Buffet is well priced.

Lot of their menu item’s closely resemble how they’re served in India. Which is good for those seeking authentic taste.

Choley bhature and samosas are my go to.

Tandoori chicken could be better but not bad.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Harsimran Singh Arora","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUeV5nBddl87-hPty9lULHuNsEV2sCet-xl41J3Ed5ab4jE70h2xA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great restaurant! The service was excellent, and the staff was super friendly. The food was tasty, and the people were really nice.  You can tell this place is run by genuinely good people who care about their customers. Highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Star Forbes","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVX3bxa6epj-Pmj6Ysk7djR6GPyFN2Nb3oWlupv9ZY8ucFacX7F=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Food was incredible the calamari was the best I've ever had..beat out some 5 star restaurants even. The taziki needs some work but the batter was amazing and squid tender. The platter for 2 combo one was delicious 😋 large portions enough for another meal. We will be back for sure!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOcseKveiRS0TQicvgRksF3wM4fgUNOqn_2VpPt&fid=0x0:0xf5cb376f8ad99a7e"],"When":"2024-11-19"},{"Name":"Angela Longo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWY1oq49pKa6hIgCWasLoQyfZXLAxCQ6hu--JV9EUi6xd7-tSw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"We had a double celebration, but when I called the restaurant, I only acknowledged my daughter’s birthday. It was our first time at this Greek restaurant, and we were quite excited to go there. I reserved the table over the phone. Whoever answered the phone was kind; nothing negative to say. I asked where to park, and the lady gave me the directions. When we finally went to have dinner, our server took a little bit of time to show up. My son was already there waiting for us, so he knew where we had to sit. When the server came after a while, her demeanor was not what I was expecting. It’s possible that we got her on a bad day, but she was seriously down, and we had to wait almost until our dinner was over for her to warm up. The food was okay. We ordered calamari and spanakopita for appetizers, and for entrees, we had shrimp souvlaki with pita bread,  salmon souvlaki, and my kids had chicken souvlaki. My daughter found the rice bland, while the shrimps were good. There is street parking in front of the restaurant, and you can park at the back only after 5 p.m.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPeRPnf1VYzzb39CpNn_Ei4uu082NkYwEEQEQSJ&fid=0x0:0xf5cb376f8ad99a7e"],"When":"2024-12-3"},{"Name":"Naser","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU0-YQ8zU5RxMjX7Szhrzpzf3k8mT3TPmCIoVpC7Yu8SS5YsZfI=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is one of the best in Maple Ridge. Kind of home made food !
All the food we tried  were really good and l found them  similar to Persian cuisine.
I like the relaxing environment inside which is designed by lots of plants and light blue color.
I went there with  my wife and the kiddos.  We tried for the appetizer the combo1  but forgot to take photo .for dinner we tried combo number 1 . For dinner l chose combo dinner 1 which l loved its Lamb Chops . Steak & Scallops was tasty too as l tried some from my wife order. its good to know that some of them are similar to dinner combo 1.
In general l liked every thing from food, environment, and Friendly staff!
Will definitely come back here with family . Thanks","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPjDUXMTkD3UsznFEVyVi7G2un72yWT86h34I5P&fid=0x0:0xf5cb376f8ad99a7e"],"When":"2023-2-15"},{"Name":"Cameron Appleby","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIfK7DVoNWzY4Tr2axkV9NzU-d_f97Lv-kg87iMyzH8Sw9NTw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had a very enjoyable dinner here. We were a large party, but all food came at the same time and was very hot and fresh. We enjoyed the saganaki as an appetizer, and had the calamari dinner. Well battered and delicious, the Greek rice and potato were excellent. Wish there was more of the Greek salad it was so good. The home made hummus is also a must try! Only note was the cocktails weren’t the best, but only $7 which is far cheaper than anywhere else! Staff were incredibly friendly and accommodating.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOXkZHyeFHJdmQtM7UAdBKSL17l4fpf_vYafF8K&fid=0x0:0xf5cb376f8ad99a7e"],"When":"2023-8-5"},{"Name":"Alannah Banovac","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUzEi2rC9FWIP0WU-iu4d8hkn6PybBsafilbsJrLsiOYj6Y0u-B=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It was so good!!! Definitely the best Cesar salad and calamari we’ve had in a while.  Our waitress was lovely.  Big restaurant and very festive.  I imagine without Covid it would be packed!!  We will definitely make the drive out again!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPfRljMz-RUso2nOVf_oVfGgJE81zhowA5J751D&fid=0x0:0xf5cb376f8ad99a7e"],"When":"2020-11-24"},{"Name":"Steve Beckett","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLvkyDhleIuENlzBAHj2NCgWKF9hnT3DHRngvRO8uUtvdNAqg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"It's really gone downhill. Prices have gone way up and quality of the food way down.  I ordered the barbecued chicken and pasta and when they brought it to me it had a tiny piece of chicken and a rack of ribs.I said I didn't order the ribs so they took it back, took the ribs off and gave me back the tiny piece of chicken. Then charged me 32 dollars. I left still hungry. Dissapointed","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Faye Cottingham","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV_8s3lDyN2LicCeKEcCn0xxfkQIcL4H-y1ZVypVQd-Da9VXOvP=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Our senior’s group celebrated the 99th birthday of one of our members at this restaurant last evening.  I want to commend Georgina and all the staff for going above and beyond for this event.  From helping us decorate to serving dinner for 20 people and then lighting sparkler’s for our gent’s Birthday cake it was very much appreciated and helped our celebration run smoothly.  All of us were happy with our meals and the service, and the atmosphere was energetic yet relaxed.  Thanks so much to all of you.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOxMd0oFJAQVfkzsYfEq6iCEWf56LIaX5bKybgG&fid=0x0:0xf5cb376f8ad99a7e"],"When":"2024-3-12"},{"Name":"Liam Chubb","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUpaHIWaoaWvNQg7wfzL_wSY3cKRHb5uW8iNsZFFY4VJqmsHCuD=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very friendly staff with very high quality food. I ordered a combo #1, and it came out with a very generous plate of lamb, rice, chicken, Greek salad, dolmades, and more. A perfectly large portion for 2 people. Flavours were very good, and interior atmosphere is also awesome. I would absolutely recommend a trip here.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO-lfnFUONG9uJPndoto7S9fztdh5-N1JsU0Bsa&fid=0x0:0xf5cb376f8ad99a7e"],"When":"2021-9-5"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Divya Prakash","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXNiQrPUZkiYQTnFdP0lhwPK2fJ3DCNtYXc-W7edCuVdf5gJjwD=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I ordered their Raspberry Lemon Cheesecake and it was really disappointing. It was sour, unappetizing and not sweet. I was looking forward to it. Would not order again. Pasta was decent.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPMN1i41zuv-jFmcBrlwaJSZxoBEwb8vdgzuCU2&fid=0x0:0xc63b0c31f63b1714"],"When":"2024-11-27"},{"Name":"Elise Ardizzi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX1tLvG9dk778TfiZNEobPfkCOpjWPfjySchaB-Y7t1mukyJZJB=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The King Caesar Review is here! I am here to rate all the Caesar salads world wide … starting at my home in Vancouver. These rating will be heavily based on the Caesar salad it’s self, and not the other food I ordered. I have been eating Caesar salad’s for the past 20 years and thought it’s about time I get serious about these leafy greens covered in cream sauce. I hope your as excited as I am.

Paliotti’s in Maple Ridge- only one other Italian restaurant to choose from

Dressing: creamy base, with a nice lemon coating, heavy garlic (yum), fresh ground pepper and anchovies. Can’t believe I’m saying this but maybe too much sauce.  Definitely tastes homemade though.
Lettuce: romaine, cold and crisp, however cut too large
Croutons: out of a package
Cheese: questionable? Powdered parm on top but within the dressing a thicker heavier tasting cheese I couldn’t figure out.
Bacon: none- which is honestly how I prefer my Caesar’s. Bacon seems to over power the sauce and texture (to me)

I went to this restaurant after 8 years of my mom passing away with my girlfriend. My mom always ordered penne alla vodka. I was searching all over Maple Ridge and could not find it on the menu. This place seemed the most authentic and warm. We obviously has to order the Caesar salad, but I asked if they could do an alla vodka sauce but on my favourite… Gnocchi!
Soooo tender, sauce missing pancetta but still very good and grateful I got to eat in my moms honour

Overall, very authentic, great service and food came quick. There is a creepy table that you can’t site at with the Mona Lisa looking over you but that’s guna stop us from coming back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNuojeziO4jMgePhjk0PXm2X7mUMU0L7plipgTc&fid=0x0:0xc63b0c31f63b1714"],"When":"2024-7-26"},{"Name":"Jacquelyn Johnston","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLfy_pLzvat08k9FzqYD-5djtqo3UfUv3fLgHw-FhXMEBTZ9A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"My friend and I thought we'd try the Wednesday steak or ribs special for $18.95, misleadingly advertised on the outdoor sign as steak and ribs. We arrived about five o'clock and the place filled up steadily until our section was full.
It was my friend's first time there and she appreciated the quaint atmosphere.
She ordered the honey garlic ribs. I was looking forward to the steak, medium rare.
The complimentary foccacia was delicious.
As I can't eat potatoes, I ordered the caesar salad as a substitute.
We had agreed to share a couple of tasting bites of our entrees but when my steak arrived I was having real difficulty cutting through it.
The ribs were good but the portion of potatoes was very small.
The salad was fine, along with the few bites of vegetables.
Unfortunately our server didn't return until I'd eaten all the veg and most of the salad. I'd finally broken down and tried a bite of the steak but it was so chewy I ended up having to leave it on my side plate.
When she did come back I apologized and asked if she could possibly have it thrown back on the grill for a minute, thinking perhaps the rareness was the problem.
She also apologized and said other people had complained and that she'd use her discount.
She brought me a new steak that wasn't much better, to the point that two thirds of the way in my jaw was too sore to continue chewing so I left the remainder on the plate.
When the bill came, she had comp'd the special completely, which was more than I expected and much appreciated.
I wish I'd read the reviews before we went and am reluctant to give a negative review but I see I'm not alone.
If you want a decent steak at that price point I recommend The Reach or The Meridian Arms.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Fred Pisciuneri","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLJa1gaoTtY22fdDEqMPm2WTbr81qQ1auvM_vNGloxSwNkGJA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"My friend and I decided to tray this place based on their sign promoting steak or rib dinner
the hostess was very friendly and seated us right away the waitress was also very friendly and took our order promptly
I had the steak special  and minestrone soup
my friend ordered the steak special
the soup was very good one of the better minestrone soups Ive had in a restaurant
the steak on the other hand was very tough I could not chew it and barely cut thru it it was very grizzly and veiny
the waitress came by to ask how the food was so I told her she was very apologetic and said she would have another made up
I had maybe a couple of bites that I could chew thru on the first one
the second one was even worse
I stopped fighting with n it and when the waitress came back I told her
my friend was also struggling with his and got about half of it down after cutting out n odds and end pieces
the waitress apologized again
I felt bad for her and told her it wasn't her fault
she offered us free deserts , as I don't eat dessert due to sugar issues i declined and my friend also declined
she brought the check and charged full amount for everything
when I questioned it she said she would get someone after a few min this lady came out and immediately started in on me with a nasty attitude as if i was trying to pull one over on her
I told her I didn't eat the steak it was sent back to the kitchen
out of 3 steaks 2 and half were sent back
she said again with a snarl this the bill
I walk with a cane as I am disabled so I went to stand up to get my wallet out .she told the girl "take his picture . take his picture loud enough for the other guests to hear in order to embarrass me in front of the whole restaurant. They took my picture and disappeared
I stood there for about 5 min waiting but no one showed up so I left

It really is disappointing to have to   deal with someone like that when the rest of the staff was great . I would gladly have taken a discount and an apology for the bad steaks
I would like the owner to contact me to make amends and I sure hope its not the same lady
either way I would not go back there as a patron as i don't need that stress . I just wanted a nice relaxing dinner","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Karen Norrie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIM0HHV52XWj0DuqS582jUGxsQfKKT4CXIFpksBWsK_BlOh4Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Made a reservation for 20 people a few weeks ago.  Called Sunday to confirm one more person, so 21 people at 6pm for Tuesday.  Arrived on time.  We did get a first drink each.  Took over an hour to get second drink, even when a few of us asked.  We were told it would take another 10 minutes for waitress to come to table, it took longer.  That was the last time it was offered during our evening.  We did ask more than once and waitress never came back.  Other than taking our initial orders and delivering food we were completely ignored.  Table full of empties, what a mess.  No one ever came to clean our table.  Plates were picked up but never any glasses and never any water refills.   We had brought in a cake and those dishes were never picked up. Our time there took 3.5 hours.  It took over an hour to get our bills.  We had school aged children and 3 women in their eighties.  They waited, we all waited over an hour for the bill.  We could not understand why.  One waitress said their machine was 30 years old and it would take awhile.  I saw and watched other tables in restaurant get great prompt service.  Their bills came in a timely matter.  They did not wait over an hour for their bill.
Their tables were cleared upon finishing their meal. We were blatantly ignored. To top off such a rude experience, the waitress hand wrote a 20% forced gratuity on every bill.  We had no prompt service.  That wasn't offered.  Shady business.  Very clear we were ignored as there was a guaranteed 20% tip from us, no matter what little service we got.  They do not get the 20% guarantee from the smaller tables. Very disappointed with paliottis, our group certainly won't be back. We have had many of these gatherings at many different places and have not met such disregard for our dining experience.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMmYvF6Ijp2OEyDwedI_Puw9G4J-z-wlnNj47RO&fid=0x0:0xc63b0c31f63b1714"],"When":"2024-3-13"},{"Name":"Meghan Klassen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKD-XbXwb6aAq-xlNjuC8BO0xaag0Zq5PBhSx8MCP7PI-YuvQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Services is excellent, but the food is pretty disappointing. Lacked flavour, just plain boxed pasta that you are paying a pretty high price for.
I had the veal Neptune, had very very small amount of seafood and small extremely thin pieces of veal. Pasta had hardly any sauce on it. I dont think we will be returning.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Urszula","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIfU5PKcg9JLueSHqTZ2mNz35scjm_8tfESVV6QKIPy8_jxxg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Decided to try the Tuesday dinner special with my family of four for my birthday; was told that because I didn't  have a reservation they could not accommodate us for dinner for 30 minutes. There was no one waiting for a table and there were numerous tables empty; parking lot was half full. Very disappointing and will not be returning.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Danny Y","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX8eoyUE6az-FmQo7i2mVq5z64Ow48sgKu1EmLZc0zWWN6DMy5asw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The OG Paliotti’s. 35 years and 4 restaurants as a family business for Italian means they must be doing something right. This location is the original; don’t get it confused with the one 3.5km west (also same family but different style).

The food here is great. Portions are generous and they don’t skimp out on the good stuff. That first zing of balsamic vinegar and EVOO with the perfectly toasted focaccia is strangely memorable.

Service was good and suited the occasion.

The only dislike was the desserts. We found that the mains and pasta were really good but the desserts were ok. Worth trying though for sure (esp. the tiramisu).

Nice and cozy, home style feel. Will definitely come again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMc-P5DZTgChPWA0vAaDAPrPbQHg27i08CXYcsR&fid=0x0:0xc63b0c31f63b1714"],"When":"2023-9-15"}]

He is the epitome of great service. Always polite friendly and accurate. He never lets the coffee cup run dry.
Food selection at White Spot is not very extensive. In my opinion breakfast is the best thing they have to offer dinner and lunch menu is mediocre at best.. [{"Name":"Kim Rhindress","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUGV1bXDBhXJzPDI9KSedz8MMWu5WbOPshbJnxk8ecoAvwrcRUU=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A local gem!
Small and cosy spot with divine Pho!
We ordered the rare beef with brisket, no noodles but extra veggies and it was absolutely perfect! Lots of tender beef, fresh Thai basil and the broth was delish!!
The owner is so friendly and you can tell she puts LOVE into every dish. Highly recommended!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO9Rt-CHtSutsJN3oXG1vthiP_jA2MrajpiIr8R&fid=0x0:0x55b7c46565840c3c"],"When":"2024-8-25"},{"Name":"Jioh Kim","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUKSWfpbNYcWQsWaiXfEMb52v-8T7Q_sZwrESiKgHFQas3hVA414Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We stopped by on our way into the city. The warm soup was much needed after a few nights of camping in the cold. Huge portions of food, the bun bo hue had soooo much meats but also variety of meats so it was very fun to eat. Everything was very good! Highly recommend!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPADTtkpSie1_AQsFEiCONH0NMXjhygogJv1pph&fid=0x0:0x55b7c46565840c3c"],"When":"2024-10-2"},{"Name":"Tyler Hazelman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVaOeOfMrKb93Y_IutfdRfQ5RnvS47tYfW1M-2iSLOIvO-Sl_d1=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Song is the epidemy of your local mom and pop shop. Staff is always quick and attentive; by your 2nd or 3rd visit they'll usually have ur order down by heart. Food is reasonably priced, Song makes quite possibly the best broth in the lower mainland, its my personal favorite anyway. I've been a repeat customer for years, Song really makes u feel like home. I Highly recommend this spot! Rain or shine Song will take care of you =)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNVfYB3FtJA6xutB0TT28UgND8WPkeYBdJjYpNX&fid=0x0:0x55b7c46565840c3c"],"When":"2024-8-9"},{"Name":"Patricia Yogi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVjlKd9mThgf7cTYIXLMXbilhcd8ljSFZMn37lWe0i8h43OGeOavQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had lunch at Pho Song Restaurant recently, and it was an exceptional experience from start to finish. The food was not only well-served but the portions were incredibly generous! Each dish was bursting with flavor and made with fresh ingredients. However, the service was the friendliest I've ever encountered and very fast. The staff went above and beyond to ensure we felt welcome and taken care of throughout our meal. I highly recommend Pho Song Restaurant to anyone craving delicious food and exceptional service!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPk5Zq3xFT_PAHSymKc9pinl9STDVc9qFuCDSog&fid=0x0:0x55b7c46565840c3c"],"When":"2024-4-14"},{"Name":"Joanne Antoniak","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWTQwhPcO13h_HhVjJVUrwpHjU5MeesKhPrxV5pA1ymdZ1edFkY=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Great Little hole in the wall pho spot on lougheed highway.
Decor was ok, shop was clean, service was great; and the pho was amazing.
The salad wraps we ordered to go with ... were ok ...meh
Best pho I've had in ridge so far.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPhWS4ifms9Wlo8KzFoxAnR7YYa8he9iWJbP38K&fid=0x0:0x55b7c46565840c3c"],"When":"2024-5-22"},{"Name":"Chris B","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKEm2JgFRxD6_hP2n3YeBkcnvE01P3EXsVOtV_iNzZjYGK0ng=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The broth was excellent. Had a great meal at a decent price. The waitress was exceptional. We ordered a Pho that was a little spicier than anticipated and she without hesitation suggested that she could take half the broth out and add less spicy broth. The thing that really made it amazing is she suggested it and did it immediately with a no problem at all attitude. Thank you for the great service.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Steven Olmstead","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWtGPLsUg7ybhRCsA9-VeVYuyaFqArSeyzqddnDm9gdPpsZ3M0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Stopped in for lunch recently after a morning at Golden Ears Park.  Were quite hungry from walking so ordered salad roll in addition to lemongrass chicken pho and Bún Bò Huế.  We soon found out we ordered too much, as the soups were very good portions.  The salad roll was just okay, being rather dry.  The soups however, were excellent.  They came out fast, were piping hot and had a generous amount of meat and noodles.  he broth was delicious!  Will definitely return next time we're in Maple Ridge","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN03LG0PddWL1XrtkM7t1WUeLHzku9k0zMK2YiR&fid=0x0:0x55b7c46565840c3c"],"When":"2024-9-21"},{"Name":"Judy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVNU7X0Zh-GjDXqejNfoqiI2QGASul0OZwrdH-FpCgF4pWayvIz=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We like the mixed meat board. Its so good !
The staffs are friendly and price is reasonable👍❤️","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPHlBydWrm8-OeIXOfkxV4CZxmqstQ1occGbtcN&fid=0x0:0x55b7c46565840c3c"],"When":"2024-7-19"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Hamid Salim","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKI3TG9oSjOLechuar9EkdFNIAYsOe-RKsY9UYMVUD2QQtKMg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My wife and I love Thai foods but is hard to find a good one. We discovered this restaurant by accident and are so glad we did dine there. It was an hour before closing on Sunday evening. The lady who served us could not be more helpful. The quality of food was excellent, ingredients were screaming freshness. Contrary to most south Asian foods that come very sweet or oily, couple of dishes we had were just right on both. We definitely will go again. The portions were large, the best option is to go with few family members or friends and get different dishes to share.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPDDAqHd6PEdf1IxqNLj95dUMVHdum-IDrrt3aP&fid=0x0:0x8ec85bbf77885a95"],"When":"2023-7-29"},{"Name":"Swimming Lion","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIoNuKoBPU8hDsJrOBlEDRPQawlWHi3C9rUvrLYtz7paaZM0w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Price was ok
Atmosphere was good and nice setting
Good services too

Food is average ….it’s so difficult to find good Thai food in Greater Vancouver area😞

- The curry was too watery and meat were cut too big
- The Pineapple fried rice was mostly plain rice with tomato sauce; didn’t really see much pineapple nor meat
- Skewers were good and interesting how they serve sticky rice with skewers
- Most of the dishes serve with a bowl of rice
- Taste overall was ok but the way the food was chopped in bigger chunk not delicate as expected","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM3ETZLMaeUoUPqW_YrVYHAScUus2S2D48rgIIH&fid=0x0:0x8ec85bbf77885a95"],"When":"2023-5-22"},{"Name":"Jamak Golshani","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWUj2LK0XJaxGCkMdV1Y3vwaPy3axo29-O-pu7Kb7eqy9PgvRrN=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We have been to the Langley location and the food was amazing so we decide to try this location. We were not disappointed. I personally like the atmosphere here better than Langley.

The service is topnotch and the food is very tasty. The only caution I have is it could get pricy. Three course meal for four will cost you around $200.

Lastly, get a reservation to be on the safe side. It gets packed pretty quick around dinner time.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNeEnFBHRuCn4CmfTZBtnCs_xifAmpzSOjsqq17&fid=0x0:0x8ec85bbf77885a95"],"When":"2022-11-13"},{"Name":"Simon Park","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKARXZijowQGioSxiOMCg-EzyxEm1UrGAfGF9hiOguYSh8sPA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I'll be honest : the staff are nice, but the food is nothing fancy. It can be a bit crowded and noisy, but overall, the atmosphere is okay. Recommended if you're looking for a nearby Thai restaurant.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMnkyNPnq0O3qvk_sAJ33P6HSWWB7uSABjjGRTS&fid=0x0:0x8ec85bbf77885a95"],"When":"2024-5-26"},{"Name":"Pramod Neel","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXw41ptGAFzVooQILRjvGPIfC76VhEZGfXXgi0sQ9YlceSXmckPQQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Second time around and they didn't disappoint in terms of the food or the service. The appetizing starters (chicken satay, veg n chicken spring rolls) set the ball rolling and whet our appetites for the main course to follow. The mains were pineapple fried rice with yellow curry, pad Thai, Thai chicken fried rice. All the dishes were one better than the other. The spice levels were accurate. The entire family gorged down the food, which left no space for any dessert (a promise to myself for next time 😉). Will recommend this place to anyone who would like to taste some delectable Thai cuisine. Kudos to the chef 👏.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPm076KnKc1LXEYq-rBglmNyeMpiKg75uMnWIZT&fid=0x0:0x8ec85bbf77885a95"],"When":"2022-5-15"},{"Name":"Nat A","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWnjKr4KNFAObzj2bIvH9BRInxwKsSvEg1PM25bKfvhxtWZTWHoog=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Edit/Update: I recently came here and had there Khao Soi soup. It was rich in flavor and I loved the crunchy noodles on top. Large portion size compared to other local Thai restaurants. Loved their spicy calamari with the green sauce dip. Delicious! Good service again too.

Great Pad Thai lunch special for $15! I ordered the Pad Thai with shrimp. The portion size of the noodles was big compared to other Thai restaurants. The flavour of the noodles was good. It came only with 3 pieces of shrimp but the shrimp was a good size, fresh and cooked well. It was served with a small bowl of soup and salad on the main plate. For $15 it was a really good deal. I had only eaten here once before and did not like the sweet and sour seafood dish. This time around was much better. Servers were friendly. They have nice decor as well. I'd definitely come back to try their other lunch specials.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMK59KB_qry66bGbsBTvvhsqYzW1DyXMI7GuqeD&fid=0x0:0x8ec85bbf77885a95"],"When":"2022-10-13"},{"Name":"Eston Stone","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVZf50HNdIFLNy3MPJ7T0z_SKBvprsk5TrIt59f6By2jLBx8sq5rg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Really great Thai food and drinks! The restaurant's atmosphere is nice and all the staff were very friendly. The food is a little pricey but the portion size is large, I definitely recommend sharing a couple dishes. The service was great even on a packed Friday night our food showed up in 15 minutes!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOgdldUNaXuuWrqnnYdQGKILmS4cUpDiO-ShwOv&fid=0x0:0x8ec85bbf77885a95"],"When":"2023-5-22"},{"Name":"Shaz Currie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ0UI1cdx8QlB8EQtgs3_0gzmuw9WKyTApAk7qnPExS0XdLhw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I just wanted to share the recent experience that our family had at this location of Ban Chok Dee. We just celebrated a milestone birthday that went off without a hitch. Lynn the restaurant manager went well above and beyond to make the evening and dining experience FANTASTIC. Not only did she make special accommodations for our family that were quite difficult to work with she also made sure that the entire experience from arranging the evening, presenting sample menus that would please the family was ready the day of. Lynn is a gem and so are her staff that she has handpicked! The food was fantastic and everyone was impressed by the quality and selection. We are a pretty particular bunch when it comes to our meals and not one complaint was had. I would not hesitate to recommend Ban Chok Dee in Maple Ridge to anyone who is looking to book a venue for a special event. The only reason I gave 4 stars for the atmosphere was that it was actually quite hot in the restaurant and the AC wasn't operating in the dining area. Other than that we had no complaints! Lynn now has life long customers from my entire family all because of how she took care of us. Thank you Lynn!!","Images":null,"When":""}]

I was a walk in and ordered a combo for 1 bbq pork fried rice, ginger beef, and sweet n sour pork from David. I had a special request and he nailed the entire order. All the meat is tender, ginger beef was crunchy and not chewy, fried rice was perfect. Sweet n sour pork was good size bites and not all breading. Lastly the egg rolls were also perfect. I absolutely will be returning and highly recommend👍

***UPDATE***DO NOT PARK IN THE LOT OR YOU WILL GET A $126 TICKET BY DIAMOND PARKING SERVICES HIDDEN LOW ON YOUR WINDSHIELD OUT OF SIGHT***","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOl6SWT2PyyAb9IOf-JuQ8_27sGSMM3clk3j2fl&fid=0x0:0x8da2ae946ca6723b"],"When":"2023-8-15"},{"Name":"Alexia Sarvan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVc6JDa1yYfq0nUgWFW8ECuapxVZ66hckQHzZsZmHnjPE9Lhhnx=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My Husband and I were craving chow mein over the weekend but didn’t feel like driving to pick up at our usual place (that doesn’t deliver to our location) so we decided to order delivery directly from Kitchen on the Ridge. We ordered on Saturday night at around 5:30pm and it was delivered right on time (within an hour). We ordered chicken chow mein, beef & black bean sauce crispy chow mein and almond chicken. It was all very delicious and fresh. Portions were huge so we had tons of leftovers which was great. We will definitely order from Kitchen on the Ridge again!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN3nhAJrBFqNb0GuQgVRj9TiqJ_B9gN4IODhwew&fid=0x0:0x8da2ae946ca6723b"],"When":"2023-2-6"},{"Name":"David Dyck","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI5xjijpXaZs2STs6BFRe-cNEGv-QQjprJx3-f3GHeEQh2Z4g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"We ordered veggie chow mein, beef and broccoli and sweet and sour pork.  The chow mein had no flavor whatsoever, the beef and broccoli was absolutely disgusting and tasted more like fish than beef. The sweet and sour pork was edible, I’d give it maybe a 5/10.

Overall, would definitely not recommend.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Alex Deagle","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK4172m11rBMIloP_3iH8GRIdcve4rXahqQ4ex_Npkmxc6mnQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best Chinese in maple ridge! Super friendly family run business. My 97 year old mom is from Hong Kong and loves this place. Thank you for your great food and service!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Evan Meloche","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI2cfpbCLahRZZfYL915tBomhuHC8EgGDfGSULODUyhGvNO9Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"The only positive aspect was that the food tasted decent and the doordash service/driver was excellent.

Our biggest problem was that multiple different food items were stored in the same container, not just as a way to save containers, but to hide the portion size. We had to call our doordash driver to make sure he delivered all the food because we thought we were missing half of it.

Everything we ordered was under portioned and left us still hungry afterwards. Compared to the portion size, the prices are nearly double what I would be willing to pay again.

Putting different food items in the same container is also a problem for cross-contamination. You never know if someone has a life threatening allergy (or even religious values about certain foods) and mixing food unnecessarily drastically increases the risk of contamination.","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Terrance Ballinger","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVfXPM0VnVW25XGLTurN53qTTrBcGu0EFRlRUVkF2_Fa_j4hjxG=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Certainly! Here’s a five-star review for Mongolian Grill:

---

⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️

I recently dined at Mongolian Grill and had a wonderful experience. The staff were incredibly friendly, and the service was top-notch.

The food was delicious, with a fantastic variety of flavors that left my taste buds delighted. Although the restaurant is quite cozy and a bit on the small side, which made it feel a little cramped, the overall quality of the meal and the warm hospitality more than made up for it.

Highly recommend for a flavorful dining experience!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM2mMubkSKrNR2fD4DRvRK_3dWMMstC84-YOzj-&fid=0x0:0x7608d6d146192205"],"When":"2024-6-8"},{"Name":"Srikantha Kalaghatta","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX7kV3vSmU11E2VJr6yMSYBtHLByJ47CPuwfOKoc_5xVBiEfsZQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"This place felt like a food maze with too many rules to navigate. Time determines food prices – after 3 PM, bowls cost a buck more. Sharing? Nope. And if your bowl hits 700 grams, cue extra charges! It's like a hunger puzzle!

Both veg and non-veg bowls cost the same until 700 grams. In what world is that fair? Also, how do you know the weight without a scale? I played it safe, staying probably under 400 grams. Other spots weigh your meal, fair and square. Here? It’s a guessing game: lose out on food or pay extra, no middle ground.

The food setup's odd too. Sauce at the start? We pour sauce on food, not dunk food in! At 19 CAD (with tax) for a bowl, the price felt steep for what we got. Plus, two bland spring rolls tagged along, probably apologizing for existing. Soggy and off, a first in my Asian eats.

Kudos to the front desk girl, trying despite the chaos. But with food and setup off-kilter, staff magic can only do so much. Have other customers of this place been to legit Mongolian spots? Because once they do, they won't return here.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN98XPVrDauZs2Eb8_PhhTXnBDfkcXFO2PdflHT&fid=0x0:0x7608d6d146192205"],"When":"2023-12-29"},{"Name":"Naser","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU0-YQ8zU5RxMjX7Szhrzpzf3k8mT3TPmCIoVpC7Yu8SS5YsZfI=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Nice experience for our family. Specially kids liked it to choose the spice and ingredients by themselves and then they BBQ it in front of them .
Food and service were good and the staff are so nice and friendly.
It's Chinese food but prepared by Mongolian Style BBQ.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPh0iaY_NAe0T5SIYyo67RH9QhofrlHOYTk6cwb&fid=0x0:0x7608d6d146192205"],"When":"2024-4-8"},{"Name":"Robert Ash","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLJQAeP8ruG-UCqNM_45mQCHPv-HxgUjGGoOGCaA0SeoNx2rg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"One of the best places to eat in Maple Ridge. Everyone knows how expensive everything is nowadays, but the food you get for the price is unmatched. 20 dollars at McDonald's or Burger King and you're probably still hungry. 20 bucks here and you're eating good and you'll be stuffed. Please bring one to Mission.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"ClayPhoenix4","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVelJECogE7AFzsG2ZmzVGlq92_4MqwMY_QK6n2nHeBRJeGCXg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"There is no need to sweat it out when you are filling up your bowl to be cooked (like some other Mongolie grill) restaurants and watch what the scale says and then find out how much you are getting charged when they cook it for you.
Just simply fill up a desired portion and pay the set price....
There is a max amount you can fill the bowl so no need to stomp down the bowl, so keep it reasonable. The plate comes with a scoop of rice and 2 small spring rolls.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Marion Kryger","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIRJCI44a0FudyaE5-DQb5xvo62PPzbT_PEXoI4RjcsAVnykA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I ordered the Wong tong miso soup it was so good nice and light on the stomach and very flavourful perfect for a nice cold day to warm you up so glad I decided to go  definitely can’t wait to go again !!!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Richard Robson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUBpP_J13Sb1Q0viZ5CNU61C6icASh3TXtZU86rpp6mmT1VYcGT=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The wife and I went here for lunch on my birthday. The food in the picture is from the small bowl. We could have crammed more food into the bowl before we had them cook it! But it was soo much food for a great price! All the ingredients were super fresh and delicious. The staff were awesome. We will be going back soon and will probably become regulars at this location!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNPhijGTgM_1tSKaalC4Y1pG1PnqyGFdX8QtFJz&fid=0x0:0x7608d6d146192205"],"When":"2020-9-6"},{"Name":"Roezell Riggs","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW4WjKBpexg6A7saNdE6W7ow6w_FZutLr4uG3a_MxnBEUNimQk3=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"It was my first time coming here  and Mongolian grill restaurants are my favourite type of restaurants, so I was coming in with a bit of high standards.
The service was great for Tuesday night, a few people working and they were very helpful in explaining the process.. In this restaurant,  they have different bowl sizes with set prices to them, as oppose to some places that strictly go by weight.
Their sauce selection was decent, but they didn't have honey garlic which is my favourite option. I'm just happy they didn't have pre-made sauces like the Mongolian grill in Whistler!
They also didn't have salmon, so I ended up having a  big bowl of vegetables and noodles. I was recently informed they have white fist as an option though.
I enjoyed the food very much, their veggie selection was a wider spread than I'm used to seeing which was great for me.
Another thing that was different and I wasn't expecting, was their rice portion was small, like a spoonful. I enjoy rice over noodles  I didn't want the noodles but when they mentioned that the rice doesn't come in a large bowl  and just on the side, I added noodles. I enjoyed the change, it was a good experience and I'll go back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPqvLCrXJxMX5BLAdArSO7hFm9rXgYPb6Y0F8uH&fid=0x0:0x7608d6d146192205"],"When":"2023-9-12"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Swimming Lion","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIoNuKoBPU8hDsJrOBlEDRPQawlWHi3C9rUvrLYtz7paaZM0w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Small but decent  Indian restaurant, servers are very attentive and polite.
Tandoori chicken a bit salty but the cashew chicken was super tasty! Tender and juicy!
Naan was a bit oily can see the oil on them  but taste was good
The place not new but it’s clean and well kept
Free parking in front of the restaurant
We went on a Saturday evening it wasn’t busy","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOngNpakrpCU9lE8Jnhi169dYin4_pfyngASOhX&fid=0x0:0xaa8e4af36f7afe06"],"When":"2024-7-11"},{"Name":"Naser","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU0-YQ8zU5RxMjX7Szhrzpzf3k8mT3TPmCIoVpC7Yu8SS5YsZfI=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We tried here on weekend.
I liked their Zaika grill.
I asked for medium spicy but still a little too much for me, but my daughter liked it. So it depends  😊

I also liked their garlic and potato Naan but had better ones at other Indian restaurants.
In general l liked it but cant give a five star comparing other Indian restaurant.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNkICAFxvo2a3UdGR_gujmjVKYeLqDdkZF2xbdK&fid=0x0:0xaa8e4af36f7afe06"],"When":"2023-4-3"},{"Name":"D L","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKhLImqrHTCGIXoFB4QEyr6EtuDMQdMBNlk7VTCBFhqqz4PtQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Tried this place the other day.  Decent food even though portions are a tad small.   The place needs a reno or something though.   Half seemed closed off and not ready for business,  and they had to turn on lights when we came in.   Not really any decor either.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"JR","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXVKZKvgEPjAseb-WsTOz6PNSLNr0d7N3-5NKC3mCdy_klfyim5=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Go to Maple Leaf for the same tasting food but better value by 100x. Dined in with a big group as a work party last week and thought it was great. My takeout order tonight was a scam. Thanks for a few crumbles of meat in my butter chicken and 2 prawns in my vindaloo. My friends and I are so full! And their ‘3 pieces’ per order of naan is 3/4 of one at most other places around here.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ron Chan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU4C9fuu3Pgu102q3bAxHKivkiOQqwqKjJditkVdy4zIZ628gCE7g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"the naan bread here is phenomenal, it is very light and crispy.  there coconut fish curry is awesome too.  overall quality of food here is excellent, better than most places around town.  service was attentive staff was great.  cleaneness of the restaurant is top notch too.  water jugs were covered, everything was clean, water was cold which most places dont provide.  also there chicken wings are so crispy, must try!!

only request I would like to make is to add butter chicken to your lunch buffet lineup, also to turn on the tray warmers to keep the food hot.

will definitely come back and try other stuff and if you can let me know that you added butter chicken to your lunch buffet, I will come back and try it right away.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPkhSukGH0rjwOnmw1HPBDei-8ZKsWF7e5e-jVY&fid=0x0:0xaa8e4af36f7afe06"],"When":"2019-10-23"},{"Name":"Vasisht Raghavendra","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJJdqlfXhrv4xWlObHOUik-BEmjW2vxVvFad9PSosG433WUa8GN=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Only customers at the restaurant. The restaurant seemed dark and has no windows but the good food made up for this.

Easter Day dinner:
Chicken Tandoori 🍗
Garlic Naan 🫓
Paneer Methi Malai 😋
Saffron Rice 🍚
Lassi 🥛

The food was delicious and sufficient.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO7nkpTrUyj4v2mbx-wMcipy5vqxf-X0REGSVnU&fid=0x0:0xaa8e4af36f7afe06"],"When":"2023-4-12"},{"Name":"Sazzad Hossain","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK5JzPg_HbQTCfL-RL2N4qcAmAyjkRuMRE7Ps-o51NovewMwA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Ordered Lamb Biriyani, Lamb Rogan Josh and Fish Pakura. All the items were really tasty. Highly recommended for the people looking for Halal options in Maple Ridge area in BC. Only Lamb is the halal meat they offer.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPcV2XFN_Qkdu5sMV55TqaHPwSScMUF-7SNCM-n&fid=0x0:0xaa8e4af36f7afe06"],"When":"2022-6-18"},{"Name":"S Hakimi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV_mvQPAHA_s1zbUyQEvtTu2ZAXWBRTh_r11OfqKURKSyvFvSVu=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Order three vegetables Pakoras for an Iftari event, it was so embarrassing they were all bitter and burned. The day after I went in person at first the front desk agreed to give three meals proper Pakoras. I asked I got that for an event I don’t need that much Pakora she was rude and said can only give me one meal of Pakora I refused and told her I am going to write an review she was it’s ok do whatever you want to!

Zero honesty in business, attitude, and food quality is really bad I wouldn’t bother going again. And not suggesting to anyone.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNvlzWx-40c8XkJGPrISyBXGfmaDIciv39qcVa5&fid=0x0:0xaa8e4af36f7afe06"],"When":"2023-4-11"}]

The portions were good and the food was delicious!  I will definitely be ordering from Shinobi Downtown again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPyUO7bctF6H7ZruH5S-6COzmV-tYesIMADp00g\u0026fid=0x0:0xd638f7427ec7a285"],"When":"2024-10-18"},{"Name":"Jessica Clark-Roesch","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWDV5_0TU2jFjH8aZU9TGAOogV1cB5enHy4mAkM9us0VcJlObKj=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I come here a few times a week because of Christine , Jennifer and the quality of the food!!!! I cannot say enough good things about their customer service and how well these ladies take care of me as a customer ! This place is superior to the rest of the Sushi businesses in town and surrounding areas! Not only do you get treated with the best customer service but the price of the food is incredible and actual food is amazing, always fresh, delicious and looks very appealing. I am never disappointed and refuse to go anywhere else. Even if I have to drive from home in Abby to grab some lunch or dinner! Its worth every penny and mile!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Bill Wilson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVrLDUKCB9KhwKlqIkCcXUiASMuWECjsxURVB66vsZhnoGGXEJCJQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"First trip in since the fire. Was hoping they would have added cushions. Take out is better organization and u have seating to wait for order, no more going to the back and lingering. Food still good! 😊 Recommend👍","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Fiorella Vallejo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW1SnfWM9cmXxEh39oA3RY-NSjUql11rlkIUXcbtqnf0ItMOAys=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My family’s favourite restaurant in downtown Maple Ridge! Christine and all the servers are very attentive and lovely!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMrW1IRrxRL9lGqDvY6T8p-DuyH_8CNET0s5wQE\u0026fid=0x0:0xd638f7427ec7a285"],"When":"2024-9-29"},{"Name":"Marcos Garcia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVrIx99K0w17o1_jz1_EhQur2HjhBKK7Idj_Dw1mjT3aruNUbguXA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great food and atmosphere. [{"Name":"Christina S","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUdydYglvNyOpnSWRlj0BJK2ybimMfTHSRhBJJTYlKFntnMOLg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The BEST Donair in town.
Yummy food, Generous portions and Friendly staff. My kids love them and can have this everyday.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN8e0yI0sFJrQbOdwmaXaejLy9fk38FiA56hzIA&fid=0x0:0xfb33fdae02e5bf7a"],"When":"2024-10-26"},{"Name":"Riley Dew","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVn12scCRP84PcL2aXqjrQ-Gzhn4dmEG55boPfaeZsLV-yvS6x6tA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great Place, I always get their chicken Donair and they're always so nice, fast, and talkative! Love em","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNr5y9hvR06U53SWTyXo4peRW5QDUg_gCTO3fOo&fid=0x0:0xfb33fdae02e5bf7a"],"When":"2024-10-19"},{"Name":"Mohammad_s Zare","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX0zvPgAwUepTiYIAUBS1yK_ACR_lBIpMWJx1RjPIgsoDnibPMz=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"We had a terrible experience at Donair Affair. We ordered chicken donairs, and they were absolutely awful. The chicken tasted off, and all five of us who ate them ended up feeling sick and even food poisoned. This was completely unacceptable. It’s clear that food safety and quality are not a priority here. Avoid this place at all costs if you value your health.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"K G","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKLRJOKOgZDz1CBS_3JgMD2bbfgt9VUhdDiTO5bGhr1q48i_A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Have been here many times and it's been pretty good, but this time I did not have a great experience.   I was charge 3 dollars for cheese.  I wasn't even aware you couldn't get feta on your salad or donair without being charged for it.  The 2 ladies in the store were also quite rude and rushing us even though it was only 4pm and nobody else was in there.  Food this time also didn't taste that great.  Lots of fat on the chicken. They lost a customer today.   Will not be back.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kevin Stumph","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXd238p66NEmxHSmbV2C7QO5xlHen-3NKfO9jCkC2Ap03tp8_Zn=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"If you have it in you to have an affair, have one with a Donair. Yes, I have a heart-on with Donair Affair. Sorry if this review is too saucy, but these donairs are as saucy as they come. Did you know their chicken is layers of succulent breast slowly spun on the pole of deliciousness?
How on earth do they get their pitas to open without tearing? That is a mystery to me. If you’re like me and always rip your pitas trying to make this at home, then just GIVE UP. Stop trying. You’re not as good as the wonderful people at Donair Affair so let them do it for you.
Everything is fresh. Everything is delicious. I won’t tell your other favourite restaurant that you are going behind their back to have a Donair. This restaurant is our little secret.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Fioretta Lombardi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJDoB6bEhvNTIsnm7a6W0FvuMLvK7eFobxwE84IvKKbIJlxlg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I ordered their baklava 2 days prior to this review and it was amazing and only 2.99. I went back today and they had doubled the baklava in price and it had no filling in it barely any at all, It was mostly filo pastry and therefore very dry. Very disappointing I am  regretful I complimented them on how good it was. Not only was it more expensive but the quality went downhill. At least if your going to double the cost keep the quality as it was.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNmRNeQ_IwvwI8mZMQXkglqd8swc7AfGlIb3by5&fid=0x0:0xfb33fdae02e5bf7a"],"When":"2024-2-17"},{"Name":"Mike Taggart","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXjR_uFVdpKrecFk9vVITA3kDNoDfjGKvrTP_tGpsyeFzFQiJR1qQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This fast food donor joint has amazing tastes. Lamb Donair was delicious especially with the hot sauce and peppers. The gentleman  behind the counter was extremely courteous.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Adam Flores","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWe4BRmj5KQqIAAUG5nAnmdw7_yQFCU9UsNd4ZM98dGlhGwNFOK=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Came here with with friend to trend dinairs for the first time. The lady who worked here was really chill and she hooked us with the best Donairs! 10/10 Place!","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Jass Aulakh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWbmM1j7u9yJwNXmQgnt0buVXOXW87adMfL7iNW6izsr0fEFNTy=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A Slice Above 👆🏻
Andiamo’s Pizza

If you're on the hunt for exceptional pizza, look no further than Andiamo’s. I recently indulged in three of their pizzas, and each one was a testament to their culinary expertise. The pizzas were not only delicious but also had a delightful melt-in-your-mouth quality that speaks to the care and quality of their ingredients.

The atmosphere at Andiamo’s is equally impressive. The restaurant is clean and well-maintained, reflecting a strong commitment to hygiene and customer satisfaction. Whether you're a local or just passing through, I highly recommend visiting Andiamo’s for an unforgettable pizza experience.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOvFGwaJ6uD8jz60x_yAy2R_yPD1VniOFC-I96u&fid=0x0:0xc8d4236b2754cc49"],"When":"2024-7-27"},{"Name":"George Coupland","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWzexTD97DVmEnAG3tKPMwmiKmCIZZIWriICj0VZoeP3VwSFEI=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I had heard that  Andiamos Pizza had been purchased by GM restaurant. I was hoping that the GM quality would have seeped over to the pizza but alas no.
I ordered the Andiamos Special and an Alfredo Chicken Pizza. The Andiamos Special didn’t look anything like the picture on their website. I have added a picture of the one on their website along with the actual pizza I received. It was supposed to have shrimp on it, there wasn’t any shrimp on it and it was terribly salty. The Alfredo was also horribly salty.
The one positive I will add is that the woman who served me was very friendly and pleasant.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP_SYugk5LvqdIoqEhJWlQx-EnqQy7LmZZaFboA&fid=0x0:0xc8d4236b2754cc49"],"When":"2024-7-25"},{"Name":"Sandi Maki","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocItcaOKChuKmNvsvgz0cE7d6pyM9VQI0z2jx3OQNSSC9ZQP-Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"We have been ordering from Andiamos for a long time and it was always good. Last time we ordered the pizza was disgusting and we ended up throwing it out. They use canned mushrooms not fresh, what they do to hide the lack of toppings they hide it under the cheese and the toppings are not cooked. When we called to complain they offered us a free pizza next time we ordered, Called a few months later to be told we waited to long and they would not honor their promise. Made all kinds of excuses. Needless to say we will never order from them again.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ryan Ballinger","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLD5a3B3-Ecgk2kT0trv96SQZurGDkcaK_Ugv4coToqzr4J1g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We ordered three of their specialty pizzas and they were loaded with cheese and toppings. When I picked them up, I was greeted by a very friendly lady, and my pizzas were nice and hot. They were delicious. Highly recommend.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Elaine Payne","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLi-cZ79vVwFEPuZ0jB7xl3YujoVxBK2BTnin4mf8s3bdVAog=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Not a complaint but information I wish I had known so I hadn't ordered. The lasagna was a good size portion with a good layer of cheese and a piece of garlic toast. BUT, though it looked like a classic lasagna, the flavours weren't Italian and it had some spice to it. I didn't enjoy it and only ate a little. We both were very disappointed. I'll have to try to mix it with pasta sauce and Italian seasonings to see if I can save it.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Cootsy Collins","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWXW7yU3MWvosAkJw22U9GvyXMv8HmPeuotrpOwu1E1X3C0dbI=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Got the baked lasagna with meat sauce & was not disappointed. Reminds me of the place I’d get pasta from back home. My only complaint is that I might gain back some of the weight I lost lol. And lucky for me, I just found my new pasta place & it’s near my work. Thank you so much for the amazing dinner & awesome service. I’ll be seeing you guys soon!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Brandon Nagy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU5geYbrbW68XZnK-xVVCQbMsaaLeInjrHXcusvGMOmVsZcXLQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We tried 10 pizza places in maple ridge and all agreed this one was the best so far! Soo much cheese. The large pizzas must weigh like 8-10lbs.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nigel Taylor","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJRcTfPJfWRiLcIzFsLQorBBJTnv5z6Li3pJEBTa1z8BoCjrQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We go here for a great lasagne. Give the super-helpful crew a short heads-up and you can easily make "additions"!  Our favourite is the meaty tomato sauce with our chosen plusses of mushrooms, spinach and a pinch of chilli flakes. Large servings and garlic bread too. You won't be disappointed 👍👍","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Tyler Mcdonald","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLDyXiT_Zvl0Oxe-jS7KuCSrfeNZyYTwLFMfWHpajzgmef2nA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"my chicken sandwich was raw, it was also a pretty thin patty. also compared to other fast food it took a really long time to get my food; this was my first and last time dining here.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM-u0NyJU73r3uALXJdk_YadatuJ-7D10Eiu9en&fid=0x0:0xc2c38f8b525f398c"],"When":"2024-8-10"},{"Name":"Ley Anne gonzales","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVGdf7E96fuZkSJQP1KznUaKO4_hvMb2VQMM0Up7KjejwN9tbKY0g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I thought the management should know... i hope they can read this. First i love the idea of one dollar wings this is the only place my family can buy it from
Sorry but I left the restaurant sad lost my appetite, good i bought fries to eat.
My spicy chicken was raw like pink meat? I compared it to the regular one i ordered i was confused. I don't know if their yellow light or what i don't know I had to look to the outside light and yeap its pink raw Chicken. We love spicy but never seen spicy ones that pink. I got replacement but it is still pink. I was worried my child is eating raw too. I heard the crew call for spicy chicken so i thought they had bunch of spicy chicken order. Hope they check  how they cook maybe they cook too much in one batch to make it looks cooks but still pink in the inside. I got. I got new and yes still hot but its still pink. So sad my favorite chicken is like that 😔 .  i used to work at restaurants but never have I ordered or got raw chicken. Please check the quality. Thanks
Thank you for the lady crew who replaced my Chicken but please check with kitchen. Thank you.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Darin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXLaHGI3oYmAo2BDSwe3R6hi9l2mLBnerv2dA89VquAGyGJqQLWIA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Just ate for the first time at Churches Chicken on 240th and Dewdney Truck Road in Maple Ridge.

Front staff were just ok, no smiles and seemed like they'd rather be somewhere else.
No music, dirty tables that you could tell had been cleared by the customers but never wiped.
Bathroom also dirty with a layer of dust.

Most shockingly the young fella cooking wasn't wearing a hair net, had pretty long bangs and in fact kept brushing his long bangs whilst handling food.

I hope the owner sees this and takes immediate steps before Health Canada gets involved.

No excuse

Chicken was quite Good, super hot and fresh.

Pity no one cares

D. Williamson","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Eric Cheng","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWOyg3d6oaJTu5sdvuUVJNteYVGj_1LBSkeQ_4988ARhRbaxE43Ew=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This place is ticking! But stellar customer service and fantastic food as advertised. I came in with a coupon order that they weren't doing. But the staff alerted me that they would still try to fulfill it, but would be delayed. The food was amazing! Everyone loved it. Super hot, super fresh, super crunchy. Nothing sits on the stand for very long. Staff were super friendly and knowledgeable and great with customers. Kudos to the Friday night crew on the long weekend for a fantastic job. Thanks for making my family night a blast!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMVUA_xx3LScRfS6gc8TGgH5FpEQzqn_ucEBrg3&fid=0x0:0xc2c38f8b525f398c"],"When":"2022-7-30"},{"Name":"Zachary Fowler","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXx5Qx9-CdiURNbNqlXMHoMdayeUaXhcA2dxUwsJ-cqE4vB1VM=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Staff seems to care.  Either your order will be cold, the wrong items, or not even the advertised item. Had a chicken sandwich that was just a bunch of dark meat someone smashed together hoping nobody would notice. Not an improvement of last time when the food was served cold. Save your money and eat elsewhere","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Adam Carich","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU0azVMhRvFNcNxf8zv4UZjhJtDNUZEYm4keHKEhFQPW2uPwkWE=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This place is great I love the classic chicken sandwich. Definitely one of the better places in Maple Ridge for food. The staff are nice the only issue I've had was they sometimes take a long time to answer the phone. I work nearby so it's inconvenient if I have to wait for half my break. But other than that I have never had an issue.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"OblivAeon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWBhAx1DfP-o36Si0salWH0937bvwUUbpkb4-TMxPX_ZBg-3BZ4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"i was a religious visitor of churches as they were my go to local. my favorite item was the mexicana burger but one day they started using patties about 1/4 the size. i pointed this out to the staff thinking it was an oversight but they informed me that this was the new standard from corporate. it was the smallest patty you've ever seen.
on another occasion my wife odered coleslaw and they gave us potato salad. after notifying them of the mistake, the employee denied that we were holding potato salad and then informed us that they do not serve potato salad. after some back and forth, the story changed to they do have potato salad but it was expired so they are sending it back to the warehouse.
needless to say i no longer visit","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"ZJ SZ","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocImelomVOqjph0wobI2yfq3okXOzO5WwuIBvLNLk5J4dBA_vg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Arrived home at around 10pm last night to find someone’s huge order mistakenly delivered to my doorstep, no names or addresses to be found so I kept it. 10/10 free food would eat again. If this was meant for you I hope you got comped a new order.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNV2wsbgcWkEWFc3WVsNG8gRkyoA1Kdtab2PX48&fid=0x0:0xc2c38f8b525f398c"],"When":"2023-8-19"}]

Over the last year or two, the food has become pretty devoid of flavour. The chow mein used to be so good, I could just eat it and be happy. Now, it is still in the fridge since we ordered takeout a few days ago. It will probably go in the compost. I think the breaded almond chicken and sweet and sour chicken balls are pretty good but the sweet and sour sauce used to be thick and it was very thin this last time.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Benjamin Chen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKBA5FB1OgRxlCyVinYuA7HZyCMqwaGLSrehr4Mn4kDvdqi1g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I relished the exquisite sweet and sour pork.
