Dissatisfied and disappointing.  I hadn't been in a couple years and has it ever gone downhill. It used to be good.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"megumi s","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUEDV-T-arppY7Ggy0cXgR13FfJZbF8Ty9M2t3rSR9PNBspi7Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Nice spot with fresh food that comes out quickly. Good option if you’re looking for a straightforward, tasty meal without a long wait.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ron Chan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU4C9fuu3Pgu102q3bAxHKivkiOQqwqKjJditkVdy4zIZ628gCE7g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Ordered takeout.

Ordered shrimp with cashews but it didn't come with any cashews just vegetables.

Got the hot and sour soup, we didn't like the huge chunks of tofu that was cut all unevenly.

Pan fried beef and noodles was great, wasn't too oily.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO-_OKK6LaQdtXmw_28o-YmlaSszQD_0y4q1a5G&fid=0x0:0xa5345ef2d2e4be6f"],"When":"2022-11-6"},{"Name":"Niko Bellic","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXwv_LQBDJWISpeRF602du0NEESI9E9uJ7oSXckjgAEnCHE6mw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Lived in maple ridge for 20 years now, this is my go to Chinese food place. user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Riley Takeo Hooge","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLgIva6PMRpqUulaj2E9b567gf1t64PfCIHKigFv65LY803xA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Smile Thai is one of the best Thai restaurants in the Lower Mainland, let alone the Ridge-Meadows area. I have been coming here since they first opened, and it has been a pleasurable and diverse addition to the community.

Do yourself a favor - instead of grabbing takeout at one of the many non-authentic Chinese restaurants in Maple Ridge, try an actual authentic Thai alternative. The flavours are exotic and complex, and the staff are very friendly!

They no longer do dine-in, but don't let that shy you away. Some of the best foods are takeout only, and this is absolutely no exception!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"marlon mcclain","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLTqWT-EhH3S15LYcpz3NgsdaQaRy5PMHt06Mn-Np63xQQ7lg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Worst Thai food I have ever had. Red Currey had no flavour no fresh bamboo shoots or  fresh thai basil,  super runny water down with coconut rice seemed it was day old and dry  crunchy absolutly no coconut taste, TomYum soup again no flavour, Padthai was best of the bad even my 15 year old son thought it was not spicy and tasteless. Also cant dine in May 2024 because of covid? What? Arent we past that?","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMtwqHpaCdgt9tRJrSuDhH7FIgUAgSZKnsnkgIh&fid=0x0:0xbfb891f71a2789dd"],"When":"2024-5-28"},{"Name":"Jessica Clark-Roesch","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUHUJ1USG6gqe3ILZYlPE5sEULzxPYzVCYQUpc3cXGQ3FO1vdwV=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Hands down best Thai food and customer service in Maple Ridge and surrounding areas. Never disappointed with the quality or price and the customer service, a family ran business goes a long way! The facility is always so clean and welcoming. Highly recommend supporting this business.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Hanna Waite","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX4w9rddcQ9lpExu1dNfEghJjG9ydsVVggFFRamVAbNCDWVaWj7=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Food is good, service is friendly, and the restaurant seems clean.

I would advise caution if eating gluten free- I mentioned twice when ordering that I need my order GF, and confirmed that it was GF when I picked it up, but there was a spring roll in the container with my salad, so I couldn’t eat it. I ate the Pad Thai as it was in a different container, but the spring roll being included made me question if the Pad Thai had actually been made GF.

Wouldn’t hurt to ask when someone orders GF if they want the spring roll, because more than likely the answer would be no 🤷🏻‍♀️","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mrityunjay Kumar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK02yKU4inEgudvhGGlKrBrAKZRxhuwnfeJyD_JeTGVlWa7qQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Worst thai food ever. I didn’t expected like this. They have thai chef even though it’s not good. I don’t say make exactly like authentic thai food but it’s not even near that taste. Red curry was just watery red spicy broth and spiced with only chilli powder they didn’t use thai red chilli. Thai food is all about 4 kind of flavor that is spicy, sour, sweet, and salt. The one I had was not thai food no taste just bland. I don’t know what it was. Next time I will try different that restaurant. 0/5. Plus no dining only take away.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jesse Day","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJdALS6-K1AhdfLOcF6-O11KPUw7FdAEcnuKZueiEPEdvDPh3k=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best Thai I've had outside of Thailand. I'm gonna remember this green curry for a long time. Sad I don't live in Maple Ridge or else I'd be here weekly.

Staff was super friendly. I called for takeout about 8 minutes before close and they still happily took my order. Glad I found this place. Will be back whenever I'm in Maple Ridge.

I don't normally write reviews but this place was too good not to praise.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOybU2c8qbDwc_UJMXwMiMKJYMnUuurzpi9y-wR&fid=0x0:0xbfb891f71a2789dd"],"When":"2023-11-24"},{"Name":"Indianna Moon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW8OPCNbUxooZdcKgFJhZk7FGEHUiGCQmqp2MgQIwJtRY_kgZEthQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I ordered take out from this restaurant today for the first time, and I must say I am pretty disappointed in what I received. The "salad" in the box is merely some brown iceberg lettuce with no dressing and one sliver of a shredded carrot. In the photo attached  the reddish colour of the lettuce is not the curry, it  is in fact the rotting of the lettuce itself. The curry I ordered is way too sweet, has mooshy and spongy tofu in it, and maybe 4 small chunks of bell pepper. I spent an extra dollar for coconut rice and my Curry is sweeter and tastes more like coconut than the rice... I don't know what the heck is going on, but I've had Thai red curry about 30 times and it has never been this bad. Im writing this review in hopes that the owner sees this and looks into the quality of their take out orders, as I will not return to this place or recommend it to anyone.
It is not a fun experience ordering food on my break to take it back to work and have to throw out half of my meal.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOWzhNNyEplyqnHzH_bmgM3SsnspIujIUlCrxiY&fid=0x0:0xbfb891f71a2789dd"],"When":"2017-8-8"},{"Name":"Duke Pufus","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWukW7L6iD7Fsj98lKPEw1hzjJ0B-rpWvm75WLGKOM6jjGxeeRp=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Okay here it is, we ordered take out for 4, staff were awesome, food tastes good, portion size is small for the price.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMC3RCWVzmvKkYroY0GruV8SIkPe_AMSoXKuEah&fid=0x0:0xbfb891f71a2789dd"],"When":"2022-8-25"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Xavier Snow","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUPCQwCJb2ZmOWDXqksCsd-vZs9ykcxfKjETkI90DQafTXUU5xa=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My wife and I stopped in to The Nut Coffee Shop today for a salted caramel latte and a caramel macchiato. The service was excellent and the store was very clean and modern inside. About 100 meters away from the bus loop located in downtown Maple Ridge this will for sure be a spot I visit more often!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMxCvx0-MoYtdhZ-Saalr2OtpuBQafAEKAWSHJ1&fid=0x0:0xd5efd2907473ae44"],"When":"2024-12-1"},{"Name":"Sarah El Daouk","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLUxg5vWixImGb2nplfdl2YjWzrkNtc_tICsVZNrFG30XyDuWsF=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"My favorite café! I visit almost weekly. I love supporting our local businesses. They have fantastic coffee (especially the nut latte) and the cozy atmosphere. The only reason for my 4-star rating is the seating – while the chairs are okay, they're often full, and the benches could really use some cushions, as they are extremely uncomfortable. I also wish they would bring back more savory options, like the cheddar scones they used to carry, as all of their current offerings are on the sweeter side. Hopefully, they’ll consider these suggestions!
❤️","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Viona Halim","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV5PMLEtvgkAwv2IjmL8XXm0-Ly_XpBo5Kd0Hv2pxoQ26_Hfy4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Nice and quaint little coffee shop in the heart of downtown Maple Ridge. Nice that we finally get some local shops here that look very cozy and welcoming.
My husband and I came here to get some lattes to go, but the space looks quite nice and cozy if you wanna stick around for a bit with your laptop.

We ordered our lattes with regular milk, but I heard what's exceptional here are the plant-based milk lattes. Nonetheless, our lattes were made to perfection. They certainly froth the milk just to the right temperature for the silkiest and sweetest consistency. Wait times are also very reasonable.

What we find this place is lacking is more options for baked goods. They have the usual suspect like scones and cookies. Then they have some bowls, wraps, yogurt, etc. In their cold display. But overall, the bite options are somewhat limited. I think they're definitely coffee-focused and there's nothing wrong with that.

They also carry other local, small-biz merch in their store. All and all, we'll definitely come back to try their other coffee options.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMYQ_F3Ob_Ypf3328lHSh6Kvjso-KRJawfGB7fZ&fid=0x0:0xd5efd2907473ae44"],"When":"2022-10-1"},{"Name":"Ewa Kreczman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK-qfsXu0WfHNDeytPhJ-h9WzO_CO49eT61A3uvpEL1bK9JnA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"My friend and I were looking for place to sit, have coffee and chat. Then she remember somebody mentioned to her this place. We decided to give it a try and this turned to be a mistake. We ordered coffees and bought some treats. We sat down waiting for a coffee. When coffees were ready only then we were informed that they are closing in 15 minutes as they have shorter opening hours today, something she never mentioned when we were putting order in. If we knew that we would just found different place. When we said that this should be mentioned when we were putting order, girl's working there attitude was far from proper customer service. Her suggestion was that we could go to courtyard to have our coffee. "Great suggestion"  while it was raining and quite cold.  We are not going back there ever again with this kind of customer service. On the other note cookies we ordered weren't quality which would make us want to go back there as well.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Prima Primavera","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVgviOjcAerRoNVlGDMxdWH5dK-NAzgYaRM-V8_yzCd5gUIyVaI=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Clean and spacious coffee shop, baristas often smiling, and always very polite. Good coffee, urban atmosphere with easy accessibility.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMH-EV-is8uUR-gvtVmzze_8WZID7nlL5hKYUoO&fid=0x0:0xd5efd2907473ae44"],"When":"2024-10-1"},{"Name":"S P","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL3H1hwIfN6Bp7TC6p9xHt7oE4AtZuMSz6HUmbD4gLsn19Lvw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"What was ordered:⁣⁣

• Oat latte
• To live for everyday cookie ⁣⁣
• Bonus Bakery red velvet cookie ⁣⁣
⁣⁣
Cute little coffee shop in Maple Ridge. Loved the variety of vegan options made by local businesses. Kinda went nuts with the cookies LOL. ⁣","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMJscSOneiiaMiQs8l_B6C-LVE2jHvj57iUsCkY&fid=0x0:0xd5efd2907473ae44"],"When":"2023-11-19"},{"Name":"Mahshid Rezaee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU9GxeUaX5WBNrmfk93lsqQgSl4Mb_xDNMvNqwfGesMvRfVpU-o=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"NOT RECOMMENDED AT ALL!

I’m really sorry to say that my visit to The Nut in Maple Ridge was far from pleasant. Unfortunately, it was THE WORST customer service I have experienced in Canada!

The staff member who took my order was notably unhelpful and rude. I had some questions about their treats, as I was considering ordering for myself and two guests. However, when I noticed that the items didn’t seem fresh, I decided to just order coffee. This seemed to upset the staff member, who responded by handing me the card payment machine in a very abrupt and rude manner.

To make matters worse, my previous experience with their meals was also disappointing. The quality just wasn’t up to standard. Given these issues, I can’t recommend The Nut based on my experiences. There are way better options in the area! super dissapointed!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jamak Golshani","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWUj2LK0XJaxGCkMdV1Y3vwaPy3axo29-O-pu7Kb7eqy9PgvRrN=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Awesome, cozy, family owned, and delightful spot. If you enjoy little local coffee shops over the chains this is one of these rare spots in Maple Ridge.

The owners are friendly and welcoming. Probably the only spot you can get JJ Beans 🙂

Locally crafted products are displayed and sold.
The coffee was delicious and the environment was just right!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOaOR7D4qMTK9fs_atEdI0cUKh1q8tHuSnGxQfo&fid=0x0:0xd5efd2907473ae44"],"When":"2022-4-23"}]

[{"Name":"Jennifer Mitton","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJM_YjoYpYPoIcKZ6_ffcMam4Ms77vkPWmucFh_D0MWF9mBQVI=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"What a great Mexican restaurant in the heart of Maple Ridge. The decor ambience and service were impeccable.
We went for lunch and were able to order from both the regular and breakfast menus.
The burritos are massive and delicious-they’d feed two easily.  That’s about $10 pp.
the queso fundio was also delicious.
I must of all loved the cod taco and all their salsas.
The cream filled churros were amazing.
We would definitely go back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOEeRl1WT5_oZ6kGh7nIklPQNumXdf4FN-XrHk_&fid=0x0:0x7a7137450555de4c"],"When":"2024-11-10"},{"Name":"Jeff Gingera","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVCiu-_EfINdBQYrLJJwQUa1eIZY2kaULP-QhWpjOxgSdQ9bLqLSw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Now one of my favorite lower mainland restaurants, Taco Fan features real Mexican style tacos.  The dine in has  a relaxed vibe.  Our Server, Maria, was warm & welcoming.  Tacos were Amazing.  Prices were mid scale so not a cheap place but still within budget. It's of free parking nearby.  Wheelchair accessible.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNIa8R1DPqlsyCm-ERBq7a0QlhRPYDr-Jw-axDF&fid=0x0:0x7a7137450555de4c"],"When":"2024-6-19"},{"Name":"Jerry Hernandez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWEKGC56Tc2lvn_hRjLXaCqV_ioShP4dyLQiP8SFMNMx9uDY8xd=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best Mexican food we have had in a minute. It's in truth a 4 star for food. But they have spicy options which add a star.  Service is excellent and friendly.  The place is extra clean.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOziwIgNhlNhrscZZbTu9I3EKo21XBNLoxeU8eI&fid=0x0:0x7a7137450555de4c"],"When":"2024-8-22"},{"Name":"Rishi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWg4QBb_dVBzhxJg5dwslBxdqBD4Sl1A3KUCEuzcw0nka54ehe6=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Extremely delicious food, got the birria tacos and the filled churros. Our server was exceptional, very welcoming and very kind. Would highly recommend to anyone in OR out the area","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOjUhVL8-wFNCXfiysHAAFzoT47Q7X5ClLjGPNN&fid=0x0:0x7a7137450555de4c"],"When":"2024-8-4"},{"Name":"Victoria Dengler","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXtlodz71lhsrz54ARL9WDlSgf7K6XUugwUjfk9RlusM9gjP_w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Beautiful lil Mexican restaurant! So neat, tidy, and homey feeling. Staff were friendly, welcoming, and had great service.

The food was AMAZING. It was the perfect amount to make me feel full and tasted so good. I enjoyed every bit of it.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP6wkJaznldvraTySmdIjzmMPbgHlu0Xd4OxncH&fid=0x0:0x7a7137450555de4c"],"When":"2024-7-21"},{"Name":"Vanessa Forouzan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW1_cocFm7SjkDDohlmX_tdPTKxFzhHUmYQsRX-gBS4JxUCl0nwTA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I highly recommend this restaurant if you're in the Maple Ridge area. The service was exceptional, with friendly and attentive staff who made me feel welcomed from the moment I walked in.

The food at this place was absolutely delicious. I decided to try two different dishes, one with chicken and another with pulled pork. Both dishes were cooked to perfection, with the meat being well-seasoned and not overcooked. The chicken was juicy and tender, while the pulled pork was incredibly flavorful and melt-in-your-mouth tender.

The overall quality of the food was outstanding, and I was impressed by the attention to detail in every dish. The flavors were well-balanced, and the portion sizes were generous.

The ambiance of the restaurant was also very pleasant, with a cozy and inviting atmosphere. The staff's knowledge and passion for the food they served added to the overall dining experience.

In conclusion, I had a fantastic experience at this restaurant. The service, food, and ambiance were all top-notch. I will definitely be returning and recommending this place to friends and family.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPgqvni58QwCY2a9R-zTxmUEDyxHP3v1vuuN08K&fid=0x0:0x7a7137450555de4c"],"When":"2024-1-1"},{"Name":"Mike Barnes","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL14AG5EcRj7fYcbE3xgYZDczsiBpGFEadXnk3mSfrCpag2mw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Absolutely fantastic true authentic Mexican with great service and relaxed atmosphere
I especially loved the kambucha and hatacha cinnamon drink pairing these two drinks with the incheladas was perfect
The only thing I will say is just little more salt that being said will definitely be coming back for that fantastic experience 🤩😘🤗😝","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOkzCMlp4eO10P-_lcbV8liUHI8wvOlsFgEw_Ce&fid=0x0:0x7a7137450555de4c"],"When":"2024-7-13"},{"Name":"Wendy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW6_SZiQStioXmbvv0S9IZORHUi5VoQzv6sQG-peGyskdFz7PuZuA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The ultimate Mexican culinary experience outside of Mexico 🇲🇽❤️ Top-notch food and exceptional service at unbeatable prices 😋 Cute and very clean restaurant 👌 Absolutely a hidden gem 💎 My husband and I loved it! Definitely one of our new favorite places 😍 We shared a tortilla soup, chicken enchiladas, and a fabulous carne con chile, a baked dish with beans, chile, chorizo and cheese served with tortillas. Soooo delicious 👏","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOMuPnwbd_uxolxYVgIiPfMzbG2I-BS_stc5Jfk&fid=0x0:0x7a7137450555de4c"],"When":"2024-3-18"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Jeremy Brooks","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU9h-pOVPEAO5xTo8LGpQ0sa5A7PNB_Rp1SEXGX_qf0-nayw0WaDQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"It was my son's 10th birthday today - I called and made reservations for 530 for my family of 5

Food takes a long time to arrive - we complained about how slow it was and the waitress said "this is a 2 hour seating" and that's "how the kitchen works". I could understand if it was fine dining but let's be clear, this is store bought pasta with home made sauces.

My three boys liked the marinara sauce and the pasta was cooked nicely.

My wife had the "special" which was roasted chicken (two drum sticks and one thigh) for $29. No mention on the menu that it was only dark meat. She said it was ok and ate most of it but was also very hungry as we had been waiting nearly 1.5hrs for the food to come out.

The manager?owner?/chef? Went around to every table except ours to check in with customers. We heard him mention it was someone else's birthday and congratulated them - he made no mention to my son about it being his birthday even though it was specified in the reservation (whatever).

The worst part of the night was when I asked the manager?owner?/chef? About my carbonara sauce. The sauce was cooked improperly - carbonara is supposed to be silky smooth without any curdling of the eggs. My pasta basically had cream, oil and scrambled eggs on it. Apparently this is "how we do it there".  When I explained that this is not what I was expecting and that it wasn't properly made he became very standoffish and rude. I had to ask to have it removed from the bill - which he did but not without his nasty entitled attitude.

The atmosphere is nice, it was clean and cozy. There's not a lot of seating and I guess the only downsides are the very small washrooms (1 person per washroom) and the tables on the right side of the dining room are so close together that my 8 year old could barely fit between the chairs to get to the washroom.

We thought this would be a nice treat for my son's dinner as we are an Italian family but this was just a letdown on all accounts. Even with my main removed the bill was over $130 (for a glass of house wine, one app- the prawns were tasty, three plates of store bought pasta and my wife's "special").

Won't be back.

***Edit: we ordered two sides of garlic bread and they never brought it.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPLi9b1a6K79_tuyWX1dKP-SCvx_AKUQTTU8jjk&fid=0x0:0xe2da073352bb98a3"],"When":"2024-10-25"},{"Name":"Monkey Couch","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKjBJae2rKS_uXWCMGu9-Vey95DYSzaWVHAACfGX9Lt21SDIw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Went here the first time with my husband and my friend for her birthday. Food was great. Everyone loved their food. If I am going to go out and eat pasta I want it to either be cheap or amazing. This was amazing. My dish came with the most tender fall off the bone chicken I have ever had. My husband kept trying to steal more of my dish. Service was quick and friendly. For the quality and service the price is right. Highly recommended.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Carol Pow","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLNTxZqPK4X8aOtVF2rc4ragFral1AR_tqdwpR5cJKJNofBJg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"We arrived at 5 when the restaurant opened.  We know from past visits they are busy.  We didn’t have a reservation.  They had to check to see if they could take us.  They said they could but we’d have to be done by 7.  Because someone else had reserved for then.  Just not a warm welcoming  feeling.  It was my mom’s birthday I said to the waitress/hostess.  She went oh Happy Birthday.  No special treatment at all.

The Cesar salad and house were good.  The food was subpar at best. Ordered the roasted chicken with Penne pasta.  Store bought pasta under cooked with no real sauce or flavour.  The chicken which I thought was in the pasta was roasted chicken on the side all brown meat thighs and drumstick.  No mention of this and I only like white meat.

Other people in our party ordered the combo.  Again no flavour for the sauce and chicken was dark and not very flavourful.

Overall total disappointment for a dinner out none less a birthday.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"danielle loranger","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJnptNzs1wQbaw2FFsd1jy4E7t0vjMoJDS7syMM-SOyTKG9og=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is our favourite restaurant in ridge! It’s so cozy, the staff are so attentive, friendly and helpful and the food is delish. We love the Caesar salad and have never been dissapointed with a dish. Check for reservations on the weekends as it’s not a huge place. We love the house red wine and always leave full with some leftovers as well! Visiting for a birthday dinner tomorrow and already drooling thinking about it!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Reece Kopeschny","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjULKOa8APzPB-oiZ47ByVkOUw3cvI4vI6xSWNOo647veRKgca1I=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have heard great reviews about Il Corsaro for a while now and the reviews are correct. Started the meal with the prawn appetizer and the sauce on it was unbelievable, the main course was the house made lobster and crab ravioli which hit the spot and came with a salad and house dressing which was some of the best I have ever had. Ended the evening with house made Tiramisu which was just as perfect and even better than the rest of the meal.

If I could have given them 6 stars I would have, the server was able to answer all of the questions right away and was a perfect date night. I can’t wait to go back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNbcbjP5yJs5gkNEr4RnGtaFvirnwc__6NQ6nyd&fid=0x0:0xe2da073352bb98a3"],"When":"2023-3-28"},{"Name":"Brad Ricketts","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIjqJT0OuLQXt06Dc_FpXglVwWIq_Tlr0-bsBV-LmQdJK6w9Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My wife and I happened on this restaurant while looking for a late dinner.  We arrived at around 830PM and the restaurant was not very busy, a group of 6, and two other couples.  We got seated right away, and the hostess returned shortly with glasses of  water
and some amazing warm buns with butter.  The server came to our table shortly afterward and took our beverage orders, and discussed the evening specials. She left us with the menus and returned a short time later with our drinks.  She took our appetizer order and our main dinner orders, and my wife and I enjoyed the warm buns. Relatively quickly, our Caesar salad arrived, and we began our meal.  The timing on our main courses was perfect, and we had a short break between the completion of our salad and our main courses. I decided on the Penne Amatricana, and my wife had linguini Bolognese and meatballs.  The meatballs were about the size of a tennis ball and they were delicious.  My penne dish was also delicious, and I ate the leftovers the following day for lunch.  I would highly recommend this restaurant to anyone who wants a great Italian meal. The service, course timing, and servers were excellent.  Our server was very friendly and explained the story of the restaurant, and I am not surprised it has been in business as long it has, serving great food in a great spot by great people.  5 stars from me.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Devan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX46jwTvLLxQHMqh-_Tq6ADgdla67lzdwdqPBC-oI4JI8tfgn0q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Make sure to get a reservation as its booked up plenty (for a good reason), I was lucky enough to get in as someone had cancelled. The pasta was absolutely amazing probably the best ive had and the atmosphere of the place was lovely too, will be back again for that 10/10 pasta","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nicole Laughlin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXq_l7wggmzJItBUT8JuYycSZA4ZE8w7Kup0NGmSBUCAXhkpsDr=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Ordered 60 dollars worth of takeout and basically had to throw it all out. The cesar salad was brown, and had literally 2 croutons on it, NOTHING else almost no sauce either, worst I’ve ever had. They forgot our soup and the pasta was extremely disappointing and flavourless.  I never call to complain about anything but I just had to. When I called I was told ‘pasta is pasta’ whatever the hell that means. I make better pasta at home in ten minutes. I was really excited for this meal but will never go back, shocked at all the good reviews… listen to the bad ones!!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMF0FNcyUma6ORPuN5g4Fgg9e1hCXAxp09CXh06&fid=0x0:0xe2da073352bb98a3"],"When":"2021-10-31"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Nicole Netik","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK3A-4p8_N-oUSsIfBHH-j4qnuWMdZ7W5Wic2AIeJhdFOboRw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My daughter and I went to Me n' Ed's last night on an impulse. We are always really careful about the restaurants we visit because she has celiac and unfortunately gets sick with the smallest amount of cross contamination.  It was super busy in there with a steady flow of customers but that didn't affect their customer service! Staff was kind and took their time to listen and was upfront with telling us about wait times (completely understandable with how many people were in there!)
The pizza was ready quicker then we anticipated, it was hot, delicious and loaded with toppings!! And the best part, safe from cross contamination for my daughter!
Thanks for a great experience, we will definitely be back 🍕","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOsjH-yuMueg5pU-k-PAHZgxSK9gmYy8iAM_QOl&fid=0x0:0xdbe181141989b9fa"],"When":"2024-11-9"},{"Name":"Afsana Tabibi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVzp6b-InW6PAK15vNh9v8ga8zbWmNjzR0Dlq305Lj5B3Ej-HpL=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Thought we would try Me-n-Ed's for the first time tonight, and it was a major let-down. We ordered a large half pepperoni half cheese with garlic jalapeno aioli, sriracha ranch, and garlic parm cheesy bread sticks. The pizza crust was some weird philo-pastry/pita bread/uncooked dough mix. I don't get it. The bottom of the crust had separated from the rest of the pizza so, the bottom was well-done and the part that had separated was undercooked. The cheese was so thick and hardened by the time we got it home. I ate two slices because I was hungry (generally food tastes better when you're hungry but not this time) but I threw the rest out. I hate throwing out food and leaving bad reviews because I appreciate local businesses, but this pizza was poorly made. I wouldn't go back and I wouldn't recommend it to anyone who enjoys a slice of great tasting pizza.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOEidUFp4IIa5NpzQHTtjxbEkPHfpsPg4s35XnZ&fid=0x0:0xdbe181141989b9fa"],"When":"2024-11-12"},{"Name":"Crystal V","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJy_8JzOAdXYM50ytFR2HidA0G9Xsyge4e68t8ePZBmeAOiPA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The best pizza in Ridge. Always loaded with toppings, always delicious. My whole family and extended family enjoys Me n’ Ed’s, it’s always the go to when they’re in town.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOAJyRLFQX3sla7T4BsmByln9cnJ9rMFCuEQk7u&fid=0x0:0xdbe181141989b9fa"],"When":"2024-10-12"},{"Name":"H S Madan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUTu4oMkDk1Z3MjNV_7rONLy371tsTTJL-xX0jcQ-rhkA8blIkVlg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"We had to give this place a try. The pizza was good but was it worth $70 for 2 pizzas. It was not that good. I feel if you are going to charge that high of a premium for a pizza it's gotta deliver to that value. And unfortunately it did not. There was nothing special worth going back for, and that's really not to say that the pizza was not good. But I feel it was just over priced for what you get. The sauce could have had a little more flavor or zest. And the crust was the same. I would not consider this place to be a premium pizza quality.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Matt Maguire","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJUjvEOVle_CBxHwXITIP_j1rPXSVCppH7zmN159uXpTYLu6g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We ordered the Monday night special pepperoni pizza and the Godfather pizza because the delivery took a bit longer than expected they gave us our meal for free! No complaints from our end, they just realized and took care of it for us. What exceptional customer service! We will definitely be ordering from here again! Not to mention this pizza is fantastic! Thank you!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Rafael Aguirre","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXE6LgR-ngDwq-zcl5ddKp8YqAVzKXAfrvyM0U1OJg8S8G4mI9J=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I am Pizza lover, I tried good pizzas from Italy, France, Chile and Argentina but I tried only once a good pizza in Canada and today I tested the second best from Me n Eds. I was so surprised from the pizza base, it was delicious!. The only point to improve in my opinion is to stop using product from cans, like mushrooms and peppers.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Joanne Antoniak","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWTQwhPcO13h_HhVjJVUrwpHjU5MeesKhPrxV5pA1ymdZ1edFkY=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Me & Ed's Maple Ridge 🍕🎉
First time at this location.
Same great Me & Ed's food.
If you like thin crust (crispy thin) you will love their pizza; if you are a think bready crust lover -- you probably will not.
The toppings are super fresh - and every pizza is loaded with toppings (right to the edge).","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNilhuXZWkxXwmFkInpH9ZeOcFzyPGwvjI1eHyF&fid=0x0:0xdbe181141989b9fa"],"When":"2023-8-5"},{"Name":"Ellen Smith","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWgbvr2VXIxmQAp2oX9KxXclaEeljzeGNAPzr2u-tCnpyZ0sXzZ9A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great place for a casual lunch. prompt & attentive service, clean and updated atmosphere. Food was very fresh, tasty and very budget friendly!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPJ3o5FgRVt7hYQyf59brPus5yBTc4VJwjDf9Kn&fid=0x0:0xdbe181141989b9fa"],"When":"2024-12-9"}]

She didn’t hesitate to individually mark an Initial on each package and the restaurant manager Jot was so kind and friendly as well! [{"Name":"Blampin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUe_Zl-7bsR_k4aPN0CDrFm3JxQQaY2wgkXgNPVdZQs9NDoFTA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very friendly service and relaxing atmosphere.

The food was really good and came quite quickly.

I had the seafood hot n sour pho , some hot tea and the kids had spring rolls.  Mom had Grilled Lemkngrass Pork and Chicken.

Everything was cooked well only disappointment is the use of FARM raised Prawns. Ocean fished is the only way. These simply are not prawns. They don't taste like anything and they're very bad for you.

I was pleased with an option for tip and no obligation by pre set percentages as some places often have.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNbmGsIeZZnWUSS68rtd3UMGmqvRdpK3Usa8FQS&fid=0x0:0xd56e87c96f1ffa56"],"When":"2024-12-23"},{"Name":"Jack Pajak","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV7kRSq5QM1wGXm36_dbE9YR6CpcUs9VUAhu1SxvpJkrQ-nGO0N=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Another great Maple Ridge Vietnamese restaurant, Hot Pho has a fantastic menu with great prices and friendly staff. We really enjoyed the spring and salad rolls, their pho was great too. I had a large bowl of pho but noticed that there wasn't as much meat and noodles as I would normally expect, but I still left full so...overall I would try Hot Pho again. The location is really convenient and parling is great, worth a stop!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOEotbdkSC2bNOyThaoaNjW7laFBde3unfFMUwS&fid=0x0:0xd56e87c96f1ffa56"],"When":"2024-9-29"},{"Name":"Rolando_ Rose","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIQBfjayv2V3eqQ6nmwU1uOEqgsWCG5VdwRxO3uXCF1EsXQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Located at the court house square, this restaurant is an easy walking distance to downtown core of Maple Ridge. There’s also an ample parking just within the vicinity. I ordered pho with beef brisket and it didn’t disappoint. The broth is delicious, not overly salty. At the table you will find a set of condiments that includes chilli oil, hoisin sauce and soy sauce. Served with a few slices of jalapeño, Thai basil, lime and bean sprouts. While I enjoyed my dining experience, the restaurant needs to declutter some empty boxes that are visible while customers are dining.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPF7pRJozgIOlk8zwh8W7fCkbxhCMfvlpV2r-s&fid=0x0:0xd56e87c96f1ffa56"],"When":"2024-10-23"},{"Name":"Daniel Jung","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXFE7g6vnjf23CW6mDeh4anchF8fxBs6O5Nsx0bvhepuO3MVzWa=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"It was okay. Flavors were decent but not as good as other places I have tried.. They didn't have sriracha. Spring rolls were tasty. May be back again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPLl_Gj107UAie902demJ4y35_HlqUojavRSrZ1&fid=0x0:0xd56e87c96f1ffa56"],"When":"2023-9-20"},{"Name":"Amy Rempel","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW4WQ_mGYG_pYFntbKu-x9F6ks5omdb55yt_SM5kIbSmUYap9w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"The food is delicious. But, you barely get anything for what you pay for. Attached is a picture of a dish I paid $17 for. There was barely any chicken.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOxWcswLeeoxmu9QXvW2gxiqWh4UjZVpFVfnoyV&fid=0x0:0xd56e87c96f1ffa56"],"When":"2024-10-28"},{"Name":"Diba Syed","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUjqdNBmu9lw_riSjJrn9EutvY83fGG0w7vJQpFN6QCCqzTaPc=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is top class restaurant in terms of food, atmosphere and service. The food is rocking for us. Hai the sole working waiter was pretty amicable and prompt.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOFTuqVDRJF8wkAKcHKN5ScLc-jPh2l0Z4NAHNI&fid=0x0:0xd56e87c96f1ffa56"],"When":"2024-5-16"},{"Name":"Stacy Archer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIj81BAT_6zpnhNQrv8O1NkGTpHWT1YRP8ZyOv9AiYf4mPW2apt=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"We have been ordering from this restaurant over the past few years, Dine in and takeout, and have really enjoyed it. Food tastes great and friendly staff. However, over the past year every time we have ordered take out, the pho noodles have been broken scraps. This is the 3rd time in a row that we have ordered pho soup for take out and the noodles are all broken and small, you cannot even pick up with chop sticks. See my picture for details. Very disappointed to see this is how they are treating take out  customers, when clearly it is intentional. For the time being we will be going elsewhere with hopes that with this review, they will stop doing that to customers. Be warned, if you order pho for take out, you won’t get noodles, just broken scraps.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO7g0A22dgW0_BQnGncYvSAWYeH3ZphvoX7-Arb&fid=0x0:0xd56e87c96f1ffa56"],"When":"2024-2-29"},{"Name":"Jonathan Hung","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXcyx4J66dX-2K0eJPsLn9dFQ4eU3qrPUFN-1LCa-9QqLBvskz2=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Opened November 2016 where Sarges Restaurant use to be. The breaded squid was very tender, not oily, and not overcooked... Very tasty! The spring roll was just the same. The Beef Pho Soup had really good flavor there was no grease floating on the top, and the beef was super tender. The rice plates both were very delicious, and the meat was again super tender and very tasty.
UPDATE (Feb 2017): By far the best Pho joint in Maple Ridge. Tried the Egg Noodles with Wonton and Veggies, and it was delicious! Also had the breaded fried squid again, and again tasty!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNn7_U8Q9a8l6SlqdNTpFgh0xfjXZ9sbCyoFU8Y&fid=0x0:0xd56e87c96f1ffa56"],"When":"2016-12-1"}]

[{"Name":"ty Lyn","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVRTHSmVN8R72q5Mxg79-j-gxHLJ7fJNNyroCHg6w-bvnCtF-c=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"As soon as we walked in a group of 5 employees stood at the front talking and staring at us without saying a word to us for 5 minutes. Should of left then i would of save $90.
Waitress extremely rude to my daughter. Also never once asked how the food was or if she could get us anything. We didn’t eat like 70% of our food. Had to ask for take out containers 3 times to pack it up. She was visibly not happy. Definitely didnt tip her she was terrible. She physically checked the receipt infront of us and audibly huffed and stomped off.
Chips were dripping in grease and queso was awful
I asked for things to be added to my wrap never got it.
If staff is going to be that awful. Then the food should be better.
I was born in ridge and have been coming to this restaurant for 30 years. I wont be wasting my money here again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO5i-NA0CvGQARZ_sxRGWoyIt2a5bdPyXX3Yq9D&fid=0x0:0xfb7e4361565a0eee"],"When":"2024-11-5"},{"Name":"Les Girard","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLF1Jw9Nt7u03nI9o0npxuji4tcLHuyXTrSjUoz8igbFBTaeg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"First time ever going to a Red Robin restaurant and we were absolutely amazed with the exceptional service, along with the delicious food. Definitely will be making this place a must stop for every road trip to the mainland!!!!

Thanks to the amazing staff as well!!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMGDqZ7KBFSsSlwNGPGNwlkQSbzGpVe8gbICGa5&fid=0x0:0xfb7e4361565a0eee"],"When":"2024-12-18"},{"Name":"sylvia lever","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKdGDLpAOLpyMt8Fw6SYaISTyJfst7V9WIrBp0VCqFEBK5x=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We recently had a wonderful dinner as a family of six at the Red Robin in British Columbia. From the moment we walked in, our server Julie made us feel welcome with her friendly smile. She was genuinely excited to help us navigate the menu and shared her personal favorites, which made it easy to decide. The food came out quickly, and she made sure our drinks were always topped up. Her timing was perfect—she checked in just enough to make sure we had everything we needed without interrupting our meal. What really made the evening special was her sense of humor. She joked about the cookies being broccoli to avoid our kids picking up on it. It lightened the mood and made our dining experience feel more like a fun night out than just a meal. we couldn’t help but appreciate how her attentiveness added to our enjoyment. We left feeling satisfied and happy, already discussing our next visit. If you’re looking for a family-friendly spot in MR, Red Robin is definitely worth it, especially with a server who knows how to make your night special as Julie did. We’ll be back soon!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Alexander Gaudet","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUsPbOTZua3qeIUnA5P6gmOuUKLsS2Q41okf6i3GpDVs6P20jdc=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Got there right as the dinner rush was starting to celebrate my daughter’s 8th birthday & the four of us were seated right away. Our waitress checked on us frequently despite it being super busy and we had great service. Only complaint I have is the extreme noise in the restaurant (definitely one of the loudest I’ve been to in a while).","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jaime Parsons","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU-7jYUFhaI9gC2bxTYMasGdv8PoNEupjGysYQz0djr9MVfHNL2vQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Renee was our server and the service was absolutely fantastic. She was friendly and attentive and anticipated all our needs. Great experience. The service is always good at this Res Robin but this was probably the best service I've had anywhere.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Christina Evdokimff","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJWSfXISbsm8KkoBRSiYXA8NUoWulpdtMSb0-lzOKvBkwEHSA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Ordered from SKIP.  Entree size Mac and cheese came as side portion (literally half a cup, I measured).  Garlic bread was totally burnt and not edible.  Missed sending an extra sauce.  We have gone to Red Robin for years but this last year really noticed poor service and food quality!  Do better","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Annie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJAG4UtHNdn-C74S5I053c9lMdRMdh_AH35u090AgjHoFmF2GSW=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"You can’t go wrong at Red Robin! There’s something for everyone on the menu and bottomless fries and fountain drinks, yes please!

We came to dinner (on a school night!) and had the most amazing server - JULIE you are are a gift and so wonderful to us from start to finish! She took the time to chat and share the features, dessert options and genuinely loves what she does!  Give this woman a raise! Thank you for a great night and ask for Julie!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM8eDuZl2nB8ycK7g0AutmifnYHCtUSNYLkPR2x&fid=0x0:0xfb7e4361565a0eee"],"When":"2024-2-16"},{"Name":"Daniel Jung","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXFE7g6vnjf23CW6mDeh4anchF8fxBs6O5Nsx0bvhepuO3MVzWa=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Update: Highly recommended the Montreal Brisket Burger.. Only here for a limited time. It's one of the best burgers I've tasted. Service was a lot faster this time!

Old post: Burger tasted good, but service was slow. Our server was really nice and did her best. It was surprisingly a very busy Wednesday night. They closed off a section we wanted to sit in. It's definitely a family vibe here","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOL_fvWGhZNP6iqfAYQFujER7dei5qS8irW3xMJ&fid=0x0:0xfb7e4361565a0eee"],"When":"2023-9-27"}]

[{"Name":"Aleksander Amer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUGOAz6hZJ2NwhTQXXReoo8ipuBBnVUyRU2feoLZjGgiTMM8r_W=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Finally made it in to try the birria tacos with consommé and get some groceries that are hard to find. I thought the tacos were phenomenal and great horchata. I stocked up my freezer with burritos, taquitos and tamales as they are a great price. The staff working there were very friendly and am looking forward to returning. Highly recommend!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMwe1Fr_OLt2VEO6BS0f3KOD3vNBWJGw3abWuCO&fid=0x0:0x93b04e724289e006"],"When":"2024-9-24"},{"Name":"Genn Richards","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIv-Bp7UhIKlk7R_WNzPvF8-SHy2B8dPh4abiUjm-9Owih0FQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The food was fabulous, as always.  Owners, cooks are very friendly and helpful.  We chose to eat in, with most people doing take out.  Minimalist authentic decor.  Lots of mexican snacks, drinks, sauces, etc and freshly made  products in fridges available to take home.  Took care of my cravings for authentic Mexican dinner.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP1SP6dpU36GJk7ppv0R2MiskX9XXUE6geJFc6n&fid=0x0:0x93b04e724289e006"],"When":"2024-8-30"},{"Name":"K Hoyano","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXE8E8JBlvzbXyn0xcaOPW-rY1kqCJ3dded_UE8jcEmnvzWlr8=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We needed lunch for an 18 person event and another local taco place was not returning calls.  Reached out to Lupitas the afternoon before the event and they came through despite having other large orders at the same time.  The lunch was a hit with all attendees.  Great food, great service, good price.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Reece Kopeschny","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjULKOa8APzPB-oiZ47ByVkOUw3cvI4vI6xSWNOo647veRKgca1I=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"First time going to Lupitas and wow I’m impressed,   Lots of grocery items from Mexico including different dried chili peppers, chips, hot sauces and the restaurant. I didn’t know what to choose so I picked one of each of the different street tacos and wow. All of them had so much flavour and fresh. I’m disappointed I didn’t find out about this place until now but I’m so happy I did. I will be back for sure!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPPdStzv93Z_XzXq5emaUmrZOCA6j0xw-P05Wc4&fid=0x0:0x93b04e724289e006"],"When":"2024-6-2"},{"Name":"Dawn Mist","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVyR-na2sQcGqnSW-JxTn27RMX1oocQ3hojpV86Eb8qwbPHRL0=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Birria & Pollo tacos were mediocre/OK. Very stripped down presentation and flavours.  They forgot my salsa with my order and never brought out water I asked for and I asked twice. Place was not busy. Had to ask the next table (and only other customer there) if I could grab a piece of paper towel off their roll.
Easy parking though....that deserves a star.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMeJWG6bFx8JI4EFfgyBMjQcRHIQETh0LpWUx6q&fid=0x0:0x93b04e724289e006"],"When":"2024-6-2"},{"Name":"Viona Halim","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV5PMLEtvgkAwv2IjmL8XXm0-Ly_XpBo5Kd0Hv2pxoQ26_Hfy4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This Mexican eatery/store is a real gem in Maple Ridge. There's certainly a shortage of good food places in the neighborhood but Lupita is special. We like the homecook vibes and super friendly service.

You can come here to have some real good Mexican food and load up on ingredients for your next taco party or whatnot. Get some snacks and drinks while you're there as well. Prices are reasonable and portion is good! We had quick supper there at around 5pm on Saturday and there's barely anybody there. It felt like we had a private dining at a quaint Mexican house. Will definitely come back and try their other menu","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNYjkwkoWFMZ_hyu0onW6jcfMpPLh15xuilj7a_&fid=0x0:0x93b04e724289e006"],"When":"2022-9-29"},{"Name":"Monkey Couch","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKjBJae2rKS_uXWCMGu9-Vey95DYSzaWVHAACfGX9Lt21SDIw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My husband and I ate here once before deciding to get catering from them for an event. Their food was delicious and moist. We had the chicken and the rajas( very tasty vegetarian ) . During the order placement the staff was helpful, and guided us through what we needed. For pick up they were very friendly, on time, and even helped load the vehicle. I will highly recommend this establishment if one is considering them for any catered event where one wants more of an authentic Mexican cuisine.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Levi Spencer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU95CQfsNB1hgrisMVHOi2FZwWI4Q3hGwtRXXEjl3ktEj-FXKKr=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"By far one of the best places for food in maple ridge. I’ve been coming here regularly for a good while and have never once been disappointed by the food. Whether it’s chips n salsa, tacos or burritos it’s always hot fresh and delicious. On top of that the portions are big and the prices are good and you can tell that the staff genuinely care about the food they make and service they provide. If your looking for somewhere good to eat in ridge that won’t cost you an arm and a leg I’m begging you to try Lupitas","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Marisa K.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLi7SX2QVAXxFvj7573IifKFZ8CRitFIgTfzmHwC6PM_IedvQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I frequent Sushi Misoya quite a few times throughout the year and it’s always been really good! I always do take-out so I cannot speak to what a dine-in experience is like (their dining area is limited), but their online ordering and pick-up service is smooth and seamless. The staff always greets me upon walking in and is kind and friendly during checkout.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNuLqfOYv8hDtWapXG1ygxmwF-u5aUdaW_YIdOs&fid=0x0:0xbcb7842ab47f5c2"],"When":"2024-6-24"},{"Name":"E Melo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVGgY2yvtEUZjjmIeI3CkEsrZ_2cfgxymAQyKJ9_Agamx8ifCVJ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is one of my favourite sushi restaurants in the entire Lower Mainland! Every food I’ve ordered from there is great!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nena","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXail0hFaAr6UWwh19nZb5xdJGv0KAVLSD1VnM8OXnts_-tYe0Nrw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The service is quite prompt and friendly, space inside is kind of small around 6 tables but clean and cozy. I would recommend this place and come back myself.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNLjFkFaC5H75XtyvXaII_NDspTBAbczrTWSjmI&fid=0x0:0xbcb7842ab47f5c2"],"When":"2018-9-14"},{"Name":"Ingrid Kwok","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJpJ7BDSOGvowBGNTTCIxIzO8iKdPQulZrzi56sGNYHPbL7Hw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Food is good there and the service is attentive. You got to choose what you want in your combo, for around CAD15. The portion is good enough for one person. Everything comes with miso soup and salad.

There is some parking space right outside.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO9Lt-lvTfPY-99P8uH4yqTDsZFJDJuESUjUh33&fid=0x0:0xbcb7842ab47f5c2"],"When":"2020-1-5"},{"Name":"K G","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWdwVGlhF7NS5T1ernsxiY-PjGbDSDg6Aw0Kx8ABcKDVRDfs2C0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Family owned restaurant, you can see and taste the perfection when they give you the food! [{"Name":"Tuly Kovich","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJjJJXegr2TKBRzxxmQv0AzOL1K90md7w2M6zPCaLqrnsCaZQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"These were the worst rolls I have ever had 👎.

The BC roll was dry, the BBQ and smoked salmon were not fresh, and the BBQ salmon was more like canned salmon, the cucumber was soft, dark and not crisp, the lettuce was cut into huge chunks, like a salad, the overall appearance of the rolls was definitely not appetising. This will be the first and last time I use your services.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPbSbkN0I7EH8edJ_mQbBA2u8nD75c94-vUCN7J&fid=0x0:0x571c55c99147cad"],"When":"2024-11-10"},{"Name":"Olivia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI8FHEV2jJpqQKxRRah5S0AcrOdPUSs4gnI91GQDoM_Fo6y9w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This place never disappoints. Every time I pass through the area I have to get sushi from here. I’m vegetarian and appreciate the extensive list of non-seafood menu items. The sushi is so fresh, prepared so beautifully, and the service is always so friendly.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNw1HC6tdW-UJqSzlXqRWUGJpsu6QyrSc2qvdQU&fid=0x0:0x571c55c99147cad"],"When":"2024-7-22"},{"Name":"edward guan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXRzlm7-6FLvtAFhYIT6QLvtnPHOja6G1bfQsda_5P4Fx5HDePK=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Portion are pretty big. The teriyaki sauce is not salty like other Japanese restaurant.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOEoTYipXvTJo2l15r4RfS5d8Q3X5HI4I4Had_3&fid=0x0:0x571c55c99147cad"],"When":"2024-9-2"},{"Name":"Eston Stone","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVZf50HNdIFLNy3MPJ7T0z_SKBvprsk5TrIt59f6By2jLBx8sq5rg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best sushi place in Maple Ridge! Tons of variety on the menu with gluten friendly and vegan options as well. I had the pan fried Gyozas, Popeye rolls and Miso Soup, all of which were delicious. In addition to all of this, the service was great and the cost of everything was very affordable. I will definitely be back here!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPbwS0B2TUtTvUz_iJW-ROW10sjEVUy0HHa3pzW&fid=0x0:0x571c55c99147cad"],"When":"2023-5-8"},{"Name":"Elaenia Eickhoff","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV_pZ7FbcappEmIZnzV5ZyKrNYTV99w5Dv5zuf0FX6V7ywDd_k=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Absolutely fantastic food and service, everything was absolutely perfect. They also had a fantastic vegetarian section, which was really wonderful. A bit expensive, but not too bad for sushi. Would highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Elin Youn","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWiNZs70kwlKzkMNGX8yp-Z2vmBDo8ebGorVWkmQ-pAHR3ox96Z=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We always feel welcomed. They are all friendly. Food is always great. One of our favourite roll is Canadian roll. (salmon, bacon&maple syrup) They are really good at fried menu.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOuzVcsGya_mLh0gPSn5mfuwRET8qGXHCPBS2Hf&fid=0x0:0x571c55c99147cad"],"When":"2022-5-17"},{"Name":"Adam Flores","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWe4BRmj5KQqIAAUG5nAnmdw7_yQFCU9UsNd4ZM98dGlhGwNFOK=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A great sushi restaurant! I bought a maple family party and an assembly line platter. A lot of food for a low cost. I also like the unique menu with funny sushi names like the barbie roll and sweating moose roll. I would suggest anyone to come here for good sushi on a budget.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN87Zany4bmidEpnQTvNK3CpUwyhsyTL1cF1sEX&fid=0x0:0x571c55c99147cad"],"When":"2023-1-15"},{"Name":"Cynthia P","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXg93SXj5dd4sLMrVK8VK4t9n4YdsIr74HXqTAORL0LtXv2ihq7=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This places defines the beauty of small businesses. This is a place that truly cares about the food they serve and the customers they serve the food to. I was so impressed of the livelihood that this place brings even before I walked in. You can tell the owners/operators are artsy, crafty, and have a genuine heart for the community.

Plus, this is one of the most vegetarian friendly sushi restaurants I have been to. Definetly the most veggie friendly in maple ridge. As for the food, creative and delicious! And they even have me miso soup and jellies as a free add on from ordering two rolls. Thank you maple sushi, truly!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPJjso_yPj9tKM3WcUup-UXpVg_wkU4n7UCq7YB&fid=0x0:0x571c55c99147cad"],"When":"2020-10-10"}]

[{"Name":"Marcos Garcia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVrIx99K0w17o1_jz1_EhQur2HjhBKK7Idj_Dw1mjT3aruNUbguXA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Got the Bacon Bourbon pizza and yam fries. Amazing match! Gotta thanks the waiter for the recommendation. It fed two adults, and we left quite satisfied.
Plus, I finally found a brewry with stout beer during summer.
Great isrish style stout! Please don't stop serving it!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMh3Ar4G5dD-l0CW4pMCAx32wVm1cY4GfM_A0eA&fid=0x0:0x5f717eeda86fa95d"],"When":"2024-8-10"},{"Name":"James Mendonca","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKDOYVs1G-8iT9QF6Fj3_nUauDo1DS6zISrEp3lZ9wij4inDQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I went to Witchcraft Bistro as my alternative restaurant when Big Feast Bistro was closed. I am glad I did because this was an exceptional restaurant, as far as bar and grills go. When I took my seat, I was served with complimentary popcorn, which is a first for any restaurant I went to. I ordered the Cobb Salad with Ranch dressing. The ingredients were fresh and tasted great with each other, both the meat and vegetables. The interior also had a charming, antiquated look to it with some memorabilia decor. It looked as if I was in a brewery. The service was good as well. The restaurant was not too busy on a Saturday, which was good for a comfortable experience. If I happen to be in Maple Ridge again, I will make sure to come back here.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOpKh-rWJZNyWUp7CRpbijRMTYYqb7Gf9slBxTx&fid=0x0:0x5f717eeda86fa95d"],"When":"2024-1-28"},{"Name":"Dev Deteriorate","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW174d3q1C68k3CIpTb3Y2mjhbzxdBX3351-dOCoOvMShWcsYWq=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Been going to The Witch for quite awhile as a local. I love the staff, the environment, but the food took a bit of a nosedive upon my last visit. Chicken was cold on the nachos, toppings were distributed poorly, but hey, compared to a lot of places in Ridge they still come out on top for the price.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPn-nVLjhB9d7fWh-RIkQwxFdhZFR6ni3Mgka85&fid=0x0:0x5f717eeda86fa95d"],"When":"2024-6-28"},{"Name":"MemoirsOfATaco","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJQ5DdT6mOsHuY3dVXp6jjjmxgHYhM1OThCPrwnDkIC5BCQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Their patio was open, it was slightly raining however it's heated, great food and drink options, definitely need more servers as ours appeared to be the only one working. The burger was phenomenal, the mac n cheese was bland, the chili was tasty and the Cornbread was the star of the show.

Bourbon Bacon Burger
Mushrooms, Bacon, Maple Bourbon Glaze, White Cheddar, Onion Straws on a house made patty, lettuce and tomato; opted for Mac n Cheese.

Chili
Hearty Bean and Veggie Chili will warm your soul…with a touch of spice! Served with Warm Cornbread on the side","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNfn3WuqfNzyXNY9HHxRjcAQAcSamb0XCikP4g&fid=0x0:0x5f717eeda86fa95d"],"When":"2023-5-7"},{"Name":"Stacey Loyer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJb25-9L3z8l-uQ3sV-lfk_-XymjGohRjUkpMUjUR9RUVg32A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A-mazing burger!!! Had the Witchcraft Bacon Chedder burger. So tasty, so fresh, with the best fries. Hubby had the Cajun chicken soup - the soups are always good!!
Great atmosphere on the patio on a nice sunny day. Great service","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOu7b2Poxz_XRemrwjdMBoqUDjR3cIOhFFp5NFz&fid=0x0:0x5f717eeda86fa95d"],"When":"2024-7-14"},{"Name":"Fran Fernandez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUY8cTrDAIV2uuA1AnOK6YWoMWcwOAd6RQynZ2wV2ujPfJ4pZ4X=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I loved the place, I didn’t have any problem, the food was really good, the service was fast, we didn’t wait at all and the person was really nice! 👍🏻","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOEKiccwu98Efq3YHPpqpUxoJdCEFvC457w4EkZ&fid=0x0:0x5f717eeda86fa95d"],"When":"2024-6-27"},{"Name":"Amanda","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV9MO0wCjI3eHFcpwJIbNEoOJF-dENYGFlKJbu1QuPzKRpml52x=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best pizza I’ve ever had! I had the bourbon bacon pizza. Watermelon sour was amazing! Server was super nice. My partner got a forty creek BBQ burger, amazing. Was the best first experience someone could ask for, will be back for sure. Left my phone at home so here’s my leftovers:","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPg_bPR9WoDapdwzyY1BsT3xUjTmXXUsDbygYV3&fid=0x0:0x5f717eeda86fa95d"],"When":"2022-9-3"},{"Name":"Gareth Anderson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUp9plk8U5ZTE_JEQpERglsO1AgdZCpFAY72fA0J30Y_nsJrBJOQg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This Sunday my wife and I decided to checkout Maple Ridge. We spotted Witchcraft Beer Market and stopped in. The waitress was very friendly. We had their kettle chip nachos and it was amazingly delicious. There are three versions to choose from, we had the buffalo chicken. Their beer selections was pretty good, however there was two we were interested in trying that wasn’t available but that did not take away from the great experience.. Definitely worth a visit and we’ll sure be back✌🏾","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMJMoDBYzePl9_kha4iVonrKCcMOiSaHbnex37H&fid=0x0:0x5f717eeda86fa95d"],"When":"2023-7-24"}]

Would highly recommend, amazing prices as well (super size mixed chicken and lamb donair was $12.99).","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM22k5jDsY5m6RxabB20heCh2q4v9A8a_Rs1VC-\u0026fid=0x0:0xd44927ceff1395af"],"When":"2024-10-10"},{"Name":"Ammaar Malik Awan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXWPvJ4-9e6vSq5FkEkPtt1WaLR8XEX3AL4DiLo4qqRApuu3nAP=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I was in Maple Ridge last night. Browsed some food places and ended up at Donair City. The couple managing it is welcoming and friendly. The food is absolutely amazing. Loved it. 😍  I would love to come back again. As a South Asian, i found the food less spicy, but it is still worth it. Portions were generous, and prices are low comparatively.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMCdMEZcIrA3SB3tU_VHAfBE5ihgAjCn4ntdTNK\u0026fid=0x0:0xd44927ceff1395af"],"When":"2023-12-13"},{"Name":"Dominic Kohler","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIr_Rds6INzk8uBD6vTiDGl0q4vd8v53cFPe8-iHXMsWrqpx1g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"First time trying donair city. Lots of food, and super fresh. Can't go wrong with the price either, with the lamb platter being $13.99. Really good bang for your buck. [{"Name":"Strange Protocol","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJpcS4LA5T7o-BiPIQZEMAIs6czOPJCu3Z_Aks4N2sDFZy5FQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Not sure if something has changed with business ownership but both the food and overall experience has gone down !

1) Got charged for Meat Tacos but I had ordered veggie tacos. Only came to know when I asked them to send me receipt. The cashier confirmed it's veggie but just mislabeled, sure but than I had remind Cashier to refund me the difference which he did but the whole interaction seemed bizarre.

2) Ordered 4 piece chicken meal. Their online menu says it comes with Gravy, but it didn't so I had to buy one. It's fine but no consistency in pricing / displayed menu between online / offline pricing.

3) Food is not great. Veggie tacos were the saddest I ever had, they were very small portioned for what these guys charged. There were barely any beans, sauce. Not even a hot sauce was given on the side, had to settle for bland tacos with poor filling.The taco shell were white and tasted like the one you get from superstore, just not great.  4 piece chicken was meh, it didn't taste same as before ,  soggy ..chewy meat. probably meat was not fresh, who knows. Only good thing was fries were not soggy.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mel Renter","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJEfQZDOgiGzmykYdPan5EnxDCYzS6ax3Bu0T-k0IRV3HYDAA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very good, will try most things eventually. I even called there to find out what kind…home made was the answer. No surprise !","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sarah Derman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXeXMApt_w0BmokoenlHKya2iQgrMJdxA6HQ6y4TkU6YvmIipI=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had them come to our grade 7 party at the elementary school. You’d be missing out if you didn’t eat here at least once.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Hera","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIdYW_WcRSplgCknqyw_ou-UIcLqtlctjImZLTZlLBg4sOZ7tlM=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Went here 3 times now and service & food are always great. Had burrito and fried chicken . Fried chicken was different one of a kind and cooked very well .
Spicy .
The beef burritos was fresh and tasty . Could have used more beef and in general I prefer the shredded beef style opposed to ground beef.
Overall tho I’d call this a win .
I’d eat there again .it was pretty good","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Dominic Kohler","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIr_Rds6INzk8uBD6vTiDGl0q4vd8v53cFPe8-iHXMsWrqpx1g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Finally tried the food truck after seeing all the good reviews. As a celebration for getting my license and being able to drive on my own I stopped by to treat myself. I've heard so many good things. I ended up choosing the large chicken burrito. It was made fresh and ready to go in 5 minutes. Has a few errands to run but it was still hot when I came home. Lots of great flavors going on, I loved the seasoned chicken as well as the choice of veggies also. The rice was quite nice as well, was like a purple color, so that was new for me. Lots of fresh quality ingredients went into this. The Chipotle sauce that comes in it was to die for. It was so good and was a cherry on top to this already good burrito. I highly recommend it to everyone, stop by pick up some beers at Ridgeway and a burrito.","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews: [{"Name":"Maya Schouten","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUO9x8oFl1z-2ncMLmfWu71Y053fpa-t4BYxDTv_0_AzOsAsA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Mona Pizza in Maple Ridge is a standout. Their service is top-notch, the crust on their pizzas is crispy and bursting with flavor, and their prices are competitive. Plus, they offer a wide selection of sodas to complement your meal. It's a must-visit for pizza lovers in Maple Ridge. My favourite pizza in town.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPsTPpoeJwwjJy5GBR9WWMrnlmv5MJ48gaJt-s\u0026fid=0x0:0xf4884f71279ae235"],"When":"2024-5-30"},{"Name":"Sonia Sareen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLiDW-rt0-DUnaWiyEifM9hg1rz-r3JSXx6bsiUf6kZL83eNA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Recently, we got a chance to try this hidden gem of maple ridge. My friend was recommending big Brand name like Pizza Hut, domino, Panago but I don't know why I choose this store for our special dinner party. we placed a Quite big order. it was Game day n they were super Busy. We ordered a lots of different items almost all items.  At the time of picking up the order, we felt some thing extra which makes them different from other pizzas store. we noticed that they have a huge variety of pizzas, drinks \u0026  they told us that they are serving keto crust, gluten free crust, vegan cheese, plant based pepperoni etc. Amazing everything at one place. they  Gave us few  complimentary drinks. which was interesting, who don't like free Stuffs. Store was Super clean, staff was very helping but still we were not sure about the taste of food because it was our first order so we all were very excited. we came back to the hotel \u0026 we start to try every item \u0026 we were speechless, all items were made with fresh \u0026 proper balanced ingredients n sauce. Pizzas \u0026 chicken wings were Awesome. it was so delicious that after finish it my friend order some food again. everyone enjoyed a lot at that day. Everyone were appreciating  my suggestion \u0026 we are waiting that when we can go there for have this food again. Everyone should try this small n locally family owned business. Highly recommend.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"martin andersen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK5isR81obH5tVmlSlmgLEcHdDcK4UjDh0_nAgkfHIul6d-HA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I feel this owner goes way out of his way to please the customer. I haven’t been eating a lot of pizza lately, but decided today was the day, I ordered one large pizza, only like $23 worth. And selected to pick it up at 12:00-12:30 pm, not realizing they didn’t open until 3:00pm. When I arrived to pick up the order the sign said open, but I noticed the business hours were 3:00-11:00pm. When I walked in the owner said he saw the order and drove straight to the store to make the pizza. I felt super bad for unconvincing him on his time off, but was super happy to have the pizza. And the pizza was amazing, I will definitely be ordering again very soon.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Laura Edwardson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUJX6nOwhdj3WIXQTRA7h6KjuT6TDLLu_XlCd0QcX5edLKznOw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I just ordered a baked lasagne from Mona’s and Wow! It’s my first time here and I have lived in Maple Ridge for 30 years… what I have been missing. The flavors ( especially the tomatoes that tasted off the vine ) and the good cheese ratio at a great price were all impressive ! Thank you, I’ll be back.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Salij Shrestha","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKjVCJE6xjPX3-rWN_UqcMn6I0MeVIv265rCmUawjOV-IJZDA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The dedication of this restaurant to serve customer is unmatched. Perfect taste combination and accurate delivery timing is what has made me regular customer of Mona Pizza. I prefer to call their cook pizza artist as they always amaze me with the freshness and flavours.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Juan Pulido","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLcXPRJOi53Zd0i5CXX5r2JtJPzQfXYXCZgjSW1_EUe5BIR5g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Mona Pizza has by far the best vegan pizza in Maple Ridge or maybe the whole GVRD. My son has dietary restrictions due to allergies and have tried many different restaurants and store bought pizzas and could not find one that he liked. He loves Mona Pizza and asks for it whenever its family Pizza Night. Please keep up the good work, we are customers for life.\n\nPS - we love that they have Jarritos too! :)","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nakia Maher","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVNHq13yHIHj7Vld6XI4uJaAXCOznlMvaF8kTpZD78kZ_-d4ERO=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Just ordered from here. Pizza was bla and barely any toppings. Got a 2 large pizzas  a meat lovers with jalapeño and I did a 50 50. Half taco half cheese burger.   All were lacking in the meat  especially the taco. Took off the  lettuce and tomato and there was barley any meat or cheese. Also had wings. They were ok. For over 80 dollars this was not worth it 😒   will  not be ordering from here again","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nishtha Arora","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJMmzHFddSpR6IkZJ7L7mtJ9zjaN8kJdGBphf-20HelYse2dw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Hidden gem of maple ridge. Pizza , chicken wings all stuff was delicious, we tried keto pizza with plant based pepperoni \u0026 vegan cheese pizza. highly recommend. 10 out of 10 \u0026 they have a huge variety of specialty drinks. everyone must try.","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Munchica","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXbQ6ACs51IPQJlRLrmnunOErED8bimOf5-y1uov4EWpuZvjQQjrA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba8-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"It’s an average tasting Chinese buffet. There is lots of variety but some items have been out for a while and the food is not frequently replenished. The sweet and sour pork is good and the buffet items were hit or miss. The ice cream selection for the buffet is good as it includes 6 flavors including mint chocolate chip, maple walnut, cappuccino flake, vanilla, strawberry, and chocolate. The fruits are watermelon and oranges. They have salad and the classic mall type Chinese food items in the buffet. Nothing was outstanding but everything was okay and edible. Price is alright for what you get. It is nostalgic for the good old days when Chinese buffets were more popular.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOY2Mni2uetbMXVWJyYkHULBorqr4PljxAa7Bpy&fid=0x0:0x85871f0dc12414ee"],"When":"2024-8-20"},{"Name":"Jaime Libby","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXWcuQUZBXxCRF5-27cV4MrzyteNpvh8tPhlqiQSMkU18wPjoAf=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"It’s got good food and the buffet is cheap I my opinion so good value for the food
