[{"Name":"Alex","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVxP-ADvohB6hXpEbci04qD4fdlJ8qjEvYJvIIZqjiOIuWU9BVM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Just wow! I consider myself a pizza connoisseur so here are my thoughts.

At $24.99, this is their large House Special. 7 toppings plus I added an additional 2 at $3 a piece. This is their normal cheese portion, I did not add extra. For what you get I consider this to be very good bang for your buck, especially these days.

Toppings are high quality and plentiful. Rather than the round, sausage like bacon pebbles most pizza places use, they actually use real crumbled bacon which I don’t see a lot of unless I’m at a higher end pizza place. The crust is perfectly crispy on the bottom/edges and light and airy on the inside. They even boast that they have “the best crust ever”

What’s more important to note is that after eating half a large pizza, it actually sat very light. I actually felt GOOD after eating this and not gassy or bloated/ heartburn etc (anyone pushing 40 knows what I’m talking about I’m sure😂)

Store was clean. Service was great. 9/10","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPsYdQZyDB_Ci7xCXRluB9LZj_Bvi2HOY06MKg0&fid=0x0:0xd880286c53ef560d"],"When":"2024-6-9"},{"Name":"Sarah Sun","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIS4kxxg3eoIDesJDI4dnOObZnXngPnZams8NTEkCB6TuqoGQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The best pizza ever!
Once I’ve visited my friends house we always order from show me the pizza and this place have the best pizza!!!!! The owener and servers were always kind and friendly. Their topings are plenty and dough is not that thin or thick! Just perfect amount! I saw how they make the pizza while i was waiting mine, they put plenty of cheese on the top literary they make mountain!! I would recommend this place! Who ever didnt try yet please please try it! We won’t be regret!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPdmc-vdE6XXpSQYNzJSwbn8HjW-njE07ggA2qt&fid=0x0:0xd880286c53ef560d"],"When":"2024-3-17"},{"Name":"Ben Pistilli","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJPgHCE2Bl9HeHSr_hupnNI74mFb3_8U5Z4eflgiV5v1aOQ3w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I ordered from show me the pizza all the time. I have never had a bad experience since tonight. My med pizza crust was very thin, and that's never happened before. I called and spoke, which I think was the owner, who explained that the crust was very thin. With no real interest in my concerns, I just scrubbed me off and said they haven't changed. I told him that every time I ordered, which  is once every two weeks on a Friday, the pizza crust had never been this thin. I'm not impressed with  the customer service..","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Danielle Clutchey","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIRCh0NOmnAADlI4nVZhaF3rW6eFVnKJ1w8_H_BB3BEZDSf7g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"We just tried this place for the first time after hearing great things. Ordered 3 pizzas and an order of bread sticks. Got home and the bread sticks are basically black and hard as a rock. Absolutely disgusting. I called and the manager laughed at me saying "you're calling to complain about break sticks?"

We just spent over $70 of our hard earned money here and that is the service we receive. After asking what could be done to rectify this I was told "we can maybe send you an etransfer". I'm at a loss for words, what a disappointment.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Stephanie Henderson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIvd6TE41ofXSIQsVETEKQwe90URxDLRLP3ccyJkWtaimnS=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We found our new favourite pizza joint!
First time ordering and we will definitely be back.
The pizza is so good, hot & fresh. Amazing crust, good quality ingredients. The staff are very friendly, and the location is clean. We also love that each pizza has a dip of your choice included.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOvPLj8LQB2lC07SuS7fIEbUpRhOnGVw8R813o&fid=0x0:0xd880286c53ef560d"],"When":"2024-2-24"},{"Name":"Luca Pollzien","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJQPGy8BO9cFSB3hMmrdn2FkKoLhKbttXWhtQdoPTRULPmg2eA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best pizzeria in maple ridge. Amazing crust, they are generous on their toppings. There chicken taco is my favourite and it’s delicious.  The only thing is they are a little pricey but compared to like dominoes they are similar in price.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tracey Mumford","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWMfVTlpNfz1D4YJyisCZf5-uh-f1hK902N886lBFgkQbhqGuMO=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great Pizza! Highly recommend.we used to always get Panago but just for the dips. So now we buy a few jars and order from Show Me the Pizza!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Roman Krzaczek Quadra Island Cortes Island and Campbell River Realtor","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUcVEVXBFySu8YcMgVSOhN0lchLPLRTEHigvCzWxArNZf_NUJSS=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"These guys saved a life tonight! I was hangry and they came just in time. Another minute late and I’d be dead. Took them about an hour and 20 minutes from the time of order but I understand that it’s Friday and they’re busy, I won’t be an as***le and complain about this because the final product was excellent. I ordered 2 small- bbq chicken and veggie. They were both great. I’d prefer more bbq sauce but it worked well. Excellent friendly service and I didn’t die :)  I will order again sometime.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMcX2ncPekJuUjchw9E82h16g3bMMMWVb3Pavx6&fid=0x0:0xd880286c53ef560d"],"When":"2018-11-10"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Colin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUJvFgjJxxaJNXmYFM985fOV76JjLyWWI2SRC_1FM5CsDcPKHP-=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Simply put, NOT ENOUGH MEAT on burritos.   The portion is RIDICULOUSLY less than other similar restaurants.  You can see one tiny bite of chicken here.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPkpEyFVddmeFVY7C5LOIdDhu1xBf2XSyvPSvz_&fid=0x0:0xa88389ac5adc0719"],"When":"2024-7-29"},{"Name":"Selena Crossland","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWWLe1RgQsIrdrrFgWveqgVWMWYardQdE6s5tHcE0xt0ncrTVv1=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"We ordered using Door Dash App & picked up ourselves. On arrival no employee was out front and food was not ready when app said it would be, no other customers were there, so I waited for the man to prep it (not a problem-didn’t take long). The restaurant was an absolute mess- garbages were overflowing in customer area, kitchen prep area had trash overflowing onto floor and food everywhere like someone had a food fight—I really should have asked to cancel my order based on the clear lack of cleanliness but don’t think I can do that on DoorDash> if I was walking in, I would have just walked out. I thought maybe they just had a massive busy time possibly - benefit of the doubt right. The man making our burritos was very kind & helpful but there was a woman employee who seemed very angry. I wished them a good night when leaving.  The male employee did a great job making our Burritos, they tasted great. The owner needs to take this business seriously and hire more personnel to keep up on cleanliness & customer care because they have a great location & potential.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jennifer Boyarski","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU0aWoR9tP6UWC4FWVEUvojoQ0uotSMnW5x7c3_cjC3HNo3X4t6=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I've been here a couple times now, I've only tried the hard shell tacos which are good! It would be nice if they could spread out the toppings better so you can have them with each bite not just one bite! The staff are not friendly at all, they only talk to eachother in Punjab and dont make eye contact. When I pay I thank them and tell them to have a nice day and they dont say anything back at all. Definitely doesn't make me want to go back :/","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNbm--h8SossxA39tx2IzD3aWOpP4bkE0753Hed&fid=0x0:0xa88389ac5adc0719"],"When":"2024-3-10"},{"Name":"Lena s","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUfiKiTYLYNYzcv_KDpRiDWqOnkYUfmc9MTcnYc7To2ftTRyQ-c=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"The food is really good but the workers have changed overtime. I come here rather often and now there's a team of a few brown girls who constantly chatter and laugh in front of me and other customers and constantly chatter between each other in their language which I find rather unprofessional honestly the bad service is what made me give up on that spot. It really makes you uncomfortable.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Vas Bach","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL25ojHCD2l96tyD0UB3_FqaxkLEOIjDIOCQp9OpjjObikP7g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"As other customers have mentioned - good food and horrible service. I cannot stress this enough. The employees are rude and once I ordered cutlery and the other girl beside her repeated what I said , the word " cutlery " in a very, extremely mocking tone then both talked to each other in Punjab and giggled between themselves. Its like they don't even hide that they're talking about you. Don't go there you'll feel rather humiliated. 👎 It's not the first ,certainly not last time they do this I don't know if the owner actually cares about their customers but that ain't it.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sean Salo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWucIBVR4qGVxSLvhlsLk6M9Kbm_gqCpRxx9oyfTrg9rGX4EGa6=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Food was fine, nothing to write home about. Probably not as good as Mucho Burrito.

HOWEVER I am giving them 5 stars because of the exceptional service. I was very tired and gave them a stupid difficult order, then gave multiple conflicting instructions as they built my bowls. They were very pleasant and accommodating.

Kudos to the staff that worked on the evening of Sun Jan 29!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMp5BwnMnCWQNzyJaZfOzZMGUXmrMfTjmikRGw1&fid=0x0:0xa88389ac5adc0719"],"When":"2023-1-30"},{"Name":"Maya Bobaya","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVbJPYUQj7PFZTXR1S5D0G0Oad7ygp3dUbJE0LvmHlzmnUXUMi2Bg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Food here is pretty decent, but the service is horrendous. I come here every so often and everyone is just stupidly rude. I find they get irritated just by customers arriving and employees will talk over you and whisper like they are making fun of you. Then have the audacity to ask for a tip at the end. Not slaying guys, 0/10","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sebastian Coats","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU2Y9B1Az1yiix4vJNO9GRSVGod1oYZBVxRYMYexyw301qjJlZV=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"The lady serving my friend and I was very rude, had a very dismissive and uninterested attitude. She was talking on the phone while serving us and when I asked her a question, she said what with a condescending look on her face. She put way too much of each topping to the point where we could barely taste the beef on our tacos. The whole time we were eating, we could hear her loudly talking on the phone and letting out these very loud laughs. Terrible experience overall and I’ll never be eating here again.","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Eunkyung Kwon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI8QbBfbB3hty99EF294UH5765EN21uQd87nV3J6NDBZA_Hmg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I visit this sushi restaurant often, and it’s always a great experience. The sushi is fresh, delicious, and beautifully presented. The staff are friendly, attentive, and always make me feel welcome.

If you’re looking for high-quality sushi at a reasonable price, I highly recommend this place.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNXurKrffUqVOG-xCGFNV1-iEQHmtuhG-zFucBI&fid=0x0:0xdd1fa9894629ade5"],"When":"2024-12-18"},{"Name":"Ian Kim","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJPXqdCYowBQ_CfYk2HQttHh7IDBeUHX7Du1VtrT_RMZb6-=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Some of my friends recommended this restaurant and it was so good today
Food is awesome and fresh also enough quantities.
Sushi is great and even ramen is good too
My recommendation menu is Deluxe combo
Servers are so kind
Price is reasonable
Highly recommend!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPfl1My_AqQ5NX-Na8t-pEeB7o4X82urvdjXJw&fid=0x0:0xdd1fa9894629ade5"],"When":"2024-11-2"},{"Name":"Rolando_ Rose","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIQBfjayv2V3eqQ6nmwU1uOEqgsWCG5VdwRxO3uXCF1EsXQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very satisfying bento box lunch! Staff are attentive even in a busy lunch. Green tea was served as soon I placed my order. Tea was nice and hot, served in a very cutesy tea cup with sushi and sashimi design. Followed by a nice, hot, not overly salty miso soup. After just a few minutes, bento box was served. Beef teriyaki is tender, not too sweet-not too salty, perfect for my taste buds! Prawn tempura was perfectly fried, airy but substantially appetizing, vegetable spring roll is crunchy and not greasy, vegetable tempura consists of yam, sweet potato and acorn squash are equally delicious, California roll is simply irresistible! Everything is 5 star except the salad, which has a lot of dressing. Overall, it was a good meal! Located at 207 Street, Maple Ridge BC, easy accessible from Lougheed Highway or Dewdney Trunk Road.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOwKyq6gqLdYZ5cp0mfJfw1N_OWPan3NEAySHM&fid=0x0:0xdd1fa9894629ade5"],"When":"2024-10-29"},{"Name":"Sky Jang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXsnlFBmRy7tyi6QC1WQMYS-_XgUyK7bm7m7BJrwzV_4Y89SkWE=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Their lunch special is on another level. The portions are huge and offer a variety of selections. Needless to say, the taste is great.

However, the quality of service could be improved. They ran out of trays, so I had each dish served individually, which resulted in a pretty big gap in between. I received the karaage only after finishing all the other food. Additionally, a server forgot about our beer, so we had to wait for a while and ask another server for it again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOuWCPoI_R_1___NHTguJEGnU4YZtkX-f2MAnpW&fid=0x0:0xdd1fa9894629ade5"],"When":"2024-9-24"},{"Name":"JOY N","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJLByk_DtKe11r1xKloMPLR9l4eCSw7rmxqnoF5M1-9uuakdg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We enjoyed the dinner in wonderful restaurant. My kids like Donkatsu and cali rolls, udong. The pork cutlet(donkatsu) was crispy on the outside and soft on the inside, and the meat was soft, so it was good for children to eat. Salmon poke was well seasoned and went well with vegetables. Salmon sushi is fresh and soft, delicious! Very kind staffs. Thanks! (Want to eat now!!)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMQBpwlfu6tCzKPU7kQoQmdqbYWUkKJJntfQqSh&fid=0x0:0xdd1fa9894629ade5"],"When":"2024-10-29"},{"Name":"DIIMIDOSE Mineral","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVQNWs0yEkOwk1jNu86jwF6IfrjSnApXJ6_zs8EV5QwFxJIdOU=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"They have fast service, I visit probably once a week, they know there customers and always make me feel happy to come back. I love their Dynamite roll and tempura the best and have brought some of my family there too! I never really had sushi much before going here but it was such I nice place I wanted to keep coming back <3! Something I especially love is even though they get lots of take out orders their service for dine in never suffers, I can't say the same for a lot of places around here so its really nice to see!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Andre Hylton","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX_PChy1Th0kOGUfQeikUPffIevYW6u7GEJEnZ-s8pmdSDTb2GM=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I visited this sushi restaurant today, and while the food was quite enjoyable, I found the service could use improvement. The staff seemed a bit inattentive, especially when it came to checking in for drink refills or additional orders. It would be great if they were a bit more responsive to customer needs, especially for basics like water. Overall, the food was good, but a little more attentiveness from the staff would make the dining experience even better.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sherwin Quilay","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU46rfoheSfvIQONToEKkejzhkSa1wImF0GNRLIYDvcMziumOlP=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Wonderful experience! Celebrated our fathers 75th birthday and they welcomed our party of 10.  We extended our stay for a total of 2 1/2 hours and they gladly welcomed us!  I got their salmon poke bowl and it is amazing!  Will definitely stop by when I'm in the are next!  Food prices are very competitive:)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPmt7MLI3z37d9uV-xFwLUiSYszkSZ7xszPREaZ&fid=0x0:0xdd1fa9894629ade5"],"When":"2023-11-16"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Daniel Vasquez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVfH4IGtDH-RZPfkWL0P5tVuSs9PJ8oLSHVNJs_o3NyG6_oaSvUng=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This place blew my expectations out of the water. This was truly a culinary experience from start to finish. The food quality and flavour were unbelievable, something I wasn't expecting. I would highly recommend this place for a romantic date, business meeting or if you just want to have a fantastic meal. Chef Gordon keeps the menu small and fresh, based on what he's buying - for example he will buy half a cow, do his own cuts and pre the menu based on this.

The service was also great, it is a family run business and would highly recommend you visit. The prices seem high at first, but once you have the first bite you can see why. This ranks as a tie for the best meal ever for me, tied with another restaurant in Vancouver that costs twice as much.

I am not exaggerating by saying that this restaurant should be considered for the Michelin Guide. it is simply that good!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNCBvDzLMY9xCd2xMKgD_Nvd0wHtM5v8ajL9VjK&fid=0x0:0x25c2f0bdeacf27e"],"When":"2023-8-11"},{"Name":"kari k","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKVvcUii6EUlxfY9JlhQ_ZfOv49WO9fppCar9xI2DZ5eIyb=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This place honestly blew me away. The atmosphere is so nice and quaint, the staff were lovely and the food, oh my God. Incredible. It is on the pricier side but honestly 1000% worth it. Treat yourself and come here for a beautiful experience. Even tried things both my friends had and it was all delicious","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMQUcjMey3Cgo-T05w6RD7RUWsE5E-3GeQvF2k&fid=0x0:0x25c2f0bdeacf27e"],"When":"2024-2-18"},{"Name":"Jozi Child","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVFGifWG8BdvF18VaKbFjDKs7F8rZetFQSzDeQ-MEH000zpoiCNUQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Meant for the true foodies who appreciate food made with true thought and precision.

Found from google reviews and so happy I did. Easily found right across from the fire house. Amazing service, absolutely delicious food made with care and attention. Not your typical menu where you can count on it being the same each place. For the real deal foodies. Lovely relaxing atmosphere.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO12zpwhA1zxw-L0eD0zfXjQG5hgNge3E2_CUA5&fid=0x0:0x25c2f0bdeacf27e"],"When":"2024-3-9"},{"Name":"Bill Wilson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVrLDUKCB9KhwKlqIkCcXUiASMuWECjsxURVB66vsZhnoGGXEJCJQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We've dining here many times and the food is aleays amazing. Service is top notch too. When you want a tablecloth, nice cutley and a fine evening out you cannot go wrong going there. To start we had cod paddies and beef cappaico, so delious. Then for mains I had the cod and it was perfectly prepared and so tasty. My wife enjoy a pork chop, but it was so tender you didn't need a knife, just marvelous. My daughter enjoyed the roast chicken with a cheese risotto. Spectacular 😍. Dessert was a wonderful "apple" made of chocolate and I don't know what, but it was so good. 100% recommend.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO9Fumu0awyzzZSqGZJ-252GXiYdlzGJdG_3nik&fid=0x0:0x25c2f0bdeacf27e"],"When":"2024-3-3"},{"Name":"Susan Rochefort","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL8rVH08cPR6VwUL0HKwjObsOf9gnrVDYn2ehalr65L6-oUpQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The food and the service was phenomenal. We had made a reservation and once seated the waiter noticed I was having an issue and offered to move us without me even asking. We were looking for fine dining food with a little more casual atmosphere and this place nailed it with the food, service and ambiance.  My husband ordered the steak (medium) and it literally melted in your mouth. The seasoning they used was outstanding as it added flavor without taking away the taste of the meat. I had the chicken which was perfectly cooked. From the great service to the amazing food, this is a hidden gem and we will return!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMKhO2JG-Ub35HwlsCuGd4CPsXJOY3scTW-S0Yn&fid=0x0:0x25c2f0bdeacf27e"],"When":"2018-5-7"},{"Name":"Tabitha B","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUeJCnFjpiqVd5yKgo41hAPVbZX9OKQejn0mrUyiMQ2BxxSg5CJrw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I called to request a donation for a local family who had suffered a tragic loss, hoping for a small gift certificate (between $25-$50) to help raise funds. When I asked if the person I spoke with had five minutes to discuss the request, his response was "for what?" in a rather aggravated tone.

After explaining the reason for my call, I received very emotionless responses. He mentioned the struggles of the restaurant industry post-COVID and how he was barely able to pay his own mortgage. When I clarified that the gift certificate would likely drive business (as the recipient would need to spend beyond the gift's value), his response was, "I get what you're saying, but $25 isn't going to do anything. It's at least $100 per person, but I'll think about it."

Given the lack of empathy and unwillingness to engage positively, I decided not to move forward with the request and ultimately withdrew it. I’m disappointed by the response and would hesitate to support this business moving forward.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Cory Wiebe","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW-koG_9qZqepUMUiLDirk4JwjzAM3O7NdZujZl2CgAT98K4Cp9=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I only thought to take photos half way through our meal...

My wife and I went here for our anniversary. It was a wonderful experience.
I've always seen this place, but never knew it was a restaurant, and had no idea it was the level of restaurant that it is.
First off, the staff were so friendly. It felt more like friendly conversation than a business transaction, plus they were so interesting! I just wanted them to join us for food and chats.
The food was amazing. We had the French onion soup followed by the ravioli and ragu over gnocchi. For me, the basil tomato sauce was the star of the show. Soooo good.
We finished up with a sticky toffee bread pudding on vanilla ice cream.
I'm always most impressed by good soups and good desserts. Both cases were brilliant.

My only sadness was learning that Chef simply didn't have time to do cooking classes. Oh well. I'll just have to go back.

Side note: I loved the dishes.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP9WrA1mYy_iI4nPFRaw_BtAJcGuR2Jl24UOc28&fid=0x0:0x25c2f0bdeacf27e"],"When":"2022-5-10"},{"Name":"John Wu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVX_G2KhQ4UDvw4Nu1dqA3AsXfC53tIj_AZn0iIn-6oDOg1Yst1=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Just the right serving size and very exquisite. The food looked so delicious that we forgot to take pictures before we ate.The waiters are very nice and helpful too. However, the food is very expensive.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP9kctvZ_EfqMKNvER5ZqK9A_9mo7ipN99phLMY&fid=0x0:0x25c2f0bdeacf27e"],"When":"2022-5-22"}]

[{"Name":"Melissa Podeszwa","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXH8wZlaTQYYVgu_4o3fku5tEdCgLkPWHJC4H70cipGFVmezpaA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Our first time and De Dutch didn’t disappoint. Our server was the sweetest, so helpful in making our choices with the menu. Their special Dutch pancakes (I can’t spell the name) were SO tasty. Could have been checked on a couple more times but when she was around our server was outstanding. The eggs Benny were prepared as requested  and just the right amount to bring a little home for later. We added Nutella to the banana and strawberry order, perfect addition—they should add it to the list. We will definitely plan to include De Dutch on our future trips to BC!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOvpeAFJXuAE0Cnl9JLinRv0gSXt2mUpc25-9K8&fid=0x0:0xd538504bf0fe9fa1"],"When":"2023-9-4"},{"Name":"LifewithTosin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUUU2Jn1mF7Q9mrdolXOXRqLqXIguSKcW4osa8ruFJytk_fbC4g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I was there not too long with my 3 kids for breakfast, we were left unattended for like 10minutes, the staffs were passing by without acknowledging us, I understand that you might be busy, but cleaning the tables and letting us know that you will be with us shortly would help, no hello, no acknowledgement. I had to leave when my daughter noticed we were neglected and went somewhere else with great service.
So shameful","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"corbin croney","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX3ABu0kfRMx6ee7BRhw8inZ8kUf8zonsK5yzb6lhPnPy_EQ2WT=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Went for a lovely late morning date and was greeted by the lovely Emma. It wasn’t overly busy but definitely busy enough for only one person. She did absolutely amazing especially for being the only server at the time. Everything was very quick, tasted delicious and no wait times at all. Seems like a very hardworking and very kind girl. 5 stars over the top, would absolutely recommend. Thank you, Emma.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jam I am","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIyrouZBkOM2ZZWfafmD0vlQIU8tX214ZRCbkrXw8EgpFMSJA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had a great breakfast at De Dutch this morning. Our server was Ema, who provided us with amazing service  .I'm pretty picky about the way my eggs were cooked and the cooks did a great job.
Good food & service.....way to go.
We'll be back for sure","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Skye Annderson Brook","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWXCLmKkdO7Mvmd70zV2r8i_5vbh4aDXVp3RfbkBxof-Q5onw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Went to DeDutch this past weekend as a party of four. Two of which were family members from out of town that we recommended this spot to, because usually it’s good.
However, this trip left us feeling disappointed.
Upon entering the restaurant, there was no hostess around so we waited for about 10 minutes until someone noticed and we got seated. We were given menus but not approached by our waitress for another 10 minutes. We kept it simple— ice waters, a coffee, a juice and a hot chocolate without whipped cream. Again, we waited an additional 10 minutes, before the waitress came back missing a majority of the order. The waters were missing and the hot chocolate contained whipped cream— which was asked not to be put on. The waitress instead of simply saying I made a mistake, just proceeded to say we spoke incorrectly and she was just following what was asked.

Another few minutes, waters came out and so did the next hot chocolate, by a different waitress. The hot chocolate was terrible— hardly any actual chocolate in it and mostly lukewarm water. Had to flag down our waitress who seemed to be avoiding our table, and again didn’t address the mistake, just proceeded to call it ‘odd’. So, gave up on that beverage and ordered another different one.

Food came out and was decent— though not worth the price. The bacon was poorly cooked and hardly edible, the potatoes were bland, and the coffee wasn’t great.

All in all, the lesson learned from this would be to pay more attention to your customers, specially when an allergen is mentioned, and apologize for any mistakes made instead of making it a big deal.

Would think twice about coming back to this particular DeDutch. 😕","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"N nova","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKVwkmAucI_zKw-myeb5xINxQiGjdUygLuG8oftGwvM-DLxuQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"The pancake (pancake comes with sausage, bacon, eggs, ham, and hash browns). One of the hams had an unusual taste, which unfortunately caused me an upset stomach. This was the only food I consumed for the entire day, and it caused diarrhea. Furthermore, the staff did not give us enough attention, as no one came to inquire about our meal and our coffee remained empty for an extended period. Despite these issues, I decided to leave a 15% tip, primarily due to the friendly and cheerful service provided by the lady in the red shirt who brought us our food.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNgINrVjPus7X2E5FDloeNKBJfACcjf_BcP1snX&fid=0x0:0xd538504bf0fe9fa1"],"When":"2023-11-12"},{"Name":"Catherine Anderson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWgu5jEuZoVvk541rDr20mH2M4gfzorSifSjd-rvRVfpaOGQCCvSg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I highly recommend this brunch spot to anyone looking for good quality food and service. My husband and I tried their classic sweet pannenkoekens today and they were very delicious. Our server Emma was amazing and the restaurant was very clean and welcoming.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jaded Rose","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVHRIJdkHY4xpStGqD0EzePZPrJnnN_cctFK8DxFwk-yX2c4ktu=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Went their for a birthday breakfast and first the coffee was cold, but the waitress returned with warm coffee quickly. The food was also cold and they suggested to remake it or warm it up. So we opted to warm it up and it was okay after that. Thats the reason for 3 stars.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMgXWofuLQKH9ZzJgAVFIduSONPOvlBnJwoF_y9&fid=0x0:0xd538504bf0fe9fa1"],"When":"2020-10-1"}]

The order was wrong, the sandwich was dry and flavourless, only had a tomato on one half, and the chips were soggy from their own grease and tasted like burnt cardboard.

Costing nearly $50 for 2 sandwiches. Overpriced garbage.

Overall, easily the worst food I’ve ever order on skip.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jeremy Vlogs","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUtkRCeAomQUd4-Oagu20SBeNF_BubC1-sWtXvE5AUGfVIsovI=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"In the 5 years that I have ordered SkipTheDishes, I have never once left a review about a restaurant. This restaurant deserves the input. The almost $50 order consisted of two small, soggy sandwiches; salt must be the secret ingredient because it drowned out any flavour that was there. For the price of $50 we didn’t even receive our side dish. . .chips. I’m content even if a restaurant forgets something or it doesn’t taste as good as I was hoping, but this was just a mistake. I feel embarrassed to tell the person who gifted me this SkipTheDishes coupon that I spent the grand total of $50 on two sandwiches that were soaking in their on grease, minus the chips that were expected. If I can leave a negative review (even after reading the reviews before ordering, with my hopes still held high) then let this be a sign that this is not at all a place to consume a meal that will leave you feeling satisfied. Extremely disappointed and glad I can put this whole experience behind me.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Alyssa Hunt","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIZLKvqqhnnqhvoi8LwiW9c3MZGOgQ4DdKYaE9lUZslCYxDduQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Order the pulled pork sandwich from here once and it was amazing and so delicious that I decided to order it again. The second time it came completely made wrong. Menu says jalapeños, coleslaw, and pulled pork….. but it came with pulled pork and pickles??? It was awful without the coleslaw and it wasn’t even hot either. Awful","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lynn Marois","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWYaClGT0H9hgzmu0XjjOpds59tZjK55ZEO3YNsCZWloToNkW3HLA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Ordered the Phylly Cheesesteak and received a dry nasty pulled pork. I went back and read the reviews and came to understand that this is far more common than not.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Martin Matahari","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUAn1gLSlBMeGXZBHUnKkSJRx9LUQmHP9VKEpiPVA6PU8EOwPbl=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Why oh why didn’t I read the reviews first before ordering. For $17 (before tax, delivery surcharge, tip etc) all I got was lousy soggy baguette with a limp piece of lettuce and miserable quantities of protein. The bacon had the consistency of plastic. To make matters worse it was ice cold. Please learn from my mistake and don’t order from here ever.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Johnny Silaphet","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUpL3l0oqBv2Alp7e9nzKsmNW67463F8ldTol-HD-nw9MhvUVQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Sandwich cold and dry Philly steak and I am missing my chips. user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Maria Fernanda Guaraná","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU949zWMPKzgd78YIgipV_4PUI5bJb069xY2JNqEIjY4HsjgWnfzQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Recently moved to Pitt Meadows and came across this restaurant online when looking for sushi restaurants nearby. Was very surprised by the food and prices. Me and my boyfriend had dinner there last Friday and the food was DELICIOUS, service was very fast and the atmosphere of a historic house gave us the idea of traditional homemade food which we loved! Their prices are very reasonable! I definitely recommend this place for anyone who love sushi!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNgc1jLdml4fIms8UicIA5u2MTjALS3l6HgCSJw&fid=0x0:0x129aa69be65c7000"],"When":"2024-10-30"},{"Name":"Muh Ruri","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUkStAcVhSLoWZluIOVQ74c2fLDnRh9SyZ_LHSDWUY1b4U3yJnx=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Akasaka in Pitt Meadows offers a delightful Japanese dining experience where presentation and ambiance truly stand out. The restaurant is located in a small, cozy house with a fireplace, providing a very friendly and homely atmosphere. With only 4 to 5 tables, it feels intimate and personal, almost as if you're dining in someone's home. It's assumed that the top floor is residential, which adds to the unique charm of the place.

The presentation of the dishes at Akasaka is nothing short of impressive. Each plate is a work of art, meticulously arranged to please both the eyes and the palate. The vibrant colors and thoughtful garnishes enhance the overall dining experience, making each dish as visually appealing as it is delicious.

The quality of the food at Akasaka matches the high standards set by the restaurant’s ambiance and presentation. The flavors are authentic and fresh, providing a true taste of Japan. However, it’s worth noting that the pricing here is relatively high compared to its contemporaries. Despite this, they do offer a decent lunch special, which provides good value and allows diners to enjoy their exquisite cuisine at a more affordable price.

For those in Pitt Meadows looking for a restaurant that offers great food in a beautiful and cozy setting, Akasaka is the perfect choice. The combination of excellent presentation, a wonderful vibe, and the option of a well-priced lunch special makes it a standout destination for Japanese cuisine","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMAOJQqUztjjNjL7b9XVFYCbwwu28UD6YyzeTT6&fid=0x0:0x129aa69be65c7000"],"When":"2024-5-28"},{"Name":"wah chi yip","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKKBykHMUbkrtJ4cwRRXsjOnAzAcOzwrpq-XVjovUt6A3trFQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A really good atmosphere restaurant.  If you dine in this restaurant, you do feel you are dine at home. The decor of this house is an old farm house.
This house is nice in and out. The service are warmly and friendly.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM8EWLrhqQs2ewZT_xX3e7Y2UrVc4Nzz2mzA9fq&fid=0x0:0x129aa69be65c7000"],"When":"2024-7-15"},{"Name":"Nova Ember","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocInptqH07SvjBDYreZDili7yUF4N5-8pTdYburZcf75y3-E4w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"First time dined in this restaurant. We were the only customers there but the service was slow. We didn’t get water until we placed the order( it seems like they were waiting us to order before serving us anything)
The portion was surprisingly small for a Chicken Breast Teriyaki $24.95, and we didn't get the ice cream. Nothing stands out for us to return to this restaurant.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNWgrt0P3b7Tui0SaNgydWB4ZgoR_DKRpHcw_pO&fid=0x0:0x129aa69be65c7000"],"When":"2024-12-2"},{"Name":"Radical Reviews","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWzxgdzIIKP9vqAYzRsir8K2Nid_X0M2c-rfedCHEHaELHzk40=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great sushi and always fresh!! I really like this place. I’ve never actually eaten inside but my wife and I get take out quite often. Their food is really consistent so you always know what you’re going to get. It’s a little bit on the pricey side but I’d rather pay a bit extra and get good quality. It’s about a 10min drive for me and I go past about 6 other sushi places on the way so that tells you it’s worth it. In the photos is a dinner box D, wild sockeye sashimi and salmon avocado roll with cucumber which came to a grand total of $57 after tax.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMC0nbZ-QR7sRuGMnKxalBiSC_PxBKIPvCQ98Lt&fid=0x0:0x129aa69be65c7000"],"When":"2023-1-14"},{"Name":"G W","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVG1FFo9GTnRGQNpjln74dhjBn3V4nGRQE_Yjur_OV6HYJsv04F_g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Nice simple decor, matching Heritage Home.  The food was nicely presented. Pieces are a bit thin. Tempura was Perfect! The sauce was really nice too. I would recommend you take some time to do a good deep House Cleaning.  Your windows are filthy, some half Christmas star pieces stuck still on the glass. Check your pictures and dust control. Or I would have given you a 5. I recommend people try it. Perfect for a quiet date.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"J ason","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLK8lS8cjzF3ZgjIcZyXI7ooB5w1ArRePHhAcera0e4BMQGng=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Super cool old house, great food and service highly reccomend","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNudU9k3Gfsg5qJdVn7xZqAIrgUo36V69zHgMgc&fid=0x0:0x129aa69be65c7000"],"When":"2024-7-27"},{"Name":"Kat","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW9KU6JHMNV2dJVHVeBb2rvEzltNXWG-yaPrGGgPwOBW0ejMgGu=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Definitely the go-to for my entire family for sushi in Pitt. Service is great and the surroundings are interesting to look at. I can say that I've never been disappointed eating here so yeah, I'm repping the homies.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMNc0olQehEexSbrSywuqPbQ0_1P19oYK7USkUg&fid=0x0:0x129aa69be65c7000"],"When":"2018-9-1"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Barendina Smith","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU4gAXNw7bsOWNo-qAPQuFfFYX-uW_wVZHByRe8lPzJaAZZQQG6pQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Well I'd like to address prices. It's getting out of control how expensive it's becoming to go put to eat, & have a treat, not just just at Dairy Queen!

A mini blizzard, which is by the way micro mini size of inside of small palm is $6 & almost $7.5 for small, which is still very small. Photos are added so u can get a price example. It's just getting out of hand.

Although this location is 1st location I've been to in a while that's listened to me asking for extra pickles, there was little condiments on our burgers, which made them dry. I had to ask for more mustard & used ketchup packages.

Now let's move on to the Blizzard. This is what was most disappointing. $6 for this little tiny thing & she didn't hang it upside down when she brought it to me (I didn't know they were supposed to do) cuz I've never purchased blizzard before.  After she gave to me I walked to car & picked up spoon & was like wait a minute, this is milkshake texture so I went back inside asking her & her response "When I gave it to u it was thick"

I'm pretty sure that only took maybe 3 min from time she gave it to me till time I walk back in with it. Hardly not enough time for it to go from blizzard thickness to liquid that was running off spoon. I asked her to remake it, she was not very happy about that. The 2nd one she gave me was better, not thick, but better...at least it didn't fall out of cup when she hung it upside down 2nd time LOL

I got the new flavor Oreo chocolate brownie & it did not taste like chocolate at all, there was no brownies in it at all. Maybe it was just this location, I don't know. Wasn't very happy with it at all.

Moving along to cakes.... wow wow wow. Inflation sure has shown in the prices of these ice cream cakes. Almost $60 for most of them with tax,  gross!!

Stick with the value meal that includes a 🍨 much better buck","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPHbvEsyOjl7xT-tYl9diDKmB1rykUbXMgfTjTz&fid=0x0:0xe9d93214f425f79a"],"When":"2023-8-14"},{"Name":"Adolfo Garcia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXk76S2kbhMbdiRSvTJO85jQ-iHosG75dMnnm-bv3ncX6tkFuc=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Unacceptable Customer Service

I had an extremely disappointing experience with this Dairy Queen location. Due to a glitch in the DQ app, my orders were mistakenly sent to this store instead of my default location. When I realized the mistake, I contacted the store to resolve the issue and requested a refund for the unclaimed orders. Despite being reassured multiple times by Dairy Queen’s corporate team that the franchise owner was contacted, I have yet to hear back from them after three follow-ups over nearly three weeks.

I strongly recommend caution if you choose to order online from this store, as they appear unwilling to assist or resolve customer issues. Don’t say you were not warned!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPQbGzoFomJ7Ulq4-MtAr_xQmCjiYmNrAiS9sxo&fid=0x0:0xe9d93214f425f79a"],"When":"2024-11-28"},{"Name":"Scarlett Girl","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIR2nrPTmLtOAwVlMAEXvQQ3zVqd8VJ-NS2NBUuOPC1WrxNnw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"If I could leave 0 stars I would.  Pulled through the drive thru last night and ordered the same exact meal I always order at any other dairy queen.  The chicken strip meal deal.  And asked to upgrade the dessert to a snack size blizzard.  Normally this meal is 13 dollars anywhere else. So I was shocked to hear 18 dollars when I got to the window.  I said um no... I always order this exact same meal and it's 13 dollars with the upgrade.  The staff said oh we don't do that you have to pay for the blizzard separately.  I said you're the only dairy queen around that does this... you can cancel that whole order then.  I then proceeded to the other dairy queen in town and low and behold I only paid 13 dollars.... management really needs to train their staff better.  Not to mention they are insanely slow at food preparation I had to wait 15 minutes for two cars infront of me to get their food.  Seems excessively slow for "fast" food.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sister Carmen Herrera","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUPRWAIjWri-AtghrtLshw0FpoIF6m4cG0RmjFzKebqCTsETIc=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Very disappointed.  The staff told me it was ok to eat the pineapple on my banana split even though it tasted fermented.  He reassured me it was a fresh batch of pineapple that just arrived and that it was meant to taste a bit sour.  I was sick later because of it.  The worst part is that it was my birthday and I was looking forward to a treat. Bad customer service or at least poorly trained staff. Will not eat there again.  The salads also leave a lot to be desired. Wendy’s salads are better for about the same price or less. Disappointed.
Recently at my local Dairy Queen in poco I asked if whether the pineapple is supposed to taste fermented and they said no. They even gave me a sample.  It was sweet and didn’t make my tongue tingle nor was it fizzy like it was releasing gasses nor anything like the one I had in Maple Ridge the previous week.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Elizabeth Hamming","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVXF7zvrQBkhho5z2JaufXuwtctcjmHV3IQU5eLESqsRmXktAY=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Got more like a milkshake than McFlurry. They remade it for me… the exact same way/milkshake consistency. This is a pic 2 mins after I got it.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPwkH51v3UbPt0AnCaFseZGgiSCIT7nubCKTSmH&fid=0x0:0xe9d93214f425f79a"],"When":"2024-6-23"},{"Name":"Manpreet","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJLZ8pTdnPBbG-WNZ73ySzFycC-YyHoY4RJzCBa0-HkPh53W1E=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Just got my poutine from this place 30 minutes back. Looks like they barely put gravy in it. Its so dry and all the cheese is in middle. There was 3 girls they were so busy in taking. It could be a understandable if there was a big lineup of customers. No one was in the store neither on a drive thru. Very poor customer service and presentation.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO4t1oDfOsmF2ez39JbXCbLJvfLu9jNIfRdD_Nu&fid=0x0:0xe9d93214f425f79a"],"When":"2022-10-15"},{"Name":"Ashley T","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJMgfJ5BeDkQBH8GDtey-vspO4L3doO-eFOQV3K5TUrfzOefg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Placed an order and it came to $30. Gave the guy $40 and he gave me a nickel back and left. Lol. I was dumb enough to stand there in shock for a minute before he left, but once it sunk in I tried to get his attention and was ignored. It’s possible that he was just confused, and then once he left he couldn’t hear me, but now that I’m reading these reviews I honestly don’t buy it. It seems like there’s something sketchy and off about this particular DQ.

Of course I could be wrong, and maybe it’s just that they hire people with special needs, which would actually be pretty cool. However, if that’s the case, there should still be a minimum requirement that the cashier be able to do grade 1 level math.

Word of warning to those who go here: double check your change! Better yet, don’t even go here. I know personally, I won’t be back, and hey, both my wallet and my waistline will only thank me for it.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Doris Escaravage","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUO3Yqt2t_lz040wu2YKnWfTpYtwu7zd3tuAMWCuwkfdyhDXC4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Went there with my grandkids. Of course they loved it, they love ice cream! Service was quick, and tables and washrooms were clean.","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Brittany","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJs_km6RslliP6cTTiQcv7eI3BYv9_LkkJf-8xS0POhDRp70O4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Came to this part of city by fluke, and tried this place without looking at reviews during a power outage! And boy! I am glad the day brought us to this gem 💎.  Ordered 2 large bowls of pho… very generous in overall size, including amount of noodles and meat! The soup was proper rich and real broth and just so delicious. So good we had to pack the last bit home, didn’t want to waste a single drop!
We also ordered the wings and chicken fried spring rolls (awesome they had non-pork option!). Wings were more so on the plain side but came with a dipping sauce and the chicken spring rolls were wonderful… tasted almost like the traditional ones, just with chicken!
Will be coming back!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNbIdOdS-NTfeTCpJ1WuFDeTYskcVTpu-Uyn-89&fid=0x0:0xa9da2966b717cf3c"],"When":"2024-12-17"},{"Name":"M Lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIsGv955Ri875E7vGmsYaHqa37baEVpl4eh0b_zeRaT_a88ew=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Edited to add photos. Note the photo is of a half order of spring roll—our first time we got the full and it was huge! Also it is a family owned business and the owner works so hard to serve everyone. Huge kudos

First time dining here tonight, and we will be back! We showed up at 8pm, and were surprised no other diners wanted hot soup on a hot day lol. We got the owner’s attention, and he promptly served us. We had the spring rolls, house special pho, and bun bo hue. The servings were huge! The food was perfectly cooked, and tasty. No msg thirst after. Highly recommend this place. Very affordable too at around $45 with tax and tip.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNK8ahYJ7qm-WpHuqxi04-8R5DASA38emLnepV9&fid=0x0:0xa9da2966b717cf3c"],"When":"2024-7-6"},{"Name":"Joanne Antoniak","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWTQwhPcO13h_HhVjJVUrwpHjU5MeesKhPrxV5pA1ymdZ1edFkY=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"First time visit today.
Ordered 2 pho and salad roll and spring roll.  Food was awesome.
Service was fantastic and decor wasn't bad.  Bowls were full of goodness and not loaded with just broth.  We will definitely go back

Return visit sept 2024.  Still good 😋","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPM-_ptKvmUxYbFqEEW2y_a1Igqh30HpMtpjDka&fid=0x0:0xa9da2966b717cf3c"],"When":"2024-6-28"},{"Name":"Lu Luna","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUcA7O0ZqYEsTqIe6QegqGUkLuq5mtLY_tuXczfLzKLPx0-XgVc=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The first time I dined at this restaurant was in 2014, and the flavor of their dishes has stayed with me ever since. Whenever I lived in Maple Ridge, I would always make it a point to visit. It has been such a long time, but today I decided to revisit the restaurant and indulge in their No.40 chicken fried vegetables rice once again. To my delight, it was still as delicious as I remembered, and the owner was just as kind and friendly as before. He even recognized us and greeted us warmly. I felt deeply moved by this experience, as food has a way of evoking memories and reflecting upon the passage of time.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPEjeC_ndUXzrVDBxgumIMLdJsUlpuNd3rWnrcK&fid=0x0:0xa9da2966b717cf3c"],"When":"2023-6-11"},{"Name":"Graham M","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWvXIcy2m-zrzQEvJPym8fBbkJUAJI8a_9vJ1dkEsVKsIxPb-U=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is some of the richest pho broth I've ever had. I have never been this full from a bowl of pho. Very nice, clean taste.

The brisket is legit, thick chunks of tender beef. Very good.

Please note this pho is lightly salted. I actually had to add salt. I've never needed to with pho before, but this seems like another advantage about the soup here.

The pork spring rolls are beautiful.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Wendy Wall","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKO-pUKK3oknGa9yeAnQSN3wiqb2kAy9hEtIRRgjz_61bzgEA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Smelled good when I walked in restaurant. Always a good indicator for me. First time here with friends. Really really good pho. I just had the veggie pho with chicken soup base with  rice noodles. Ate all the veggies but couldn't finish all the noodles. So filling and huge helping. Great Vietnamese coffee and best tasting spring rolls I've ever had. Will definitely be returning and bringing friends. Unassuming little place in the corner of a small retail area. Well worth a try.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jack Pajak","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV7kRSq5QM1wGXm36_dbE9YR6CpcUs9VUAhu1SxvpJkrQ-nGO0N=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Went for dinner with the family. I had a pork banh mi and a small pho (rare beef and beef balls). Wife and kids shared some appies and the pork on rice. My banh mi was very tasty, crunchy but soft bun with delicious tender pork and fresh veggies. The pho was the best I've ever tasted. The broth was spectacularly flavorful and the meats were equally as tasty. My wife and kids really enjoyed their meals as well, particularly the salar rolls. The owner is also a very friendly and nice man who is very attentive of his customers. We will definitely be back, the wife and kids are already planning on what to order next!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN-OY7S5N02plFO00qWtWF1P6Lf9B7sed5TiucA&fid=0x0:0xa9da2966b717cf3c"],"When":"2022-4-23"},{"Name":"Chunfang Huang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJmjTHBdo-AGkcGIh-YmihUY3OM9lB-8c7khtHpqH863RpDqA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"delicious food. Especially bun bo hu beef noodle soup. The size is so big even you ordered small size. The owner is very nice and gentle.","Images":null,"When":""}]

I found out later that you can order online for pickup in store, too! Looking good Chopped Leaf Maple Ridge!! Thanks for a great lunch :D (I had bowl 3 (greek) and the mango iced tea - yumm! My recommendation, try somewhere else.
Chopped leaf is good but not this store","Images":null,"When":""}]

The pan veggie was good. But the handcrafted pepperoni was not!  Too bad because we were so looking forward to it.

Young lady was very pleasant. When I finally got food, it was good n hot","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Warren King","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUhEYUtjiaHqTPCDxqH6xHBeSpgYOQ6lTsEzWD4fFDTnz_NKAMZ3w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Ordered for the second time in a while (their new crust was good last time so tried again).  Pizza got delivered and was terrible, the peperoni was have just bread, no toppings!  Called for 30 mins before someone finally answered, they finally agreed to deliver a replacement.  The guy just dropped it off at the door an we didn't know it was there.  Last time ordering here, don't do it!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Carl - Pinnacle","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJX-l3Zg4ENLvaQ2BkXSSePno8LlJ2gNfHqPUFB4ZEpqTOi6A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Everytime an online order is placed, the ordering system either fails or you spend 30+ mins trying to get transferred to the store, they never answer the phone at the store and always divert to the main call centre. Constantly things are forgotten from orders and rarely show up correct. Hands down the worst Pizza Hut location in all of BC and that’s saying something.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Manthan kaushal","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVreUKKbyBuL1rDd3rHCEU5fDRo7eKuUo_XTKDp9VeX_MheiuuA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"To this particular pizza hut's management. Ordered a pizza today at 9 and got a confirmation that it will be delivered in 30, cool!. Called your customer service rep after an hour+ wait and even they got embarrassed coz they were unable to connect me to your store to ask what's goin on?. Went to your store and it was closed before your actual closing time. Took the mentioned pic at 10:30 PM. Check your staff. Worst experience.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNXoJS3Qu3dyN7d2SP5sWMZh9vD0cX_oFDrNBrW&fid=0x0:0xa37b1ccd45646da5"],"When":"2021-8-17"},{"Name":"Mario Figueroa","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJgyVpZ-MEyPnVPYI2HzYRQ9qtKaunlIOUGDz3B-UIJlQfPgg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I'm surprised pizza hut hasn't disappeared yet all of their bigger eat in restaurants are gone though cuz business isn't that good anymore. Chicken seasar medium pizza is $28 after taxes are you kidding me??? They use cheap ingredients nowadays they forget the competition out there is plenty and abundant pizza hut is a rip off I DO NOT RECOMMEND THIS GREEDY PIZZA PLACE stay away there's way better deals out there my family and I are done with pizza hut they're out to gauge the customer every time you walk in their pizzas have increased in price they're roothless do they think people get wage raises every month????","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jaspreet Sidhu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKMn9Y7OgyTHCI0dvowhzMfvajkjJ5D-MZ1SWwg-z4_cxSqrQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Worst customer service ever they never pick the phone we tried 4-5 times sitting in the front of their store they was busy with gossiping each other nobody pick up the ph the guy name emiuel was very rude","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Aaron Scott","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXn-lvwTGMhUxCV421M_xqu_u5MrGrT6chcjNAjFFyrJKuOzGho5Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"There is one delivery guy here that does a great job. But the rest of them are incredibly inept.

One guy who has been to my building MULTIPLE times still can’t operate the buzzer. Another can’t seem to figure out how to open the door when the thing buzzes. They barely speak, and have no customer service skills.

Today the guy brings me pizza and his debit machine battery is so low that the machine won’t process the payment. So he leaves and days he’ll be right back to collect payment. He has to go get a new machine. Two hours later I had to call the store to find out what’s happening. I can’t wait all night for a guy who can’t figure out how to do the basics of delivering pizza to decide to come back to get the money.

The person who answers the phone hands it to the delivery guy who gets on the phone AND DOESN’T TALK. After about 30 seconds he says, “I’m the delivery guy”. I asked him when he was coming back because I can’t sit here and wait all night, and he said “oh, I’ll come right now.” HE WASN’T EVEN PLANNING ON COMING AT THAT TIME! He totally did not care how long I was waiting for him. Like a complete narcissist, he just figured he’d show up sometime before midnight when he felt like it?!!!! I mean seriously. I told him if he wasn’t here in 30 min he could forget about it because I won’t be home.

So now he says he’s on his way.

I then talked to the manager. I told him what happened and he couldn’t even manage a simple conversation. He barely said a word and had no idea what to do or what to say. And that’s when I realized this Pizza Hut is staffed by the people who can’t hold a job anywhere else and that no one from management down cares about anything at all. They’re just insipid space fillers… if I owned this Pizza Hut I would close it down because clearly the owner also doesn’t care about his business.

One competent delivery guy. I order from here once a week and the only thing that’s more frustrating than their garbage service is the fact I have kept doing business with them for the past year+.

No more. That’s the last time.","Images":null,"When":""}]

The chef, Raju, prepared some of the best dishes I’ve had in a while. The flavors were fresh, perfectly balanced, and everything was cooked to perfection. You can really tell the passion and skill that goes into the food here.

I got the burrito bowl with chicken and guacamole and it is delicious. my wife got the garlic chili chicken which she thought was great. I really hope this place stays around because the fresh ingredients at the affordable price make eating healthy very easy.. parking is great when we went at dinner time. overall it was really good and we'll be coming back again.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Saar Dvir","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVKXGHkbuG2Ma3DU2io3X6uWQ0amHvz1IG2QLFeWhSBm-ndm9VYnQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Had the Mexican bowl.
The beef portion was too small. The meat was chewy. The vegetables portion was very small as well. The Guacamole was only a small tea spoon. The food had no flavor.  And just to put things in perspective: 90% of the bowl consisted of white rice. Flavorless.
Big disappointment.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Deepu Raj","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWj47A1-Z5jXIbT5XRjMaWmxYzLzzY3xYnQpm4Ik-G_M4cwdgRDcw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"New addition to Pitt Meadows airport area. The food taste and quality is very good .","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMMl9IvQh0K3AeGOSLHmjutXmy12JjRmiVM6LFj&fid=0x0:0xddad2273cf242f75"],"When":"2024-8-26"},{"Name":"Samantha Garcia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKn4n6HUx6aGkgmuZK23Na9fGd6tB0UD9lumDFqZ1m7SbIT6A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Our first time ordering and unfortunately, our last.

My daughters school had go grill cater a hot lunch and they had a gluten free option for her (she is celiac). She has been talking about it since so we decided to order there tonight as there aren't many local options that will accommodate her.

I spoke to the PAC person and she told me the ginger garlic sauce was gluten free and showed the email from the manager confirming this. I went on the website to order but this sauce doesn't exist in the build your own bowl so I called. During the call, I told the person who answered about our school and gluten free and she confirmed the ginger garlic sauce was the one. I said I would call back with the rest of our order.

Less then 5 minutes later I called back and I said "okay I will get one of those ginger garlic with chicken and rice" then I ordered the rest of our meals. She said ok, it would be ready in 25-30 min. I told her my name and said my husband would be picking up and gave her name. This was not a rushed conversation. She had lots of time to clarify anything.

So my husband went in time to pick it up. He forgot his phone at home. I noticed it was taking super long to come back. When he finally arrived he told me that when he went to pick it up, the lady told him that she knows I wanted gluten free but nothing I ordered was gluten free. He said that was weird but paid anyway and left. He then had to go to a different restaurant to pick up something else for my daughter, spending more money and taking more time.

When he got home and told me, I called back and was told I ordered a different dish. I said if that was the case, and you knew I was ordering gluten free since I just spoke to her and I told them it was me asking about the gluten free, why did she not confirm with me at the moment of ordering instead of waiting for when my husband went to pick up? Even if he had confirmed that was wrong, he would have had to wait for them to remake the dish. It would have made much more sense for everyone if she just confirmed when I ordered instead of not saying anything, especially since I kept saying gluten free. I am not the expert of their menu, they are.

She kept essentially blaming my husband and kept condescendingly saying "I understand" (sounded like this was their training, because it was clear she did not understand). She offered no solutions so I ended the call. She called back and I chose not to answer. In the voicemail, she said she would make it no extra charge and we can go pick it up. But this isn't really a solution since 1. We already paid for the one they made that wasn't gluten free 2. I already spent extra having to get an alternate meal for her 3. It would have taken even more of my time to wait for it to be made and then drive back. Personally, I think they should have offered a refund or a coupon for the cost of the meal at the very be least.

As for the meal we got, those of us could eat it felt it was all just okay. Good value for money. It's a big serving. Had the customer service been good we would have tried again as it is good value for money.

Bad customer service combined with just okay food means we won't be repeat customers.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Erik Ostensen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKQpXi3wqlUgDP12KMcq1OauP6eTj3rkSzpWb3LA9l6F_pUCw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I work in the area and go here for lunch very often. Always fresh, perfectly cooked, and personable service. I also like you remember my order every time =)
Thanks for providing a healthy option for the area.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Christina Gomes","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVR0XeP1ln2r2NSQUZ5Wk5de1kur7NBvUAAq1X4kd3xnYnf6IY=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Go Grill is a fantastic spot for delicious and customizable food options. Their menu offers a wide variety of fresh ingredients that you can mix and match to create your perfect meal. The concept of choosing your own ingredients and watching your meal being prepared adds a fun and interactive element to the dining experience. The flavors are bold, and the portions are generous, making it a great choice for a satisfying meal. Overall, Go Grill is a must-try for those looking for a tasty and customizable dining experience.","Images":null,"When":""}]

I hope someone contacts me.

We order from here quite often, and usually the food is okay, but today was awful. I placed my order online, when I got there the young guy working ignored me until his coworker arrived, then told me he would be a minute. I got my pepperoni deep dish pizza and brought it home.

When we started eating it, it tasted funny and had weird texture. I pulled the toppings off and the dough was only half cooked. It was so under cooked the dough was stringy just under the toppings. By then it was too late to drive back into town and complain in person. So I sent in feedback online and decided to post here. Make sure to check to see if your pizza is cooked before you leave.

Hopefully we don't get food poisoning from eating uncooked dough. I do hope the owner contacts me as we spent 30$ there and this is not okay.

The cheese and toppings are removed from the photos. That is a layer of undercooked dough on top of cooked dough. 😭🤢","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPjZgkSeMSWQ3-tIr9Yeu2UeRQA9AwNPLGMQyIv&fid=0x0:0x17a69f59f0f7702e"],"When":"2023-9-25"},{"Name":"Rob Pottinger","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLqFUbWPrHlfqnEteD4oYDQjOQGCZg8MoFsI1ACR8G-m4fcmw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Absolutely terrible. [{"Name":"Kwan Fu Sit","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXxITaxZ3hn037Zh1z9TQmbQPt6WsiezaGcj9Pv2Zl7Dcs1bGxF=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Ordered a baconator combo and when the clerk gave me the burger she mumbled double baconator and I asked her, is that my baconator and she said yes.

When i get home to my surprise it's not even a baconator, just a single!  What the hell?  Would not recommend this location.  Been here a few times and each time it was bad","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOof5cTxkshb6qIPVdoZAZ8efKHGiQcekECeMl4&fid=0x0:0xf6a9f673239af39d"],"When":"2024-9-6"},{"Name":"Fredrick Zoller","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL01F2QlXvuCUnZwPCtofa0r29cQHvBmtrY6v5OjsG39ImLPw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I ate in the restaurant for breakfast. It wasnt busy, and all of the booths were empty but were dirty, with old trays and food. No staff came out to clean them for the half hour I was there.

The food was fresh and tasted really good. The breakfast potatoes and the breakfast baconator were both really good.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPAFT6y48pcfAer14NSNmR5XZdsnGlI7qjfvKWu&fid=0x0:0xf6a9f673239af39d"],"When":"2023-10-31"},{"Name":"Kenneth Wourms","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUyjwJ5PmMoIXgzWyq3YmiyqVwetAcqPoCHNAiHiV85lckagnxj=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"This is the fourth time in a row that they didn't give us spoons for our frosties. Do they think we're drinking them through that little hole in the lid? They do realize these are a frozen drink, right?? Or are they convinced that EVERYONE just buys them to dip their fries?","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"jackie spears","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWQSpIRsoeLZKzPhRjMQrTuHhWXI2eeJUv_G6fSe8jGwzpSrvc=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Ordered delivery from Uber eats from here a few days ago. Got the Spongebob collab burger, pineapple frosty ,chicken nuggets and cinnabits.
Only to have my delivery sent to me and my burger was cold and mushy and gross. I did not receive my cinnabites and I received two chicken nuggets in the pack. My frosty looked like it was half eaten just like my 6 piece nuggets obviously were and I guess they just forgot to give me the cinnabits. I did report this discrepancy to Uber eats to be faced with not eligible for refund (even though I sent pictures of my order and what was missing) nope they didn't care! So I've taken to google for my review of this location! I want my money back Wendy's I'm not paying for your staff to eat my food! So despicable. Will not ever be ordering from this establishment ever again! Stay clear of this place 😞","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Daniel Gerlach","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKrEvt8WPP6iriDpH0OkxJmJYGPkDnaeurZUiT5zf5D4GtWug=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Food is usually pretty good. I've had missing items from my drive through order. Also don't come here when they are busy. They seem short staffed. I've waited 30min to order and receive my food before. Like most fast food places they prioritize skip and uber and drive through and leave the customer who come inside feeling forgotten about. Hire more staff if you can't keep up.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN4lHp1xaS9fuDL8ehRwtF1BG_sk7DTce36yt19&fid=0x0:0xf6a9f673239af39d"],"When":"2022-2-24"},{"Name":"Luke Sweet","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV9QeFiL7Y_5vgEXhwPtQROLfzuFoGuUMMTWJA3gL_TYNU4OALy=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Super unprofessional.. I was going through the drive through waited 2 mins for them to say something at the speaker and all I could hear in the background was laughing and messing around while taking my order. After that I pulled up to the window to see them screwing around and laughing while spilling my coffee all over my cup and then proceeded to hand me a wet straw.. and yes they’re cardboard straws so I got a soggy straw and a coffee which was also spilled all over the cup. Super disappointed won’t be going back again anytime soon.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Heather Ulrich","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWD6f9LeJuwM9yA12l9039u49wt8-HhJCcGbAHaOypdE6Pofbaq=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I ordered a large chili with cheese, no cheese,
I ordered a large fry well don, they were soggy and cold.
I ordered spicy nuggets, got regular ones
Ordered a Dave’s double with heavy pickle and mayo. No heavy pickle or mayo and it’s cold.
Also no straw for my lemonade.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Michelle Hillock","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJrzRoOQIhVr_Azv33mg4FgqnXjS5clP8SiddvR3MVEWC9e9w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Hot and fresh and does customized orders with perfection. They are so fast. Amazingly fresh and juicy. They don't use old stuff. I saw a woman manager leading the team.

Thanks! Please keep up the good work!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNSNAC5XGHJfC5BHKoGZjuFeEb92JoAj6X5MDCp&fid=0x0:0xf6a9f673239af39d"],"When":"2022-7-28"}]
