user_reviews:
[{"Name":"saran samy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocId3tLOAv75Dn1v7FhYDfK0ZjoMAHpnlb_HoxyOl4wRaK0o=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We ordered Seeraga sambha mutton briyani combo and Basmati rice mutton briyani comb. We also ordered Pepper Chicken once and Beef roast on another time recently. They both tasted very authentic.

both the times, the Briyani was very tasty (both steeraga sambha briyani and Basmati Mutton briyani ). The portion was large and more than 4 persons can easily eat even though the menu says “serves 4 people”.

The combo comes with complementary Chicken 65, Raita and 1 portion of sweet.

They deliver 20 kms from Maple Ridge and the delivery was very prompt both the times.

We need to order at least 1 day ahead.

What I liked the most is they contact you for your feedback to improve and cater your needs in future.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMUvHYkhSCXb76D_gW__iRgl1CaXwRf6dpKbcc&fid=0x0:0x4950d3f5c462a9e"],"When":"2024-9-16"},{"Name":"Siva Mani","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVryG20BiVgNr6YbAAWMmr-eBPc2fNxP2cBUoelmhV8_Y7FcJogTA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I recently tried their food with my friends and ordered the Seeraga Samba Mutton Biryani combo, Chicken 65, and Pepper Chicken. The biryani was authentic and tasty, bringing back memories of my hometown Bhai Veetu Biryani. The sides were also delicious, and everyone enjoyed the food thoroughly. The fact that its homemade adds a special touch to the overall experience. We're planning to make this a recurring monthly order. My only suggestion would be to improve the portion size of the sides considering the price. Otherwise, everything was top-notch!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO2DFBsT5v6v6g1IdpZJyZPYCUQrYS4M_skw5wH&fid=0x0:0x4950d3f5c462a9e"],"When":"2024-6-30"},{"Name":"Jayaprabha Jayaraman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIlz-U-bxoz1UhJPSpoj7hjMUDR9nfJcWjnNYe7HZ6e2uOi5g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I got briyanu from Meer. Biryani is super tasty! It's like a flavor explosion of rice and yummy spices. It's a must-try for anyone who loves good food! 👍  it soo good with homemade taste . Chicken 65 is ultimate with its flavor and crispyness. My kids loved it. !","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOT6_VdqUzF_So4RrM41MvPf1RzUQA4FzLXUx-D&fid=0x0:0x4950d3f5c462a9e"],"When":"2024-4-27"},{"Name":"Subash C Canapathy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVce9rG62-EB5iwG8OOMDTLiCCMbhslo1gEwvh1irx-WsRi7fWMzg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Home made biryani with a fantastic flavour profile, properly fluffy and light like how a dum biryani should be. Can confidently say this is the hyderabadi biryani to beat for the maple ridge / pitt meadows area and I would rate it right up there with other known top biryani places in lower mainland with the added advantage of non greasy home made goodness.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ali Mansoor S","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX8_10jbBrTlilf1_MYZNAvCIfo4FIUpScZrXkOs71EwBhWfFXr=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Perfect place for anyone with a desire for biryani. Tried Seeraga samba biriyani and it was delicious.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMPZsdEwVE1QnXnTvF_tJMICmwBp9npFyUipbI-&fid=0x0:0x4950d3f5c462a9e"],"When":"2024-10-19"},{"Name":"Liji Varghese","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWRyOds2V82kNIGYrmYa5wVX583Nt3Lpj3nPO_RihjcfEyyPLyW_A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Delicious, authentic food with reliable delivery. Ordered Hyderabadi mutton dum biriyani and fish pakora today, took us 25 years back to India. Reshma accommodated on short notice and customized the spice level which worked out perfectly.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Azhaguvelan Ganesan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKLXxU6DMkXPAQpU7yHH-9meCOtsAyMBg2riCb6f6sR9I9SfA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Really Proved again briyani na Bhai  Kai pakkuvam pola varuma..The smell of briyani on opening itself made it feel great Vibe.
Still has smell in the hand after 2 hrs of eating.
Beef roast is just awesome , kind of pallipalayam Style , but tasty well cooked beef & very tasty semi gravy style.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sneha Philip","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWsk8mBh13uGAY7-s8dhfFkgamv03B7jtwvNC24jplvJ7Rtt655=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I was craving South Indian biriyani and some mutton curry when I saw the ad for Reshma’s Bhai Veetu biriyani in a neighbourhood group post. Even though I was a little late to order, she made piping hot biriyani and her partner delivered it home. The food was awesome and tasty! The quantity was amazing too. They deliver the curries in cute reusable  containers.
Highly recommended Reshma for any South Indian craving home taste !","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Pradyumna Gujjar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXVHYwZPoeWTWb_r-Pj3URXZmwvjMuE8IJLkPSR4xqAVv86CR0HjQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"One of the better coffee spots this part of town.
Live their white chocolate mocha and caramel macchiato.
The crustless quiche was alright but their blueberry almond croissant was delicious l.
Ample seating space and a cozy atmosphere.
The staff are friendly and always greet customers with a warm smile!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM9dRoqL3BsSp9XqSAU7gRN_nD5TgAc5tKMruzM&fid=0x0:0xdb649e8e70848e80"],"When":"2024-11-10"},{"Name":"MJ","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUlm_XRYtoUIMsDe0r0YhYfxDQnj37a3FGprKGl2_zxeQCNP_XX=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Got a white mocha and an iced matcha latte, pretty mediocre - not bad.

The GF Bagel was dry, lacking something while the cheddar and kale scone was also lacking some flavour.

Cute sitting area, new view to look out.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNHJUzRGAyBksruWXWvJPvpMsi63q35C7vJuASE&fid=0x0:0xdb649e8e70848e80"],"When":"2024-10-21"},{"Name":"K H","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVo2hR2qKHBGSuFyVVc1kqvuNnr23GVLd19IdZCsiU8tz8tbtW-=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Good amount of outlets. Tables and chairs weren’t the most comfortable. Really high traffic on warmer days. Only thing was coffee was really not that good, none of us enjoyed it particularly. Prices are high.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMOfU_iw6MKN_VNcprT4qzkhpJDp8qhn7A8ihys&fid=0x0:0xdb649e8e70848e80"],"When":"2024-6-1"},{"Name":"George D","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXqMA7qbYytlO_4Jfi4rlocuHdAGheOdmR3fEbGAbM7yIf_VUe3=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Really good Chai lattes ❤️ just came here with my niece and mom for a coffee but we got a little something something 🫠 to go with our coffee. Highly recommend coming here for sure. If your into coffee and a walk by the  river adjacent to here also a popular thing to do.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipONNpTeljW_1SvY-Hg84WnPOJkwF_nAxc0OGVow&fid=0x0:0xdb649e8e70848e80"],"When":"2023-12-17"},{"Name":"Simon Hardy-Francis","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUB8AdQYxUYJCAE_cHqFT87JPS7eQsmUoL3mGal92dnU64RGEWt=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Dry cappuccino was not dry, nothing really breakfast so ordered the quiche without the salad; price was $6 which seems steep. Nice atmosphere close to the river.

Update July 2017: Got a Cafe Frap but it tasted mostly of milk and not coffee :-(

Update Sept. 2024: 4 people were working in the cage but none were smiling. Nothing looked cleaned  or maintained. Napkin dispenser was almost out. My wife ordered a 20oz coffee and for myself only a 16oz. But we were given two 16oz coffees. Although busy, they told my wife that she was wrong about the size of her coffee. Think this will be our last visit :-(","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN7INVkA9B6nvoTKjGfrHA8WRwuZS5xBIgO8zDZ&fid=0x0:0xdb649e8e70848e80"],"When":"2016-9-18"},{"Name":"Madison G","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVtZsEld-Yz5a2Swm5LesjF83lo03ZXPGgujeQvQiLn6WLaIuGx=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Such a cute place, great location and easy parking. Staff was friendly and the coffee ( Caramel macchiatos) we’re so delicious.
I got a grilled cheese, and my friend got a veggie bagel. The bread tasted very fresh. The building is pretty small so limited seating if it gets busy. But super cute cafe and look. Great experience","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNY98G5lU5qiX10hl6orPxomKrz9EF_g7gpoS-1&fid=0x0:0xdb649e8e70848e80"],"When":"2023-2-28"},{"Name":"Hawraa Rashidi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLnfXqnhjnxiVzwIzqwqkFNU9110Cm2o2ZtxwHhWm_d8FB4WA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"LOVE this cafe! The staff is very attentive, kind and friendly, and the cafe is very cute and doesn’t get loud. The sandwich selection is also very good and all the veggie sandwich options are so tasty. The coffee (I get the Spanish coffee) and pastries are the best I’ve had in all of Vancouver! Usually at cafes pastries are so sweet you can’t taste what you’re eating, but not here! The pastries are the perfect amount of sweetness and there are many to choose from. My favorite is the blueberry almond croissant :)","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Henry Yim","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXyAeUh2CClKb5j6bPCfm4WTuRVeJI0Sj2rgBonFkle79yB2OU=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Im my opinion, this is one of the best neighborhood cafe in the city area. It is quiet yet cozy . The  Club Panini with juicy chicken breast was delicious. My favorite place in Tri-Cities area for hangout on weekends or a sunny afternoon.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNfxZD9wRETihmfUARtoMUNVjOP0bKFUmtU-uAU&fid=0x0:0xdb649e8e70848e80"],"When":"2023-6-8"}]

[{"Name":"Paul Chu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL5lxnU3YfG8x9qJBbP15A_fXhwtTX1HkK0tPiOpx4539Uefw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Tried this place when I first moved to the area and thought it was decent.

This is my second time ordering here.  I ordered a well done pizza, got a undercooked one.    You can tell by the colour of the dough above the base of the pizza.     It was the most floppy pizza I've ever seen.    I'd rather order Domino's, at least it's always cooked.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNpwWEQDU-rXFFvPCiB55GHYGOK1BiFjOQiHdhC&fid=0x0:0x49d7d6291e20e0a"],"When":"2024-7-21"},{"Name":"Tyso","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUe-PMAamIzccUC1PqMGbnx_ywowjHedHr-jT-4dCeppN2zSweu=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Decided to give it a try because I was in the area and dang, their pizza rocks. The ingredients are super high-quality, the crust is delicious and the sesame seeds. Well, every pizza crust should have sesame seeds. A killer deal for a large two topping for 13.99.
Keep up the great work!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOXMGW_bqbNKpuhoM6CALD5oiX9seqYeq6ntrtx&fid=0x0:0x49d7d6291e20e0a"],"When":"2024-10-8"},{"Name":"Arjun Suresh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWEpJoyxT6YA-E54KtAWnbG_xqHyiwWeMNVg-d8SkVDMsUSXZyK=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently visited Red Swan Pizza and it was hands down the best pizza experience I've ever had! The crust is perfectly crispy, the sauce rich and flavorful, and the toppings are fresh.

This exceeded all my expectations. Whether you're a pizza connoisseur or just looking for a great meal, this place is a must-visit. I can't wait to return and try more of their amazing menu. Highly recommended! 👍","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Heather Lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK-FjuL-J5usI3tdhAx0shsC7MZVKxHrBgw_A8y0ONGYLmhjw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Pretty good pizza! Better than any of the big chain restaurants that is for sure!

Lots of toppings and nice amount and flavoured sauce. We ordered 2 gluten free pizzas - it was my first time trying gluten free pizza so I have nothing to compare it too; looked thin but maybe that’s normal?

They were running a bit behind, but I’m guessing it’s just because they just opened. The staff is very polite, and some of their pick up deals are insane. They are also open late which is nice.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNv2M3Hi0AT-zYJtbGpcpIchJUzBFA6lxcGH1qf&fid=0x0:0x49d7d6291e20e0a"],"When":"2023-2-4"},{"Name":"Vimmi Kumar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIAuj0mWs9v0DtwLOyoLGiNRGr_AjmgYpm32RVSrAqlaydz7w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"My first time trying Red Swan. It wasn’t overly impressive. Just mediocre. The toppings especially mushrooms were scarce. Q","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNkqR6YQlkSflOtk9-VMNz3lj9XkGQDbuVCVgCC&fid=0x0:0x49d7d6291e20e0a"],"When":"2024-6-19"},{"Name":"Wheels","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVsz1Rg53Q2-m5JHAwzfaowNSrC2JEVYhO1hHp4iyxB4sDy77VI=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Only have got 1 pizza from this location. Staff are very friendly, there are some tables and chairs inside to sit down and eat. It's definitely a happening vibe with the music, the facilities are new and very clean! The pizza was ok, I got a spicy pierogi, but it's definitely not on the spicy side, tho. I think banana peppers would be a good add to the topings... just my opinion. Will definitely be back to try other pizzas.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN85oGfzEcTJV1ZmuG6fPGiVMy_RlD0Kbs7jG8P&fid=0x0:0x49d7d6291e20e0a"],"When":"2023-2-20"},{"Name":"Joseph Ng","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXk_ILL6lzJT19B32s4QofXWam1Q3xrQ9wM4qN1TEB1_CFfyjY=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I didn't know this pizza place was opened until today. Ordered a personal 8" pizza with Alfredo Chicken Bacon topping (there are 41 choices to pick). It requires 15 - 20 minutes to wait. I lost track of the time but it is not too long and when my pizza arrives, WOW! It is the best in town no doubt. The sesame crust is phenomenal, it is cripsy and tendered, the topping is full, all I can say this pizza is fresh and excellent. I also ordered a regular size wedges. It is very so tasty that the restaurant next door cannot compete. I wish to finish it but the portion of the wedges is big. I am going to try again to see if they are going to maintain the standard. Further, the staff is very courteous and friendly. The interior of the restaurant is clean and tidy.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNkT8z6mV57KWYaPEoh1lMS3JkDEjbEMPrAFExN&fid=0x0:0x49d7d6291e20e0a"],"When":"2023-7-10"},{"Name":"Ashish Sam","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXP1lm96XEfH5oggDIqnPQ0PW8yNitVv1eEAHR2soD7K03hbZs=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Trying second time newly opened restaurant in town! friendly staff and verity of items to choose. ordered tandoori chicken pizza, wings and potato wedges. everything was delicious, wedges cook perfectly with nice seasoning and wings was one of the best that I ever had, with tender and right amount of seasoning. Definitely come back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNGsI5PhjPMmi1ozy65sYbVHV1MEuY9W2qSbRQ&fid=0x0:0x49d7d6291e20e0a"],"When":"2023-1-31"}]

[{"Name":"Annie C","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUiQJYF4_BS-QCtzODpwt_N5rIUplgHFCiJnOSYNTLBW_fQWDG4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Pardeep working close tonight was AMAZING.
He got the long line dealt with QUICKLY and made sure to get all the details right for everyone's order ahead of us.
All I had to say was that I wanted the jerk chicken bowl (he even let me know what came in it!), and he took care of the rest! I didn't have to list off everything I wanted in it, and he omitted the cheese per my request.
Food was phenomenal. Best bowl I've ever had.
Absolutely amazing service from him.
Would absolutely come back in a heartbeat due to his service!
⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️ 5 stars to him alone!
Give that man a raise!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Joanne Antoniak","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWTQwhPcO13h_HhVjJVUrwpHjU5MeesKhPrxV5pA1ymdZ1edFkY=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"First time at this particular subway lougheed highway (203rd).
Eat in area is tiny (maybe 6 tables).
Shop was busy.  Plenty of staff kept the line moving.  Food was good.
Ingredients are fresh and you add what yoy like.
Lobby Area was clean and tidy.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP5Tq-aP6HlzCZEJHzHwiBPXrMv2J12YZYTO8eH&fid=0x0:0x532a8cf0e2066c35"],"When":"2023-5-26"},{"Name":"Sahil Jhamb","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXi61en5o7COh8vP6mtco_YkqCLtcfHpnNfb3x0ncWhE5kxcBzRUw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Online ordering was not working due to some tech issue at location, location denied to use app coupon as they facing some issue, and ask to go to another location ? Is there no way to entertain manually ? Surprised! Then the member said ok I will do this time for you, is it a favor you are offering to customer when there is tech issue ? Will not be going back to location, no rewards to my account as there system failure.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Dave backeland","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVcv64Vs5yBlfxYxoVSibb1CSK_GewvZ_CHwRAGyPnm_H2NUHk=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"My daughter and her co worker both nurses at the local hospital ate here today during their dinner break. My daughters co workers had a steak sub. They had already eaten then noticed the maggots on the wrapper of the steak sub. Do not eat here I will contact the appropriate agency to deal with this. Should be closed pending an Investigation. They quickly left leaving the maggot covered wrapper.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Veerpal Kaur Sran","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIBNQKpadS6X7lyFj0bmmYePq51U1wBDv_gQk6Qr4JvEOqVDw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I am really disappointed by the service and food. I went there at 9.30pm may be and the girl who was making the sub was really rude she don't even ask for the patty that which patty do you want. It was really a bad experience for me.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Roman Rapoport","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXZ1RhWJk7FNleGt5iAf_4WNTf0NEMtRINKw-n19Y7BK3Oh9vvq=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Puneet & Prabhjot were amazing, super friendly and kind. Kind of people that make you want to come back and order again.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"aarav saraon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUNpGMrFAcOG9hVTK0Vb9-EE6Ym1HHLGJafzt9fTiy4MdH_P_qS=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"A good sandwich shop. Recommend if hungry or want something else. And it is simple and very customizable, you can easily order by asking "Can I get a footlong (what sandwich you want)." Than add your toppings. The cookies are great too, they just taste so good.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ynday","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXpxBZuYdrIP3-2FyehoRc3qi4pGPkMQfcVRc4KIHLqx54GJocY=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"The cashier charged me for 3.29$ for the fountain water. If I didnt call someone I know from Subway, she will not refund me

Also, we are 4 people inside and they were in the back by the computer talking so loud with their language from back home.

Very UNPROFESSIONAL","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Bernie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVPXTBFQGy4UZogf6r0hGxUGZ8fvtwePPN5iicbAtQksaWtpwOP=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A great place for lunch on our way to the City of Mission.  We got chicken nuggets, crispy chicken sandwich, fish fillet sandwich, chocolate milkshake, iced tea and poutine. This store delivers very good food quality and the food is served fast.  It’s worth the price you pay.  The service is efficient and amazing.  Dining place is clean. Washrooms are well-maintained and neat.  There’s a need for you to ask the front cashier to use the washroom.  Parking is spacious and free.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOJKu2jfE81tLwsZq9a33OXtoyCMAqpM73xZ8Cj&fid=0x0:0x89d0f9cb00350f81"],"When":"2024-7-27"},{"Name":"Jane Carter","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKiiTPX_fDwYFOprgDX6WAKchWNE78d2wrdQHvem3ChMR34eA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"November 14th 5:30am. Wow, all I wanted was a BLT no cheese no egg. I expressed that, and when I drove away, realized I had both on my sandwich, their cheese always makes me sick so I can’t eat. I went back through, the lady who took the order was lovely but I don’t think the kitchen listened at all, I saw her modifications on the screen were correct. I got a new sandwich and this time there was only lettuce and bacon on it. So I drove back through, and the lady that gave me the food said they were out of tomatoes… I was surprised that that wouldn’t have been mentioned since it’s a pretty big part of a BLT. Honestly, I don’t even think it was true I believe she just wanted to get rid of me at that point. Anyways, she gave me a refund- for the egg BLT. So I made a dollar for wasting half an hour of my time. The times they’ve actually got it right here my BLT has been burnt or soggy. I won’t even bother with the manager because they will probably replace them when they realize business is down 1000% percent due to lack of consistency. I worked at McDonald’s for four years and this place is a joke, my boss would have scalped us if we ran the place like that. Like I said, the lady who took my order was great, so there are some good staff members but it sounds like they are promoting the wrong ones…","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Denisa Olpretean","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUl7WgjcufKdYwiFQkN2tKR_fJpCvqfyrTH6j_Z3gLcWWVojF7U=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Someone should teach nabjul the "manager" how to do her job properly and count. I bought a 6 pack of nuggets and large fries only to receive half of the large fries and only 3 nuggets. When I drove back to ask that the correct amount be given and the issue to be fixed, she accused me of lying saying "that's not possible".... WELL NABJUL it clearly is since I drove all the way back to tell you it was wrong. Don't waste your money, the McDonald's at this location has always been terrible, and to no surprise has become even worse.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMsOKqTMdlwDlUZj5DrFhoEI00VQS3_7UKW9TSu&fid=0x0:0x89d0f9cb00350f81"],"When":"2024-6-21"},{"Name":"Mehak Faridkot","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW41qVA2Ru2BH2K2bSO2hHaFsuP6L3gxSiBCs1N5JqxvhZO5Zc=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Ordered 6 junior chicken and 2 sets of medium fries. 2 junior chicken are missing from the order. ordered 3 habanero sauce but got garlic. Whole order was very cold.

Never coming back to this store.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOuTit7gmnx3hIryHkpkC5BoUobi5OSzpqxvhj6&fid=0x0:0x89d0f9cb00350f81"],"When":"2024-7-17"},{"Name":"Nick","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJWx_SrRlP1O06yBviUEWCNgig44vUBKe1GCzn2KDwj2EzM4Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Ordered takeout and paid for 2 paper bags.  Girl handed me my order on a tray.  I pointed out that it's a takeout order.  I need two bags.  She muttered something, picked up some bags and tossed it on the counter.       Then proceeded to walk away as I packed up my own order.  On the bright side, she threw 3 bags at me.  So overall, I'm gonna count that as a win.  Sep 19. 630pm.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sydney Soltesz","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUKesXoa0DOgwu8k-QJ1W5HgLsRRGht2beDOTr31REHgZFDzjQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"placed on order on the app only to be told that we can't get our food. When I asked why they said it's because the menu is unavailable, I asked but you still have the food and they said yes and told us that we would have to place a whole new order to get the food that we already placed an order for. The person was not very nice when explaining it to me and I was already annoyed because the lady at the pay window couldn't even find the order in the first place. The dumbest thing ever. McDonald's is awful.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Matt Heisler","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUsk5HdVT6j7Pb3jfkcNNOIoQF6u7VN7cXdy2Q5ytMJ4XmUZxr3=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I have been an avid visitor to this establishment for quite a while. I am friendly and never mean to employees. I have noticed this place over the last 5 years turn down hill.

Lately have been noticing my drinks only being filled 3/4 and no ice or even cooling system for the drinks. My drinks are now warm and not the actual amount of ounzes i paid for.

Also, you run the risk after 11pm any night of the week that this store closes down till the morning. I now have to drive to the other end of town or across the bridge for late night food.

I just want my go to place after work to be back to normal. After tonight, quite let down.

Well normally you see a 24 establishment maybe go down for a little bit to clean but when you close at 12:30 and not open till 4am, that is misleading. Especially on the weekend. Not very happy about this.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOTH5-xrgUslYykTFcZBEnG2DCuL5RowGWC09O-&fid=0x0:0x89d0f9cb00350f81"],"When":"2022-6-19"},{"Name":"Cassandra Tracy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU-5vKwbJUrgf_pbtU6AtIeiIYyxP3V5bWP29S8mvlOhJ7QUfRn=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I placed a mobile order for the pick up kerbside hoping it would be faster than the drive-through. I gave them my number right away when I got there. And was waiting for over 10 minutes. The kerbside pick up seems to be extremely flawed at this location. I would not recommend it.","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Ana T","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLY6qyNt5y_HddRrNE3HFvlLSKc1M3fIS2cKYSDXj52qO5dtQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently visited Jolly Coachman for the first time. I had an overall enjoyable experience and I highly recommend this local gem!

•VIBES/ATMOSPHERE
The atmosphere was laid back and the place has a fantastic old school pub feel (which is exactly the way I like a pub to be). They also have a lovely patio with some misty water spray to keep you cool in the summer. I didn’t sit on the patio, but it sure looked nice.

•SERVICE
The service was excellent. The waitress (the very tattooed young Asian lady) was fantastic. She was friendly, knowledgeable, attentive, super fast, and made me feel welcomed and comfortable. She checked on me the exact correct number of times (I get annoyed by waitresses who repeatedly pester, this one had good instincts and was on point). My order was taken immediately and my drink/food arrived fast. As a smoker who has no incentive to aimlessly hover in/around a pub with no smoking areas, speed of service is very important to me.

•DRINKS
They have a pretty extensive drink menu with lots of choices. The variety of cocktail choices impressed me as a cocktail drinker. I ordered the Blue Hawaiian. While it was more teal-green than blue and not as sweet as my sweet tooth alcohol taste desires, you couldn’t taste the alcohol but could feel it. And that is everything a successful cocktail should be. I will definitely have to be back to try more of their summer cocktails (and ask for them to be extra sweet!)

•FOOD
I noticed other people eating burgers and being the nosy follower that I sometimes can be, I thought I’d go for the burger special. But when the waitress said the burger is a regular burger, I decided to order the calamari instead (my burgers need to be irregular otherwise I’m bored, there’s a limit to my sheepish follower behaviour after all). The calamari was delicious! It was warm, fresh, crispy, flavourful and a large portion. The tomato & green onion salsa that came with it was sour and salty; tasty and refreshing. The sauce was also delicious, although if you dip every calamari piece, you will run out of sauce on your last 3 pieces. I recommend they add a tiny bit more sauce to ensure that all calamaris are successfully dipped. This calamari was the crispiest calamari I’ve ever had in my life, which was a pleasant surprise. Even the squeezed juice from my lemon and the tomato pieces didn’t and couldn’t make this calamari soggy. I bet you could pour buckets of water on this calamari and it wont lose its crunch. A waterproof non-soggy calamari. It seems I have searched my entire life for such a thing. And now I’ve finally found it!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOH4AERpkElu4yTZKq9vFJ3c1y1W2XvEbIAHOyN&fid=0x0:0xd08aec90d2675cc2"],"When":"2024-7-29"},{"Name":"Christopher Adams","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXcL5bNZ-lkkKT4gy1k5l3D2BvEp2MJobsZwK2jpBW_3saF1nbleg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Great place, really good food and service, plenty of options to eat and drink. Service was really good from Tim the bartender as the 3 of us sat at the bar be a use the place was packed.

There were reserved sections that were not getting used due to waitress shortage (2 on shift) so to not stretch the staff too thin, about 4 tables (not much) so as we could not find anywhere to sit, we chose the bar.

Had a great time, and we plan on coming back soon.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jonathan Hung","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXcyx4J66dX-2K0eJPsLn9dFQ4eU3qrPUFN-1LCa-9QqLBvskz2=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The service was fast and friendly. We went on a Friday night and it was really busy but we never had to hunt down the waitress.

The food came out in a timely manner and we were a table of five. Portions were huge and a good value for your dollar.

Returned on a Sunday night for dinner. Same good service and huge portions!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMlndTPq2rrf0rilRib01JIxdOVseUp8VM2kbzK&fid=0x0:0xd08aec90d2675cc2"],"When":"2016-10-24"},{"Name":"Phuc","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKKyZ93IRCJCH1JLRAyZ_1EXfrz5einBZ6MH8s6tB1BEDR2Ksg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This pub is a bomb! user_reviews: [{"Name":"Angela Longo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWY1oq49pKa6hIgCWasLoQyfZXLAxCQ6hu--JV9EUi6xd7-tSw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I can't get enough of this place. I have been here several times already, and every time we leave quite full and satisfied. The last time was on December 1st for our wedding anniversary. We ordered the veggie dinner combo, a side of dynamite rolls, and miso soup. The service is also top-notch. Our server, knowing that we were celebrating our anniversary, gave us a side of their dessert, fried ice cream. That was a nice and appreciated surprise. user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Kanako Sakurada","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKYybgPjG_d3LYq66Ui47Ocd_2PMrfkKaju5V_L0IyVTR19lQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Beautiful setting surrounded with flower garden and vegetable field!
Such relaxed feeling sitting outside sipping wine while hearing birds chirping.

Their food was indeed fresh, unique, and delicious! We had eggplants that melted in our mouth, gnocchi with crispy edge, and soft and juicy beef we savoured every bite.

Wine list was excellent, well thought out to match and balance their veggie forward menu. Wish I had space for a cocktail as well.
Every host and server was friendly, capable, and thoughtful. Very highly recommended!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPccUEEvPsviuccafuN4mmn8dI3nyjbsF_thq5F&fid=0x0:0xb1af0fd0c39a122b"],"When":"2024-9-30"},{"Name":"Amin Jamshidifar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUmawAHejbM9RGl-zt4ktWscRtuT9Yw9dT5UQi6bJKKTxEWL7buJw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently had the pleasure of dining at this restaurant and opted for the chef’s tasting menu. Each dish was a delightful surprise, with unique flavors and beautiful presentations. The highlight of the evening was the salmon—it was perfectly cooked, tender, and full of flavor, easily one of the best I’ve had (I forgot to take a picture of 😬). The attention to detail in every course was impressive, with creative combinations that kept me excited for what was coming next. The ambiance was cozy yet elegant. fantastic dining experience for anyone looking to explore innovative cuisine.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPFyGUCZBa1dr2me5a4Zin_xcu_yFkBYS-Vyjjc&fid=0x0:0xb1af0fd0c39a122b"],"When":"2024-9-19"},{"Name":"Tara Walker","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKW1kTu76JveMo2p9nMhdKdTyIKHMDbXw1p-Yhzvh6-6nrVrg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We held our monthly book club here and what a beautiful location. The gazebos were intimate and the staff was top notch. The food was fresh and we loved that everything was locally sourced. One of the best meals I have ever had. 100% recommend.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNjelCZui9OHyNtgz9Yxw75h_i3eoLMt1L9232Q&fid=0x0:0xb1af0fd0c39a122b"],"When":"2024-9-9"},{"Name":"Kaelen Cohen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW8VdHhgP1zfVxibP0FccLaIbx4KR3eXZIw2AzC2DGjQqLruhjpQA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Unforgettable birthday dinner for my wife. Our reservation was for 5:15 and it was pouring rain, however we had the most incredible time and the weather only added to the experience. We were warm under the patio heaters and they also supplied blankets for my wife.

Exceptional service and a visit from the chef was a nice touch. Everyone is extremely knowledgeable about the menu and entire process that goes into the operation. The staff were extremely attentive and the service was the best we've had in a long time. Refreshing to see again!

We will be back again for more!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNca0zlnR9j15lLpEw6_buAapyPm_bOJCNDAyVj&fid=0x0:0xb1af0fd0c39a122b"],"When":"2024-6-3"},{"Name":"Annie Lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIQqFhnb0FQdPjEiZPluCq2gc2XCF6bB-kKmmbsV_FIqXwnrw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’m surprised at how under the radar Sunflower Cafe is because this was such an amazing experience! It was true farm to table fine dining. I was so impressed with the food quality and presentation, the top-notch service and the super cute atmosphere! I definitely plan on coming back and introducing new people to this gem.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPqipyDS2iHK7tP7h-q_zpmXSmC9a51w8tu3UmE&fid=0x0:0xb1af0fd0c39a122b"],"When":"2024-7-21"},{"Name":"Carlo Elstak","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjURmCYKbAxd9AVUBSqowG0Mo3Qt9rlKxFPXWrnkLHqMytAynY2iXQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We went to the Sunflower Cafe based on a recommendation by a friend. We visited there last week and we were not disappointed. The setting is quite unique in a charming tent-like setting adjacent to the farm. Despite its simplicity, it is an inviting and warm environment. We opted for the tasting menu with the matching wine pairing.
After a refreshing Cucumber Amuse-bouche, we were presented with a delicious tomato salad, followed by a variety of wonderful wild mushrooms.
Our first main course was a Salmon Filet, served with a delightfully crisp skin while still maintaining a moist and perfectly cooked centre
The Beef Tenderloin that followed was cooked to perfection and melt-in-your-mouth tender.
After a Chocolate Amuse-bouche, we ended the meal with a choice of desserts.  It was impossible to pick a favourite out of the selection of Carrot Cake with Salted caramel gelato and carrot frosting, or the Sticky Toffee Pudding.
Our service was very good, the wine paring made sense, and the whole experience was very enjoyable.
A couple of improvements could be made by ensuring the hot items are served at a warmer temperature than they were. Also, servers should have an in-depth knowledge of the history and philosophy of the restaurant as one of the main reasons for the visit was to partake in a true Farm-to-Table experience.
Overall, we found this to be a wonderful find in the Lower Mainland and without a doubt will return.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMh7aZzSFKPf_9_PkEFs0EiV3cTCwqAjEpCxOym&fid=0x0:0xb1af0fd0c39a122b"],"When":"2024-9-9"},{"Name":"Stephanie Henderson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIvd6TE41ofXSIQsVETEKQwe90URxDLRLP3ccyJkWtaimnS=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This restaurant is truly a hidden gem. One of the best restaurants I’ve ever had the pleasure of dining at.

The food is Michelin star quality and each dish is meticulously executed to perfection. To say I was speechless is understatement.

Instead of farm to table, they bring the tables to the farm! Ingredients are grown on their farm or locally sourced. The menu changes depending on what’s in season.

We went for our anniversary on Sunday, even though it was raining the outside tent was warm and comfortable. The staff went above and beyond to make our anniversary an unforgettable experience.

Here are some photos from last night + the few other times we have been on sunny days. They have outdoor gazebos that are great for larger groups or date nights!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPKHnuKc_b4jmDLL_-D75P3DQ_dcjt7ehdfmj0&fid=0x0:0xb1af0fd0c39a122b"],"When":"2024-3-11"},{"Name":"Yana","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIaUlCK73O3dM9H2k784cXLtXrMmH2WgZCF6Y5SaQw97wPHYQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had an amazing dinner today! That was a truly unique farm-to-table experience. The food was great, especially the desserts, which are absolutely unmatched and a real must try. On top of that, these guys provide exceptional service and have highly qualified kitchen staff. A huge thanks to the chef, the sous chef and the rest of the staff who made our visit so special.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOV-e8zawwPujY52k-yGLDTDn6d1HP1T780e9PX&fid=0x0:0xb1af0fd0c39a122b"],"When":"2024-6-14"}]

[{"Name":"Kanako Sakurada","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKYybgPjG_d3LYq66Ui47Ocd_2PMrfkKaju5V_L0IyVTR19lQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"With so many things to choose from, I wanted to try everything! Would love to come back and try more!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPgOX0UW0ZhoqgYoqW_rmoJyqiRDNvFuE52njj3&fid=0x0:0xf6019e6a84f80e2d"],"When":"2024-9-30"},{"Name":"Danial Dehghan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVXgDzaiKXT97_r82ZF9d2HsnV9L5L_dmiF-k12CY0fufyZgoVyUw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"It's a nice bakery with plenty of options to choose from. I tried a pistachio raspberry croissant; that was absolutely delicious, and it has a new taste for me. Amazing cakes, bread, cookies, sandwiches, and coffee—everything you could want.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOSiYkJc2TAwNAWdMFYObTVlT0hU_BlOqkRXy5W&fid=0x0:0xf6019e6a84f80e2d"],"When":"2024-11-11"},{"Name":"Camilia Rodriguez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWigkoqaNhHJinW1sDEWmiP5-QkCbLl16QFp5xZiy1DDMYI0dmUuQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I came here for coffee with a friend and ended up grabbing a bite to eat. I asked the girl at the counter what I should get and she told me the best sandwich was by far the Asiago on Focaccia and I think she was right. It was delicious and they were able to make it on Gluten Free Bread for me which I really appreciated. I also ordered a Decaf half sweet Lavender Latte and it was also delicious. The drinks are made and left at the counter for customers to pick-up while the food is brought to where you are seated. My friend and I enjoyed the ambiance of the cafe and visited for a couple hours. Thanks Gratia for the excellent service. ☺️","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMOp4yTWzJUKQjVPSM4FiU0yQrySohtTMkFSFQB&fid=0x0:0xf6019e6a84f80e2d"],"When":"2024-10-21"},{"Name":"Darina Mishkova","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXgP7nSgMXisGjXETJm3txKovwig8H6PZWG5D0GvzeoGSpRJhMLnA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Almond Blueberry Chroasant, Matcha Oat Milk Latte, and Sourdough Bread. The patio looks at the parking lot behind the building,  but it's ok.
We'll be returning with my family. Thank you!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP5m38wcS9-PZMRv0orA2IDsVSQopy2h0Tjb0jQ&fid=0x0:0xf6019e6a84f80e2d"],"When":"2024-8-7"},{"Name":"Suyun Kim","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUq9V6Vha9sUNbwnt9Nj3a0dWvXMRpHq5bw4GJRrWW0eKZMhis=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Pistachio croissant was GOAT it was the best breaky ever coffee and sandwich was also very tasty I will definitely comeback here to try again! you gotta try their croissant for real","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPngR1_stW-wAmRozOgbSjL5rPgu8r13_-5Jm8&fid=0x0:0xf6019e6a84f80e2d"],"When":"2024-8-18"},{"Name":"Immanuel M","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjURCHQQ_gUlRsGGjwdJWcNj1pi4KH38rEIuyGH3UdE60vvwMfQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This place is bumpin'! user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Lisa Simmons","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLUCbM7Sv-M1pAApVUnGKleUtAL_QtjEhlmjRjJZl7LJUXJqg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Gotta say, I read complaints about service here not long ago. Not our experience at all. Service was quick, food was great. Ate it so fast, I didn't think about taking a picture of it. But the pesto chicken sandwich with fries was FAB. Hubby had pizza and loved it.

30 July 2024

Both of us had burgers, mine was the Alehouse burger, with fries. So good. Fries, were so fresh. Hubby had a burger as well, he very much enjoyed it, and he scarfed down the fries first, because they were so good. Obviously we ate so fast I didn't get a picture of the entire meal. Lol. Great spot, good service, loved the food.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMuM_CDNorBgY6WhcxWPFWJrWXNFvaFxojPeYNq&fid=0x0:0x5353b6ce1ac8c1ee"],"When":"2024-5-28"},{"Name":"Grant M","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXRWL_i5cZiVpXExK1H8xMkwx4_6CHC_xRkP2HoYZIVJehiW1g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A group of us that have known each other since Elementary School and High School, have been meeting and getting together at the Billy Minor Pub for about the past Five years.

It's convenient as one of our friends lives in the Cayman Islands, and his parents live walking distance to the Pub. So meeting here just makes it easier for him that way.

We always have a great time getting together and of course sharing some great memories along the way.

We've always been treated well at the Billy Minor Pub and well taken care of as well.

We always enjoy the food and the nice Beer selection as well.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO2-3Tu-9Z7RpRbX_-KVdQw0jYQBGmOHRUMbE6r&fid=0x0:0x5353b6ce1ac8c1ee"],"When":"2023-10-15"},{"Name":"Tanisha Bamforth","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ0LC_3KUtsRX1orCCIwBlT-_-eWOVwy4ooCYtcq_-eG4d2WA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Delicious food and good service. The cornbread is one of the best I’ve ever had and the house salad even as a side is very well made and much better than the average salad you get elsewhere. Prices are very reasonable, large selection of beers and good range of food options. Will definitely be back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMMTYrjL7ZeVUfYtaKAX8I31X6zpQsbdcu6QPXl&fid=0x0:0x5353b6ce1ac8c1ee"],"When":"2024-4-23"},{"Name":"Sarah Barnes","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV1ca2s2Ju78fXB3WcTna5eoONK6rtbXd-or7AsBLVFqiGf04UKIg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Been here a couple times now. The prices are really fair compared to other restaurants. The portion sizes are huge. Not what you'd expect considering the price. Lots of taps of beer to choose from. Definitely order the cornbread with maple butter.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNBJFOhK53KqjnTAdAUEPDfx9L0jJ9Y885SMEEV&fid=0x0:0x5353b6ce1ac8c1ee"],"When":"2024-1-14"},{"Name":"Chris Fraser","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLdFrFnRzpExWWxWQEfkMvL6U9ji3VSY-gP7YyePpl68UHCbQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great place. The patio is large and has a great view.  We went on a monday and the patio was still busy with lots of seats to choose from inside.  The pizza is great and the beer is cold.  Amazing view of the river and a great place for a stroll before or after.  The patio is a great place to celebrate in the sun or watch the sunset.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOVC_gkf1CGV2esSdsNz_5jLIblKof9l-q0mj20&fid=0x0:0x5353b6ce1ac8c1ee"],"When":"2023-6-28"},{"Name":"Ken B.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKi0UHEqvrtK9b7zXvBSni89V4qdFRQmlmzKuNqGFJ9iPTWGGw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"All the food was so tasty. The garlic sauce combined with the bbq chicken was insane, so creamy and tangy. The bell ringer burger was surprisingly good, perfect amount of spice and the chilli sauce wasn’t too sweet, it was perfectly balanced. The pizza was shockingly good, one of the better pizzas I’ve had, only issue was because the ingredients were laid on heavy it needed a bit more sauce added such as Bbq sauce or ranch on top. They have a massive beer list to choose from as well. If you haven’t tried this place yet you are missing out!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOr3INzI5mzur2sOpw0U4lDjMMR1Qv48QmvlQoY&fid=0x0:0x5353b6ce1ac8c1ee"],"When":"2021-9-11"},{"Name":"Andre Xado","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV4pF2kcxQctE24BGb5mTVOt8Vw7IK0bjuvwABeQ4ZahtlItYM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Recently went to visit this well known place that has intrigued me for the longest time.  The atmosphere is amazing.  Love the location and the decor.  Food was also great except for the wings.  Ordered hot wings and they were a tad gamey and flat.  The sauce was normal but it seems they just poured the sauce on them and heated them up.   Service was good except it seemed as though server was a bit angry or in a bad mood at first? Appeared to calm down after a while.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Michael N","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI8o8LmUdbsatKosLCY7Szl1T_faKG4qFUELCdfPSbHQ5n4Zw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Food tastes great.  First time trying the pizza.  Generous amount of toppings which is the way a pizza should be made.  The crust was salted therefore tasted like a soft pretzel. So good.  Also had the outlaw chicken burger.  I had that last time and craved it again.  Had the house salad on the side and it was also very well made.  Will look to come again next time I'm in the area.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMq8sSvU23Shd6jhmPJv4VyEPUCW4By2NSrfqQj&fid=0x0:0x5353b6ce1ac8c1ee"],"When":"2023-10-31"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Mucahit Mert Alagoz","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUlZFzlr8OmJ6ReNSeqILjiXkPYOR-Wi6HlJhjaTTE_xGsRl7kohA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"First of all, the restaurant is very clean. If you're a cleanliness freak or super picky about hygiene, this place is perfect for you. The bar, kitchen, plates, and forks – everything shines! I haven’t seen such a clean restaurant in Canada in a long time.

There was live music, which was another element that made me happy.

Now, let’s get to the food. We tried (I forgot the name, but I'll call it broccoli fries), and aside from that, I loved everything, especially the meat, which was incredibly delicious, and the portions were very large.

The prices are a bit high, but considering the portion sizes and the quality of the restaurant, it’s totally worth it.

You might have trouble finding parking, but other than that, everything was great. Big thanks to the staff for their attention and great service!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNQfyozV9UhZfpNabnL4liNRc94-Ll1rIbVgl4W&fid=0x0:0x463ff72a13f16c9b"],"When":"2024-10-25"},{"Name":"Jordan Ho","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW11-xeEA0Ih57ocfphXt0C50QwI614ll6t2qknklEqHoDt3aVy=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"A busy bistro with some delicious brunch options! The shakshuka was great, and the short rib hash had some really tender and flavourful meat, though the actual potatoes were not crunchy and a little soft and soggy. My friend did very much enjoy the pasta as well. The service was also excellent, as even though there was a car show going on this particular weekend and the restaurant was full to the brim, the waitresses were attentive, and very understanding and helpful with regards to our toddlers making accidental messes over the meal. A great restaurant with great service overall, and would come again!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNeBIa2-q_6F6HNh-vPg-xIAg_rVqfEoEc3se4q&fid=0x0:0x463ff72a13f16c9b"],"When":"2024-9-23"},{"Name":"Jenny Anderson (jennycanderson)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV5zBrQ2SgSAq7cjPWmWTgRLDBFty535Ptns-qCKJ_Edl0iJO-X=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Fantastic meal, prices and service. We ordered the risotto, beet salad, and duck confit to share between 3 people, with an espresso martini and wine to drink. For dessert, we got the seasonal pear panna cotta which was amazing! I feel like the menu was very well curated and each dish was cooked perfectly - kudos to the chef 👏

I’d recommend this restaurant for a date or girls night. Friendly, attentive, and helpful service. The ambiance was lovely and calm for an early Thursday evening and the live music was a plus.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMwRYA_-JP1Eos3hjeSCsdIuoNqAB9uC9fZTlDM&fid=0x0:0x463ff72a13f16c9b"],"When":"2024-11-22"},{"Name":"Aneesh Vaghadia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLWrL7cKUXjPtxgV-J_aqDc0U8QhiCuyIUBtGHmUeqQs8V-GQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Located in Fort Langley, Saba is a great spot for a weekend brunch.  With double height ceilings and a brick feature wall, the atmosphere is open, modern and full of light.  The staff were pleasant and quick to provide service. At 11am on a long weekend, there was no wait for a table.

The menu theme is Mediterranean, and there are a mix of options for this and for a classic breakfast as well (see menu photo). The shakshuka was excellent, served piping hot in a cast iron skillet and full of flavour. The Croque Madame was also delicious. (We enjoyed dipping the fries in the leftover shakshuka if you have a willing partner!) Each dish is around $20-25 and was very much worth it for the serving size and the flavour. Also of note, the restaurant shares ownership with Saba Cafe around the corner, so the coffee is the same good quality.

Overall, this was a great spot to come on a weekend and would definitely come back again!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMWsb_AGxONIELaF3dIw8FJrIaMZg3dURTvIf8&fid=0x0:0x463ff72a13f16c9b"],"When":"2024-8-4"},{"Name":"Natasha Giesbrecht","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJVy0F6zEhg7cM_bDmObBvf-3ZxIl5dG3C2TBScZ2piRGny9g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I love eggs bennies and I had the salmon benny today and added an avocado. It was very good. However, I had been looking at previous pictures posted here on Google Maps, and other pictures showed chunks of cooked salmon, and that's what I was expecting. Instead I got thin slices of raw salmon. I was disappointed and questioned the server on this and she explained that they had had a menu change a couple months ago. I'd never been here before so that really didn't mean anything other than the pictures posted from a year ago might not be valid any longer. In any case, the service I was given regarding my complaint was outstanding considering I still ate the full meal given and it was still delicious, just not what I was expecting. Seriously amazing service and I'll be back, though I will make sure to ask more questions before ordering the next time 😀","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMJgIPq5vsZFX38dNuFHzvesb4oTxCVxrbZmxue&fid=0x0:0x463ff72a13f16c9b"],"When":"2024-11-24"},{"Name":"AJ","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX6v4uGyFg0WW8-vpkMo_Q1qI1_-YVeHcr9BrbnKxbwivkO5GDq=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The Peaches & Cream French Toast was fantastic, though I would recommend sharing it—it was a bit too sweet for me to finish on my own. The Lamb Kefta Flatbread was also really flavorful and delicious. Overall, it was a good brunch experience. The space has a beautiful open-concept design, but it can get quite loud inside.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM_HrhNiPfFDJ23oVp-HFL_1jp3coO10XRhlWYV&fid=0x0:0x463ff72a13f16c9b"],"When":"2024-10-6"},{"Name":"Darlene Kemp","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXgwwGuFoHvNYs2Uy7o6DnrTQFssfKNuG22yRrnqcR8DXBJmDcMGg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I absolutely love and recommended Saba Bistro in Fort Langley. The service,the ambiance, the food, the food presentation and selection of beverages that are available are great. A perfect sunny day to stop by for late lunch (after a nail appointment) was the perfect end to a fabulous afternoon with my girlfriend. We were greeted right away and seated at a nice table in the middle of the restaurant. Our server was friendly, knowledgeable and attentive. I started with a prosecco and had  their grilled Ceasars salad, dressing on the side, with chicken. It was delicious and the presentation was appealing.  We were able to have conversations (without being rushed) and really relaxed during our lunch. This is a fabulous spot to chill, enjoy a Thursday afternoon, great food and ambiance. I'd definitely recommend Saba Bistro (and their fantastic staff) ... see you soon and Thank you Thank you Thank you 🙏 🥰","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO1x237tG-PKs3YjbTc2dcAJ_8w9-VFvaxybUfP&fid=0x0:0x463ff72a13f16c9b"],"When":"2024-9-21"},{"Name":"Satnam S. Sangra ਸਤਨਾਮ ਸਿੰਘ","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUDoRVzCpgfWfiLaL6rpEs8s72xDvTJgSn7X4IgOdgqRdDECOU8WA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The place was nice. I enjoyed the coffee. The menu was a little too rigid for my liking. You can remove things but can’t substitute them for something else! So essentially you may end up paying for less… Not Cool!

The veggie bowl was flavourful,  I have to say I’ve had better.

My partner ordered the breakfast sandwich on the brioche bun. It was okay….

I thought it was a little expensive for what you get…","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMPRFF4ndVsLyZJKh_HZ5a3te-hod4PLrC1fkIZ&fid=0x0:0x463ff72a13f16c9b"],"When":"2024-4-24"}]

[{"Name":"Moira Casey","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVqH8ArDou9s_zoBtlaH2uA9ZPMDv3j1_WOTzaJd-UkxMhhAnEjxw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We were very hungry when we came here and were happy to find they had burritos which they were happy to make to order due to dietary preferences/restrictions. The burritos were huge. Adriana was our lovely server but all the staff were friendly. Didn't realize until we were leaving that they serve margaritas but that will have to happen next time.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP2ZatjMgYikkgK_0-Nn52JfGlgJhFcKoliXkzy&fid=0x0:0x7911bdee6ff125d6"],"When":"2024-12-14"},{"Name":"Maria Reyes","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVT4VIguuWaBPRzr3vwjMN5Oxv5461iYNuM4q-kfJX1dGCzcrcp=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Have heard many friends recommend this place. Finally got to try it for takeout. Had a four hour stretch from purchase to eating with a quick reheat (came from fridge). The wrap has a good flavour (huh? Wow the wrap has flavour?! Appreciate that!). Both burritos were delicious and filling. Actually only could eat ⅓ of each, will save for another day.
Will recommend to others.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMshMZwMPy3BVak2HSsy1QjeaKw458TF6MS0WtX&fid=0x0:0x7911bdee6ff125d6"],"When":"2024-9-24"},{"Name":"Ben Moreno","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXbXIQA5QNY2om_rvFeJhZDcAcErydWjpf8dpxFoZ8JJurbSZgE=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very nice restaurant with beautiful theme decorations, they keep all the sliding glass windows open when the weather allows it, making it feel  like the whole restaurant is a patio.
Very good taste and  good-sized burritos, good choices of beers, and soft drinks,  fast service,  friendly servers,  the seating areas are kept very clean, recommended.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMB-G40Vox86v_d_g90w5UHE4TWUu8Euihzj6SE&fid=0x0:0x7911bdee6ff125d6"],"When":"2024-10-6"},{"Name":"Kim Lishman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWoLip5cDVmyG9tqCTLI4iijakhf4W2VYZg3aEWyBWtOfnKc61HDQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Really enjoyed the Little Donkey burrito and it kept me full for the entire afternoon. I loved reading the sign about the owner and meaning behind the restaurant. Would recommend!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNoB9ObAapXrCDCy_XxWu-OG6uDiJ-3cIDMSVxl&fid=0x0:0x7911bdee6ff125d6"],"When":"2024-9-30"},{"Name":"To Ching Chan (Raymond)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW_JNaVYtt5g0NGwmOn0CZ8D3OYXoGeQEAGHictSSpxFK2__U6u=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great burrito that’s packed with flavour and value for the money. I ordered a little donkey burrito, it may look not too much from its appearance, but when I got it, it was really heavy and kept me satiated for the whole afternoon XD.

10/10 recommended.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNjVz7VacEj2vjQ1eRCZFYPR_c07t-1HaTs0Dwi&fid=0x0:0x7911bdee6ff125d6"],"When":"2024-8-11"},{"Name":"Josiah Johnson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUfIUxbBekeLBDf62gJ6QVeoeFzTIXl8WlsfLT8nsYKNjGbXs8j=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We were going to go to a chain restaurant when we stopped in Langley but decided to walk through fort Langley instead! Boy were we pleasantly surprised by this unique burrito spot! Amazing taste, beautiful patio view, and very friendly and fast staff! Thank you!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP8cSlP1uEVWoRq1FIEudj0_r5IAkC6Bcb_UDwT&fid=0x0:0x7911bdee6ff125d6"],"When":"2024-6-15"},{"Name":"harmen k","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUE3qJRedpffMosEWeiRlm3_opTsV7XQ8-2XOHWsUXGSuTzHgxK=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The food was good, and the service was really quick. Very cute spot in Fort Langley. We had a nice day out here, and little donkey was a great spot to get some food.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM3r964Pr0cqjT4jD592eOeuwHyzUYzCA6S3Kn3&fid=0x0:0x7911bdee6ff125d6"],"When":"2024-5-19"},{"Name":"Paulina Pedrero Miranda","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXoiOld2vaC2Dv18bWNi8EDRiykD7MSCRsU3RK7RESh6xQghXxb=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing burritos!, we where starving!, and this place was excellent!, they prepared everything fast and the quality of the ingredients is sooo fresh!, the staff is very friendly!, the place is clean and have a very calm atmosphere, the burritos are big and pretty tasty! They give you valentina hot sauce😄, we order jarritos and enjoyed our meal!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOR3z2wYWdwW0yw9RcXJNR0Ebu2UHnr7WpHMOZq&fid=0x0:0x7911bdee6ff125d6"],"When":"2024-1-22"}]

user_reviews: [{"Name":"Carolyn Browne","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLbo_4BBpY-qqW0RyhEqXosu5DHABd_UOfdgR3pjBsTfrHoRQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We had a celebration of life for my father in law here. The hall was clean and we thought everything was in perfect shape. The hall is a bit old but it definitely has a rustic charm. The people who run the hall were kind and amazing people.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Debbie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVywiURI8wAtYd_iJpx0H7IbqPnhDBrcKTReNrpmFau5YdLyf1P6g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"We had our Father's celebration of life here.  The morning I picked up the keys they told me that the day before they had found out that the fridge had stopped working.  They could have informed me at that time so I was prepared, as we had a lot of cold foods which would have given us a day to find coolers and ice, instead we had a couple of hours.  Once we got to the hall and began to set up there were mice droppings on the floor, the bar, in the kitchen, in the drawers.  Something if they had been there the day before for the fridge they definitely would have noticed.  We swept and cleaned up the spaces we needed.  When we pulled out the chairs they were moldy and had mouse droppings on them as well so were unusable.  So we had to make the event standing which was hard on the older guests and caused a lot of early departures as it got to be to much.  With all of the extra cleaning and sanitizing we had to do we couldn't get it set up on time, food didn't get out and served and we had to throw out half of it as waste.  All they said they could do to compensate was $25.00 back.  I was also overcharged as their website says the hall rental is $200.00 for a celebration/day use and I was charged $250.00, which I only just noticed today looking at the site info to see who manages the hall.  I would never recommend this place to anyone.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Belinda B","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKXqn7rTojP4MXVryUqjgwCTos4gm75rJRJFw13FKFUfuS0bA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"This place was gross, went for a celebration of life couldn't use the chairs, spider webs all over the place. I felt bad for the hosts as it was a emotional day with many disappointment's, people were uncomfortable with having to stand, and you could see that they were still trying to set up and clean while people were arriving. also watching the hosts throw out food as they were informed in the morning of the event of a broken refrigeration unit that the hall knew about the day prior.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Phoenix Braund","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJmjHG6nGovc2akowXmTecyV6XF_rcoaKTD0iI94TKGTA0OZQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I wouldn't recommend this hall for anything, we rented it for a celebration of life. We ended up not being able to use the chairs as while I was setting them up I found mouse droppings all over them and they were moldy. It was disgusting there was even mouse droppings in the drawers of the kitchen which we couldn't use the fridge as it was broken and they didn't tell us until the day of the event when we picked up the keys. There was cobwebs in the bathroom like they hadn't been cleaned in months. It was a very disappointing experience making an already stressful day even worse. If I could give 0 stars I would!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Rita .A","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWPcPEbWu_De4r50YbllEm0QYkNWsu4DWQh7CaPRN6lEUhA9OA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"My daughter's rented this hall yesterday July 10th for celebration of life for their dad. Would not recommend this place couldn't use chairs they were moldy hall dirty. They new event was happening and didn't clean any thing mouse droppings every were. To bad you can't give zero star","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Rose K","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVoCr4kBFnqVi6E3MQEhRAhVdAkkj0-5N7sTDHCW0rORNV9078=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Thornhill Park is a great 13 hole disc golf course which I recommend you try. It is one of my favourite disc golf courses in Greater Vancouver.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jody Hall","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU8eD-b-qME-DWkKM7CLZwOczJ97PdUS_BaymqG6wSleVK44jRkwA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Beautiful spot for Frisbee golf.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMd1BcRI4X6VhS9XFpDLRIguNl9XYr3FBcfo9Au\u0026fid=0x0:0x7aa65cdcda893455"],"When":"2024-8-12"},{"Name":"Rob Sebastion","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVjakSj6i9_7dOk20y3wCpxp4vXE8xXOrxZQc5WQ3-s5BmvTvRT-A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"It's just not the best place. We were a group of 5 and had to wait for one of the larger tables but the wait wasn't too long. We ended up grabbing coffees from a place nearby while waiting and were told it was okay to bring them in since our table was ready. Once we ordered our food we were given a refill on coffee free of charge! The food was awesome and the service was also great! Lots of great options for breakfast, and the lunch menu looked really promising.  Will definitely recommend and return.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPbly6UT9n1kxc53vrJNwsOSaBr1Zp3GiIkO29E&fid=0x0:0x477dfcc4e00ca354"],"When":"2024-12-2"},{"Name":"Sandhya Iyengar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWWYcFo4p7ZievJafEzdENBwKuQ3ZO3m9AoFLaWoaCRR85W5BSKlw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"On our way back from Harrison Hot Springs, we decided to stop for brunch after reading some promising reviews about this restaurant. Just be prepared to spend a little extra time enjoying the atmosphere before your meal arrives.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMgINq36tEVt9GrucLXEhF6Xfmez8RzyaEl-hgP&fid=0x0:0x477dfcc4e00ca354"],"When":"2024-9-22"},{"Name":"Raven Vance","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWtidU_64uAbazm7owCnEztecVOleq8AsYe5FIg3ggYzpckLKE2=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best eggs Benny I’ve ever had. Hands down. Comparable to pike place eggs Benny restaurants. Good portion for the price. Very busy so service wasn’t 5 stars but it wasn’t bad either. A little crammed but worth it nonetheless. 6 stars for food!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPzIIJozCAgLccXZZN3cBUFa4Nh07CBqpyHbu3S&fid=0x0:0x477dfcc4e00ca354"],"When":"2024-9-14"},{"Name":"Tanya Whalen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJBQkXTZXNzSbvJfyEKweuOpjj9jjKofLdIJg2tCxNSR_f53A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"AMAZING food. Very delicious, excellent portion size, great price. Highly recommend this place.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMNE_DhPB4vz_zoIiEnIQRfv_mk_e3BaLIUV7Z1&fid=0x0:0x477dfcc4e00ca354"],"When":"2024-10-14"},{"Name":"Allison Roche","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKRxkZqNC0A9HPtfucPfr-jvVD5FIQL0dYFYovXWd3KvH4ZeA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We just stopped in here on a whim on the way home and while the restaurant was packed and our table wasn’t the greatest - the service and food was outstanding.

I asked the owner (I assume) if they had any non-diary milk for coffee and he went to check. I thought he forgot about it so I was fine without. I would have been fine with black coffee.

He came back a bit later with lactose free milk, which he had run out to the store for. Totally not what I meant ( was inquiring about nut milk) but…

It’s really rare to feel that cared for when dining out these days. I super appreciated how way over and above he went, even though that wasn’t what I asked for or expected.

We will definitely be back when we are in the area and everyone should check this place out for really good food that was decently priced.

We had the Bennie, Corned Beef Eggs, waffles and pancakes for the kids and everyone left happy, with full tummies and hearts.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Odog The Great","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU6iq9Fro6MAo2ohRNTijtSFeH43nBBDLbDNzgtyH8JUn30p9U=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing little place, good prices and large portions,
me and my friends stopped on the way out to a camping trip and it was the perfect spot!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOx8ffzybUJrT2RAV0IVU_5CP0RZOaM59BHOvZC&fid=0x0:0x477dfcc4e00ca354"],"When":"2024-9-16"},{"Name":"Lilesh K","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWZMp024jZfOBuM1XKJORf-SD1dPfa91bUxktaIyS4u5N8pRWs=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing food, exceptional service. It's my favorite breakfast place.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMBXT3Od3uaxLoTVEQEhmgxRTRDcXhYVNi2n3mX&fid=0x0:0x477dfcc4e00ca354"],"When":"2024-11-24"}]
